Zushi Kuro strain by In House Genetics is an elite dessert-gas hybrid that fuses the deep cherry sweetness of Black Cherry Pie with the exotic blueberry cream and gas of Blue Zushi. Sold in a 6-pack of feminized seeds, this strain was bred for flavor hunters, hashmakers, and connoisseurs seeking resin-heavy flowers with striking color and high-end terp appeal.

 Lineage
Black Cherry Pie x Blue ZushiType: Feminized SeedsPack Size: 6 SeedsDominant Type: Indica-Leaning Hybrid

 Aroma, Flavor & Terpenes
Zushi Kuro strain boasts a luxurious dessert terp profile with layers of cherry syrup, blueberry candy, vanilla cream, and gassy undertones. The Black Cherry Pie side contributes richness and color, while Blue Zushi enhances sweetness and adds creamy fuel for a smooth, flavorful smoke with balanced depth and power.

Zoonami Feminized Seeds - Zoap x Blue Slushi (Indica)
Buy Zoonami Cannabis Seeds Online - Premium Indica Hybrid
Zoonami cannabis seeds bring together the best of Zoap and Blue Slushi genetics to create an exotic, potent indica-dominant hybrid. This strain is known for its rich, fruity aroma blended with sweet tropical notes and a refreshing soapy finish. Zoonami delivers a euphoric mental high followed by full-body relaxation, making it the perfect choice for unwinding at the end of the day.
The buds of Zoonami are a visual masterpiece—dense, sticky, and coated in trichomes with hues of purple, green, and blue. Bright orange pistils wind through the frosty surface, giving Zoonami its striking, premium bag appeal. Whether you’re growing indoors or outdoors, this strain is a strong performer with harvests of up to 550g/m² and a flowering time of just 8-9 weeks on a 12/12 light schedule.
Medicinal users value Zoonami for its potential to relieve chronic pain, stress, depression, and nausea. With its balance of uplifting cerebral effects and soothing body calm, Zoonami makes a versatile choice for both recreational and therapeutic use. This strain is easy to grow, resin-rich, and highly suitable for solventless extraction.

Why Choose Zoonami Feminized Seeds?


Potent Zoap x Blue Slushi genetics


Dense, colorful buds with heavy trichome production


Unique fruity and soapy aroma


Euphoric, relaxing effects for evening use


High indoor/outdoor yields in just 8-9 weeks


Zoonami is a must-grow for connoisseurs and commercial cultivators alike. Order Zoonami feminized seeds nowfrom Neptune Seed Bank and bring top-shelf flavor, effects, and yield into your garden.

Product description
Zombie Storm Strain Feminized Seeds by White Clouds Genetics

What Are Zombie Storm Seeds?
Zombie Storm strain seeds by White Clouds Genetics combine Zombified and Shitstorm S1 to form a heavily sedating, visually striking feminized hybrid. Known for its grimy gas, deep coloration, and powerful couch-lock, this strain was designed for fans of old-school funk with modern frost. Each 6-pack contains all-female seeds, making them a consistent and reliable choice for serious growers.

Structure and Appearance
Zombie Storm produces dense, chunky flowers wrapped in thick trichomes. Expect deep greens, purples, and occasional jet-black hues, especially in colder climates. The plant structure stays short and bushy, with tight spacing and strong lateral branches, making it a solid fit for indoor tents or sea-of-green setups.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain reeks in the best way—expect rancid gas, burnt rubber, and earthy skunk up front, followed by hints of spice and fermented fruit. Zombified provides the dirty funk, while Shitstorm S1 adds a fuel-heavy, chemical-rich backbone. It’s the kind of aroma that fills the room before you even open the jar.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Zombie Storm is deeply relaxing, delivering a heavy body stone and mental sedation. Ideal for nighttime use, it can help manage insomnia, chronic stress, muscle tension, and appetite loss. It’s not for the faint of heart—expect strong, long-lasting effects that can flatten even seasoned smokers.

Growing Zombie Storm at Home
This feminized hybrid has a flowering time of 8-9 weeks and thrives in low to moderate-height setups. It responds well to defoliation and minor training techniques, and its sturdy frame can support heavy colas with ease. Zombie Storm is also a strong choice for solventless hash making thanks to its resin output.

Why Choose Zombie Storm Seeds?
Zombie Storm seeds are ideal for growers seeking loud funk, purple frost, and serious body effects. With unique genetics from Zombified and Shitstorm S1, this cultivar offers a memorable terp profile and a true end-of-day experience. Grab your 6-pack of feminized seeds now at Neptune Seed Bank.

About the Breeder - White Clouds Genetics
White Clouds Genetics is a craft seed company known for producing feminized hybrids with bold color, heavy resin, and potent terpene profiles. With hits like Ghost Car, Winter Storm, and Phosphorescent, their catalog appeals to both flavor chasers and extract artists. Browse the full White Clouds Genetics collection today.

Product description
Zesty Drip Strain (F) - Feminized Seeds by “42”

Zesty Drip Strain: Pure Citrus Fire from “42”
The Zesty Drip strain from breeder “42” combines two powerhouse flavor lines—Tangie and LA Zkittlez—into one vibrant, resin-heavy hybrid. This feminized release is available in both 3- and 6-seed packs. Even better, every order includes a free full pack of Sour Sage OG (Sage x Sour OG) as a bonus gift while supplies last!

Genetics: Tangie x LA Zkittlez
This fruity cross was bred for serious flavor and resin lovers.


Tangie brings bright tangerine terps, energetic highs, and strong sativa traits.


LA Zkittlez adds candy sweetness, smooth smoke, and extra bag appeal.


Together, they create the Zesty Drip strain, which offers bold citrus flavor, uplifting effects, and sticky, colorful buds.

Flavor & Aroma: Citrus Zest and Sweet Candy
From the first whiff, you’ll notice strong orange and tangerine notes. On the inhale, it’s zesty and sweet, with hints of lemon peel and candy. As you exhale, it leaves behind a clean, citrus finish with a smooth aftertaste. Thanks to its high terpene content, Zesty Drip Strain is ideal for flavorful extracts and rosin.

Effects: Energizing, Uplifting, and Smooth
Zesty Drip starts with a clear-headed, happy lift that boosts focus and creativity. While it energizes your mind, it also provides a light body buzz that keeps you relaxed—but not weighed down. Because of its balance, it’s a great daytime strain or a perfect pick-me-up for slow afternoons.

Medicinal Benefits: Great for Mood and Fatigue
This strain may help users manage stress, anxiety, and mental fatigue. Its upbeat nature also makes it useful for those dealing with low mood or social tension. Since it doesn’t cause heavy sedation, it’s a good option for people looking to stay active and focused throughout the day.

How to Grow Zesty Drip
These feminized seeds are easy to manage indoors or outside. Plants stay medium in height with strong branching and a thick layer of trichomes. Flowering time runs about 8-9 weeks, and the finished buds are sticky, colorful, and bursting with citrus aroma. With proper care, you can expect solid yields and excellent wash potential.

Why Choose Zesty Drip Seeds by 42?
The Zesty Drip strain brings together loud terps, balanced effects, and top-tier resin production. Whether you’re growing for flavor, extractions, or visual appeal, this cross checks every box. Plus, you get a full pack of Sour Sage OGabsolutely free with your order. Grab your 3- or 6-pack now, only at Neptune Seed Bank!

Zagnut Strain Regular Seeds by Uprising Seed Co.
Zagnut strain by Uprising Seed Co. is a dessert-meets-gas powerhouse that blends the sweet, doughy terps of PCG Cookies with the sharp fuel and lemon-pine punch of Fire OG Bx3. Offered in a 10-pack of regular seeds, this cultivar is bred for big flavor, resin-rich buds, and heavy-hitting potency—perfect for connoisseurs and extract artists.

 Lineage
PCG Cookies x Fire OG Bx3Type: Regular SeedsPack Size: 10 SeedsDominant Type: Indica-Leaning Hybrid

 Aroma, Flavor & Terpenes
Zagnut strain combines fresh-baked cookie dough, vanilla cream, and sweet earth from PCG Cookies with OG gas, citrus zest, and earthy pine from Fire OG Bx3. The result is a loud, layered terp profile that’s dessert-forward with a powerful gassy backend.

⚡ Effects & Experience
Expect a fast-hitting head rush followed by deep physical relaxation. Zagnut is ideal for evening sessions, stress relief, and full-body calm. Its long-lasting effects and flavorful smoke make it a staple for heavy indica lovers.

 Growing Info
Zagnut strain produces dense, frost-covered flowers with medium height and strong branching. It finishes in 8-9 weeks, displaying deep green and purple hues. Exceptional resin content makes it a top choice for solventless hash production.

 Why Choose Zagnut by Uprising Seed Co.?


 Dessert cookie terps with OG gas punch


 High resin output for hashmakers and extractors


 Indica-leaning effects: potent, relaxing, and long-lasting

strain_name: In House Genetics - (Yellow Zushi x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44
description:
Product description
In House Genetics - (Yellow Zushi x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44 (Feminized Seeds)
Key Info

Strain Name: (Yellow Zushi x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44
Dominant Type: Indica-dominant hybrid
Type of Seed: Feminized
Lineage: (Yellow Zushi x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44
Breeder: In House Genetics
Aromas/Flavors: Citrus zest, candy gas, creamy kush, tropical funk
Effects: Euphoric, relaxing, stoney, body-heavy
Appearance Summary: Frosty, colorful, exotic
Detailed Appearance: Bright green buds with lavender undertones, thick trichomes, and neon orange pistils
Aroma Summary: Sweet and citrusy upfront; complex gas and spice after the grind
Medicinal Benefits: Stress, insomnia, pain, low appetite
Growing Info: Great indoors, mid-height, heavy resin, 8-9 week flowering, moderate difficulty




Overview
(Yellow Zushi x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44 is a standout feminized hybrid from In House Genetics, blending three terpene titans into one powerhouse strain. The Zushi parents bring vibrant citrus and exotic gas, while Slurricane 44 adds frosty density and calming power.
Ideal for growers who chase flavor and resin, this cross offers high bag appeal and serious potency. Each presale pack includes 12 feminized seeds—limited drop, maximum impact.



What It Looks Like
These flowers are resin-coated with vivid color. Expect lime green buds kissed with lavender and purple swirls. The structure is dense and rounded, with eye-popping trichome coverage and bright pistil contrast.



Aroma & Flavor Profile

The Velvet Rozay strain by Neptune Pharms blends the best of Lemonade, London Pound Cake (LPC), and Rozayinto a terp-rich feminized hybrid. This vibrant cultivar offers a balanced experience that’s both uplifting and relaxing. Available in 3- or 6-seed packs, it’s perfect for growers who want flavor, bag appeal, and reliable results.

Genetics: Lemonade x LPC x Rozay
This cross brings together three popular cultivars:


Lemonade adds bright citrus terps and a happy, clear-headed high.


London Pound Cake (LPC) delivers smooth, berry-like flavor and calming effects.


Rozay contributes floral notes and resin-heavy buds.


Together, they create the Velvet Rozay strain, which delivers great flavor and a soothing yet functional high.

Aroma and Flavor: Citrus, Berry, and Floral
As it grows, the Velvet Rozay strain gives off a strong citrus aroma with sweet, floral undertones. The flavor is just as complex, with notes of lemon, ripe berries, and a subtle hint of candy. Because of its loud terpene profile, this strain is ideal for both flower and extracts.

Effects: Relaxed, Uplifted, and Balanced
This strain starts with an energizing mental lift, followed by a smooth body buzz that helps you unwind. While it calms your nerves, it doesn’t weigh you down—so it works well for both day and evening use. For this reason, Velvet Rozayis a go-to for those who want balance in their session.

Medicinal Benefits of Velvet Rozay Strain
Many users find the Velvet Rozay strain helpful for reducing stress, easing mild pain, and improving mood. Because it combines calming and uplifting effects, it’s especially useful for managing daily stress and mental fatigue. It also offers relief without heavy sedation.

How to Grow Velvet Rozay Strain
These feminized seeds perform well both indoors and outdoors. Plants flower in about 8-9 weeks and stay at a medium height. Buds grow dense and colorful, coated in resin and packed with terpenes. With proper care, growers can expect high yields and top-shelf quality.

Why Choose Velvet Rozay Feminized Seeds?
The Velvet Rozay strain brings together bold citrus flavors, balanced effects, and a smooth grow cycle. It’s perfect for those who love sweet terps and powerful visuals. Available in 3- and 6-seed packs, it fits any size grow. Grab your pack now from Neptune Seed Bank.

About the Breeder: Neptune Pharms
Neptune Pharms is the house brand of Neptune Seed Bank, known for producing millions of feminized and auto-flower seeds. They specialize in high-yield, terpene-rich strains that work well for both commercial and hobby growers. Their offerings are built for ease of use and strong results. What Are Vanilla Frosting Seeds?
Vanilla Frosting strain seeds by Humboldt Seed Co merge the heavy resin production of Humboldt Frost with the rich dessert terps of Humboldt Gelato Bx3. This feminized hybrid delivers creamy vanilla flavors, stunning visual appeal, and potent hybrid effects. Available in 3- or 5-pack feminized seed options, Vanilla Frosting is perfect for growers seeking sweetness, power, and top-shelf quality.

Structure and Appearance
Vanilla Frosting plants grow medium to tall with thick branches supporting large, frosty colas. Buds are dense and colorful, often showing lime green and purple tones under thick trichome coverage. Its strong structure and short internodes make it ideal for indoor cultivation or light-deprivation setups.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
True to its name, Vanilla Frosting brings a sweet vanilla cream aroma, layered with gassy undertones and hints of sugary dough. Humboldt Gelato genetics intensify the creamy sweetness, while Humboldt Frost brings fuel and frost. The flavor lingers with a smooth dessert-like finish on every exhale.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Vanilla Frosting offers a balanced, euphoric high starting with a mental lift and gradually easing into full-body relaxation. It’s perfect for afternoon or evening use, aiding in the relief of stress, anxiety, mild pain, and insomnia. It’s potent yet smooth, delivering comfort without overwhelming sedation.

Growing Vanilla Frosting at Home
Vanilla Frosting flowers in 8-9 weeks, thriving in indoor, greenhouse, or outdoor gardens. It responds well to topping, SCROG setups, and moderate defoliation. Growers can expect moderate-to-high yields of resin-heavy, aromatic buds that make this strain a hashmaker’s favorite.

Why Choose Vanilla Frosting Seeds?
Vanilla Frosting seeds bring together elite dessert terps, gorgeous bag appeal, and potent hybrid effects in a dependable feminized format. Bred by Humboldt Seed Co, this hybrid checks every box for growers chasing sweet flavors, heavy frost, and therapeutic strength. Why Choose Vampire Kiss Seeds?

Tropical Trophy from Surfr Seeds brings out the best of Tropical Blunt and Trophy Wife. This unique regular seed cross offers stunning terps, bright colors, and heavy resin. Genetics Behind Tropical Trophy
This cross blends two flavorful cultivars into one standout hybrid:


Tropical Blunt provides loud tropical fruit notes and vibrant bud structure.


Trophy Wife contributes thick frost, creamy aromas, and balanced effects.


Combined, they create a plant that is easy to grow, full of flavor, and visually stunning. Not only does it stand out in the garden, but it also performs well in the jar and press.

Aroma and Flavor: Fruity, Creamy, and Loud
Expect a bold tropical scent as your plants begin to flower. You’ll notice mango, pineapple, and citrus notes up front, followed by creamy vanilla and a touch of fuel. This strain offers a smooth, sweet inhale and a rich, flavorful exhale. Due to its strong terpene output, it’s also an excellent choice for solventless extractions.

Growing Tropical Trophy at Home

Why Tropical Trophy Belongs in Your Grow

Thorpe’s Gold Strain Auto Feminized Seeds - Bred by Gnome Automatics

What Are Thorpe’s Gold Auto Strain Feminized Seeds?
Thorpe’s Gold seeds from Gnome Automatics combine the sweet sunrise flavors of Mango Sunrise with the dark, mysterious funk of Moth Man in a fast-finishing, frost-laden autoflower. This strain was bred for terp hunters, extractors, and auto lovers alike. Each 3 or 5-pack of feminized auto seeds comes with a bonus pack of The Forge—another hit from the Gnome vault.

Structure and Appearance
This strain grows compact to medium height, making it ideal for small grow spaces and stealthy setups. Expect deep green leaves, occasional purple tones, and dense, trichome-covered buds. Its strong central cola and even canopy make it easy to manage during the full lifecycle.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Thorpe’s Gold bursts with tropical mango, citrus zest, musky funk, and earthy hash. Mango Sunrise brings sweet and fruity notes, while Moth Man adds depth with rich, gassy undertones. The result is a tropical funk bomb with a creamy backend—perfect for hash making or full-spectrum extractions.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Thorpe’s Gold seeds produce flower with a mood-boosting head high and a smooth body buzz that eases tension without full sedation. It’s great for daytime sessions or creative work. Medicinal users may find relief from anxiety, low mood, and minor inflammation.

Growing Thorpe’s Gold Auto Feminized Seeds
This strain finishes in around 70-80 days from seed to harvest. It thrives in both soil and hydro systems, and it benefits from LST or light pruning. Its short life cycle, strong resistance to pests, and excellent resin output make it a favorite for new growers and extractors.

Why Choose Thorpe’s Gold Seeds?
Thorpe’s Gold seeds offer elite autoflower genetics that shine with tropical flavors, heavy frost, and well-rounded effects. Bred by Gnome Automatics, this cultivar is both stable and unique. Each order includes a freebie pack of The Forge, giving you two bangers in one drop. Order your 3 or 5-pack now at Neptune Seed Bank.

About the Breeder - Gnome Automatics
Gnome Automatics is known for its elite autoflowering strains that rival photoperiods in terp profile, structure, and resin production. Their lineup includes flavor-driven hits like Mango Sunrise, Bobby’s Widow, and Moth Man. If you’re serious about autoflowers, Gnome’s work belongs in your tent.

strain_name: Katsu Seeds - Thai Neville’s Haze x Northern Lights #5
description:
Product description
Buy Thai Neville’s Haze x Northern Lights #5 Cannabis Seeds - Neptune Seed Bank
Thai Neville’s Haze x Northern Lights #5 feminized seeds from Katsu Seeds combine two icons from opposite ends of the cannabis spectrum. On one side is Thai Neville’s Haze, a landrace-inspired hybrid with soaring, psychedelic highs. On the other is Northern Lights #5, a late-’80s indica clone known for fast finishes, structure, and narcotic weight. Together, they create hybrids with serious resin, wide expression, and balanced intensity.
Key Information


Strain Name: Thai Neville’s Haze x Northern Lights #5


Lineage: Thai Neville’s Haze x Northern Lights #5


Seed Type: Feminized Seeds


Seeds Per Pack: 6


Breeder: Katsu Seeds


Flavor, Aroma & Effects
The terpene profile swings across a wide range. Haze phenos lean toward spice, incense, and pine fuel. Northern Lights phenos, however, bring plum-pepper funk, earthy sweetness, and hash-like depth. As a result, the flowers are layered and unique.
The high also shows dual influence. At first, the haze side delivers a clear, euphoric lift that can feel electric. Soon after, Northern Lights #5 grounds the experience with dense, narcotic calm. Therefore, this hybrid is both uplifting and body-heavy. For some, it even carries a psychedelic edge.


Aromas: Spice, incense, pine, plum funk, earthy hash


Flavors: Spiced fuel, citrus pine, earthy sweetness


Effects: Euphoric, mentally bright, physically heavy, balanced


Growing Thai Neville’s Haze x Northern Lights #5
This hybrid offers a wide range of growth patterns. Thai Neville’s Haze stretches tall, produces minimal leaf, and builds long towers of silver frost. NL5, in contrast, keeps plants shorter, denser, and faster to finish. In many cases, growers will find hybrids that fall in the middle.
Flowering takes 10-12 weeks, depending on pheno. Yields are high, especially when the vigor of haze meets the density of NL5. In addition, resin production is heavy across all expressions, making this hybrid a strong choice for extraction.


Difficulty: Moderate to advanced; training is recommended


Structure: Tall spears or squat resin-packed colas


Flowering Time: 10-12 weeks


Yields: High; frosty buds with early trichome coverage


Why Choose Thai Neville’s Haze x Northern Lights #5?


Brings together two legendary strains with opposite traits


Produces wide pheno variety for hunters and breeders


Offers bold terpene mixes of spice, incense, earth, and fruit


Feminized seeds ensure female plants only


A collector’s choice for old-world hybrids

Sweet Stripes Strain Feminized Seeds by Star Fire Genetix

What Are Sweet Stripes Seeds?
Sweet Stripes strain seeds by Star Fire Genetix bring together two top-tier cultivars—London Mints and Apples and Bananas—in a feminized hybrid that hits hard on both flavor and resin. This decadent cross produces sweet minty cream terps with tropical funk, delivering gorgeous buds, strong effects, and top-shelf hash potential.

Structure and Appearance
Sweet Stripes grows with a medium height and bushy frame, stacking resinous, dense colas with purple tints and vibrant trichomes. It forms tight internodes and develops exceptional bag appeal, making it ideal for indoor and greenhouse cultivation. The plant responds well to topping and moderate defoliation.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect a rich mix of cool mint, creamy vanilla, sweet banana, and gasoline undertones. London Mints provides the frosty mint profile, while Apples and Bananas layers in tropical sweetness and backend funk. This combination creates a bold, candy-forward smoke that’s smooth and flavorful from start to finish.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Sweet Stripes delivers a relaxed, mood-lifting high with euphoric head effects and a soothing body buzz. It’s perfect for evening use, social relaxation, or winding down after a long day. Medicinal users may find relief from anxiety, muscle tension, and low mood, thanks to its calming but not overly sedative profile.

Growing Sweet Stripes at Home
Sweet Stripes flowers in 8-9 weeks and produces medium-to-heavy yields of frosted, terpene-rich buds. It thrives in indoor setups, greenhouses, or well-managed outdoor grows, and performs well under low-stress training. Its greasy trichome heads also make it a great option for solventless extraction.

Why Choose Sweet Stripes Seeds?
Sweet Stripes seeds deliver dessert-style terps, reliable structure, and versatile effects in a feminized format. Bred by Star Fire Genetix, this London Mints x Apples and Bananas cross is a flavorful addition to any grower’s lineup. Grab your 11-pack of feminized seeds now at Neptune Seed Bank and grow something uniquely sweet and gassy.

About the Breeder - Star Fire Genetix
Star Fire Genetix specializes in high-terpene, high-resin hybrids designed for flavor chasers and hash artists. Known for standouts like Appleade, Limonada, and Banana Pancakes, their catalog delivers consistent potency, bag appeal, and exotic aromas. Browse more Star Fire Genetix strains.

description:
Product description
Sundae Driver x Trophy Wife - Regular Seeds by Surfr Seeds

A Sweet and Creamy Hybrid from Surfr Seeds
Surfr Seeds brings together two standout strains in Sundae Driver x Trophy Wife. This 15-pack of regular seeds blends flavor, resin, and effect into one amazing cultivar. Whether you’re a breeder, grower, or connoisseur, this hybrid is built to impress. Because it’s a regular release, you also get the chance to hunt males or females for your next project.

Genetics: Sundae Driver x Trophy Wife
This cross combines the best of both worlds:


Sundae Driver is known for its smooth smoke, fruity dessert flavors, and calming high.


Trophy Wife brings frosty buds, creamy notes, and a touch of gas to the mix.


Together, they form a balanced hybrid that offers sweetness, visual appeal, and a relaxing experience without being overwhelming.

Flavor and Aroma: Creamy, Fruity, and Loud
Right from flower, this strain releases a creamy berry scent that fills the room. When smoked, it tastes like sweet dessert with subtle earthy notes. On the exhale, you may notice vanilla, grape, and a hint of gas. Thanks to its rich terpene profile, it’s also great for rosin and extract lovers.

Effects: Smooth, Relaxing, and Uplifting
Sundae Driver x Trophy Wife offers a feel-good high that won’t knock you out. First, it gives you a calm, happy headspace. Then, a light body buzz follows, easing tension without full couch lock. Because of this, it’s great for afternoon or evening use.

Medical Benefits: Soothing and Mood-Boosting
This strain may help reduce stress, anxiety, and mild pain. Many users also report feeling more relaxed and content after just a few puffs. If you’re looking for something to help unwind without feeling too heavy, this could be a great fit.

Growing Info: Strong, Resinous, and Worth the Effort
These regular seeds grow strong in both indoor and outdoor settings. Flowering takes about 8-10 weeks, and with proper care, you’ll see colorful, frosty buds. Plants produce heavy resin and are easy to trim. Because it’s a regular release, it’s also great for breeders looking to make unique new crosses.

Why Choose Sundae Driver x Trophy Wife?
This hybrid brings you flavor, structure, and relaxing effects in one standout package. It’s great for pressing, smoking, or breeding, and it produces excellent results with a little care. Whether you’re growing for yourself or searching for a future stud or keeper female, this strain delivers. Pick up your 15-pack of regular seeds today at Neptune Seed Bank.

Product description
Strawberry Jambi Strain Seeds - Lovin In Her Eyes (Feminized)

What Are Strawberry Jambi Seeds?
Strawberry Jambi strain seeds by Lovin In Her Eyes are a powerful cross of Zambi and Strawberry Cadillac, delivering sweet berry funk, exotic color, and balanced effects. This feminized hybrid is bred to please the senses—whether you’re chasing flavor, frost, or rare lineage, Strawberry Jambi brings it all together in one striking plant.
With six feminized seeds per pack, this drop is easy to run while offering elite quality in every phenotype.

Plant Structure and Appearance
Strawberry Jambi plants grow with medium height and strong lateral branching. Expect dense, round buds that turn deep purple and silver near the end of flower. Resin production is heavy, and the plant’s tight structure makes it ideal for indoor growing and controlled environments.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
The flavor is where Strawberry Jambi shines. From the Strawberry Cadillac side, you’ll get creamy berry, vanilla, and a fruity sweetness. Zambi adds complexity with exotic spice, musky floral notes, and a hint of sour funk. The overall profile is loud, layered, and lingers long after the exhale.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Strawberry Jambi strain seeds produce a hybrid effect that leans euphoric and creative without going too sedative. The high begins with a wave of mental clarity and calm, followed by a relaxing body buzz. Many users report relief from stress, low mood, and tension. This makes it a great strain for social use, art sessions, or decompressing after a long day.

Growing Strawberry Jambi Seeds
These feminized seeds flower in approximately 8-9 weeks. Strawberry Jambi performs well in indoor grows, greenhouses, and controlled outdoor environments. Plants benefit from topping and light defoliation to boost airflow and maximize bud development. The heavy resin content also makes this strain a favorite for solventless extractors.

Why Choose Strawberry Jambi Seeds?
Strawberry Jambi seeds are the perfect pick for those who want rich berry terps, bold visuals, and balanced, feel-good effects. The Zambi x Strawberry Cadillac pairing offers both novelty and performance. Pick up your 6-pack today at Neptune Seed Bank and add this limited-edition beauty to your lineup.

About the Breeder - Lovin In Her Eyes
Lovin In Her Eyes is a Colorado-based boutique breeder celebrated for her luxurious, terpene-rich crosses and artistic vision. Each strain—like Silver Stream, Strawberry Cadillac, and Midnight Moonlight—is crafted with beauty, emotion, and flavor in mind. Her genetics are highly sought-after by collectors, pheno hunters, and terp lovers alike.

What Are Strawberry Cheesecake Seeds?
Strawberry Cheesecake strain seeds from Humboldt Seed Co combine the legendary genetics of PPD (Purple Panty Dropper), Strawberry Cheesecake, and Vanilla Latte Auto to create a dessert-flavored feminized hybrid with sweet terps and vibrant appeal. Structure and Appearance

Flavor and Aroma Profile
The terpene profile is a dessert lover’s dream—ripe strawberry, creamy vanilla, and sugary dough dominate the palate. PPD contributes fruity tartness, Strawberry Cheesecake adds rich berry notes, and Vanilla Latte Auto layers in smooth, milky sweetness. Every puff tastes like a fresh-baked strawberry cheesecake with a hint of coffee cream.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits

It’s a great choice for managing stress, mood swings, mild pain, and appetite loss. Its calming nature makes it perfect for afternoons or early evenings without overwhelming sedation.

Growing Strawberry Cheesecake at Home
This feminized hybrid flowers in about 8-9 weeks, producing moderate-to-high yields. It’s beginner-friendly and thrives in indoor, greenhouse, or well-controlled outdoor environments. Thanks to its sturdy structure, it handles topping, SCROG, and light defoliation easily, rewarding growers with top-shelf bag appeal and rich terpene production.

Why Choose Strawberry Cheesecake Seeds?
Strawberry Cheesecake seeds deliver dessert-grade flavor, colorful bag appeal, and relaxing hybrid effects in a fast, easy-to-grow package. Strain Name: Sensi Star x Gas Casket

Flavor, Aroma & Effects
The aroma is loud and layered. Sensi Star adds citrus and earthy notes, while Gas Casket brings fuel, rubber, and kush funk. Together they create a profile that cuts through any room.
The smoke is thick and greasy. On the inhale, you’ll notice sharp citrus and spice. On the exhale, however, the flavor shifts toward gas and earth. The effects arrive quickly and heavily. First, you’ll feel pressure behind the eyes, then the body relaxes completely. For many, the high ends in deep calm and couch lock.

strain_name: Surfr Seeds - Star Pebbles x Trophy Wife
description:
Product description
Star Pebbles x Trophy Wife - Feminized Seeds by Surfr Seeds

A Beautiful Cross with Flavor and Power
Surfr Seeds delivers again with Star Pebbles x Trophy Wife, a feminized hybrid made for flavor lovers and serious growers alike. This 10-pack of female seeds produces vibrant plants that smell amazing, taste even better, and hit just right. Whether you’re growing indoors or outdoors, this strain brings both beauty and strength to your garden.

Genetics: Star Pebbles x Trophy Wife
This cross brings together two unique strains:


Star Pebbles is known for its colorful buds and fruity, candy-like flavor.


Trophy Wife adds creamy undertones, high resin content, and relaxing effects.


Together, they create a balanced hybrid with a sweet aroma, sticky buds, and a smooth, calming high. This combo offers both bag appeal and potency.

Flavors and Aromas: Fruity, Creamy, and Loud
From the moment it starts to flower, this strain fills the room with a strong fruity scent. The flavor blends notes of berries, grape candy, and a hint of cream. On the exhale, it leaves a smooth, sweet finish with a slightly herbal kick. Because of its strong terpene profile, it’s a great choice for pressing or making extracts.

Effects: Calm, Focused, and Happy
Star Pebbles x Trophy Wife offers a balanced high that starts in the head and gently spreads to the body. At first, you may feel focused, clear, and uplifted. As time passes, a relaxing body buzz takes over, helping you feel calm but not couch-locked. For that reason, it’s perfect for day or night use.

Medical Benefits: Great for Mood and Relaxation
This hybrid may help ease anxiety, stress, and mild pain. Its calming effects can improve mood without making you too sleepy. In addition, many users say it helps with focus and daily stress. If you’re looking for a happy, easy-going strain, this one’s a solid choice.

How to Grow: Easy, Resinous, and Colorful
These feminized seeds grow strong and steady in most environments. Expect flowering in 8-9 weeks, with colorful buds and plenty of frost. Plants stay medium in height, making them great for indoor tents. With a little care, growers can expect sticky, high-yielding results.

Why Grow Star Pebbles x Trophy Wife?
This strain brings flavor, potency, and visual appeal all in one. It’s easy to grow and rewarding to smoke. Whether you’re in it for the fruit-forward terps, the resin, or the effects, you won’t be disappointed. Grab your 10-pack of feminized seeds today at Neptune Seed Bank.

description:
Product description
Star Fox and Moth Man Strain Auto Feminized Seeds - Bred by Gnome Automatics

What Are Star Fox and Moth Man Auto Feminized Seeds?
Star Fox and Moth Man strain  seeds by Gnome Automatics bring together two of the most unique autoflower genetics in one frost-heavy, flavor-packed hybrid. This cross is bred for growers who want bold terpene profiles, dark visual appeal, and standout resin production—all in an auto feminized 5-pack. Every order includes a freebie pack of The Forge, another elite autoflower from Gnome’s arsenal.

Structure and Appearance
This cultivar produces compact to medium-sized plants with great stacking and excellent trichome coverage. The buds often display deep purples and silvery frost, supported by thick stems and strong lateral growth. Its structure is perfect for both tent growers and light-dep outdoor setups.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect a unique blend of spicy funk, berry sweetness, citrus, and fuel. Star Fox contributes fruity top notes and creamy undertones, while Moth Man brings in musky depth and skunky haze. The result is a loud, layered terpene profile that hashmakers love and connoisseurs chase.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Star Fox and Moth Man strain seeds produce flowers with a balanced hybrid effect—uplifting and creative up top, followed by body-melting calm. It’s a great option for daytime relief from anxiety or inflammation, or for evening chill without full couchlock. Medical users may find it helpful for stress, pain, and mood enhancement.

Growing Star Fox and Moth Man Auto Feminized Seeds
This strain finishes in around 70-80 days from seed to harvest. It performs exceptionally well under strong LED lighting or outdoor sun, with minimal training needed. The dense buds, heavy trichome output, and loud aroma make it an excellent option for solventless extractions and rosin.

Why Choose Star Fox and Moth Man Seeds?
If you’re looking for feminized autoflower seeds with elite breeding, flavor complexity, and hash potential, Star Fox and Moth Man seeds are the move. Bred by Gnome Automatics, this 5-pack includes free seeds of The Forge, giving you even more value in every drop. Get yours today at Neptune Seed Bank while supplies last.

Product description
Stank Cake F1 Strain Regular Seeds - Bred by Romulan Genetics x Katsu

What Are Stank Cake Strain F1 Regular Seeds?
Stank Cake F1 regular seeds are the result of a flavorful and potent collab between Romulan Genetics and Katsu. This indica-dominant hybrid crosses Vanilla Frosted Cake—a strain known for its sweet frosting and gas—with the legendary Romulan, adding deep body effects and earthy funk. The result is a cultivar that blends dessert terps with piney power, ideal for fans of relaxing indicas with a complex nose. With 12 regular seeds per pack, this drop is perfect for pheno hunters and breeders alike.

Structure and Appearance
Stank Cake F1 grows low and thick, with a bushy canopy and tight node spacing. The plants develop chunky colas with heavy resin production and deep coloration in late flower. Buds appear dense and sticky, often showing shades of green, lavender, and silver-white frost. Due to its sturdy structure, it handles topping and light training well.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain explodes with creamy vanilla, bakery dough, and sharp gas. Vanilla Frosted Cake brings sugary, dessert-like notes, while Romulan adds pine, earth, and diesel funk. On the inhale, expect sweet frosting and subtle citrus; on the exhale, the flavor shifts into deep earthy kush and fuel. As a result, it’s a terp bomb ideal for both flower and extraction.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Stank Cake F1 offers strong body relaxation with a balanced, euphoric high. The buzz begins behind the eyes and gently spreads through the body, easing stress and softening tension. Because of its indica effects, it’s best suited for evening use or low-stress weekends. Medicinal users may find relief from anxiety, chronic pain, muscle tension, and insomnia.

Growing Stank Cake F1 Regular Seeds
Stank Cake F1 flowers in 60-65 days and thrives in controlled indoor environments or greenhouses. It prefers moderate feeding and steady airflow during late flower due to its dense buds. Growers can expect medium-to-high yields with rich terpene returns and impressive resin content. The regular seed format also offers opportunities for selecting standout males and females for future breeding.

Why Choose Stank Cake F1 Seeds?
Stank Cake F1 seeds combine the dessert-forward terps of Vanilla Frosted Cake with the timeless power of Romulan in one elite collaboration. Created by Romulan Genetics and Katsu, this cross delivers flavor, potency, and stability in every pack. Order your 12-pack now at Neptune Seed Bank and unlock a frosty, flavorful indica with breeder-quality potential.

About the Breeders - Romulan Genetics & Katsu
This collab pairs two respected breeders. Romulan Genetics is known for therapeutic hybrids and classic frost, while Katsu built his legacy with heavy hitters like Katsu Bubba and unique OG crosses. Together, they’ve created a strain with loud flavor, stable growth, and deep, relaxing effects.

Squirt Strain Feminized Seeds by Humboldt Seed Co

What Are Squirt Seeds?
Squirt strain seeds from Humboldt Seed Co combine the sweet berry smoothness of Blueberry Muffin with the bright citrus burst of Tangie, creating a vibrant feminized hybrid packed with loud terps, quick flowering, and energetic effects. These feminized seeds, available in 3- or 5-pack options, are designed for growers who love zesty, flavorful flower and easy grows.

Structure and Appearance
Squirt grows into a compact, bushy plant with dense, trichome-rich buds. Expect bright green flowers accented by orange pistils and sometimes purple flashes late in bloom. This strain is perfect for small spaces and low-stress training, making it highly versatile for indoor and greenhouse setups.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Prepare your senses for a blast of citrus soda, sweet berries, and tangy zest. Tangie brings powerful orange and tangerine terps, while Blueberry Muffin adds a smooth, sweet backbone. The result? A refreshing, juicy flavor explosion that sticks to your palate and fills the room with fruity goodness.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Squirt delivers an uplifting, mood-boosting high with clear-headed focus and light physical relaxation. It’s ideal for creative work, socializing, or outdoor activities. Medicinal users may appreciate its ability to relieve fatigue, mild anxiety, and low mood without heavy sedation.

Growing Squirt at Home
Squirt finishes flowering in just 7-8 weeks, making it a fast, reliable option for growers seeking multiple harvests per year. It thrives in indoor, outdoor, and greenhouse environments and is resistant to common pests and mold. Its strong lateral branching and quick finish make it beginner-friendly and a favorite among production growers.

Why Choose Squirt Seeds?
Squirt seeds offer fast flowering, explosive citrus terps, and uplifting hybrid effects in a reliable feminized format. Bred by Humboldt Seed Co, this Blueberry Muffin x Tangie cross is perfect for growers who prioritize flavor, speed, and easy cultivation. Order your 3- or 5-pack today from Neptune Seed Bank and add a burst of freshness to your garden.

About the Breeder - Humboldt Seed Co

Product description
Spiked Lemonade Strain Seeds - Lovin In Her Eyes (Feminized)

What Are Spiked Lemonade Seeds?
Spiked Lemonade strain seeds by Lovin In Her Eyes are a refreshing new cross of Peach Lemonade and Winterberry, bred for flavor, color, and calm. This feminized hybrid delivers citrus brightness with sweet berry depth, all wrapped in frosty, purple-hued buds. Crafted in small batches, this strain is a must for collectors and terp hunters alike.
Each 6-pack contains feminized seeds, offering a smooth and consistent grow experience from start to finish.

Structure and Appearance
Spiked Lemonade plants grow medium in height with balanced structure and strong branching. As flowering progresses, buds develop rich green and violet tones coated in shimmering trichomes. The dense colas are eye-catching and resin-rich, making this strain perfect for both flower and hash lovers.

Aroma and Flavor
This strain smells like a splash of citrus soda with hints of berry and cream. The Peach Lemonade parent delivers tangy, fruity top notes, while Winterberry brings complexity with soft sweetness and floral gas. On the exhale, expect a smooth, candy-like flavor that lingers long after the smoke clears.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Spiked Lemonade offers a calm, happy high that enhances mood and relaxes the body. The initial effect is uplifting and mentally clear, followed by a warm, tension-relieving body buzz. For medical users, Spiked Lemonade strain seeds may be helpful in reducing stress, easing headaches, or supporting restful sleep.

Growing Spiked Lemonade Seeds
These feminized seeds flower in about 8-9 weeks and are suited for both indoor and outdoor setups. Plants respond well to topping and low-stress training, with moderate stretch and high resin output. Thanks to its dense bud structure and unique terpene profile, this strain performs well for solventless extraction.

Why Choose Spiked Lemonade Seeds?
Spiked Lemonade seeds bring citrus zest, sweet flavor, and high-end frost together in a compact, grower-friendly plant. The Peach Lemonade x Winterberry cross offers a rare combination of aesthetics, terpenes, and effects. Grab your 6-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and treat your garden to something truly special.

About the Breeder - Lovin In Her Eyes
Lovin In Her Eyes is a boutique breeder from Colorado known for unique, elegant crosses that focus on flavor, color, and emotional effect. Every release is limited and lovingly selected, with standout hits like Boardwalk Bubba, Midnight Moonlight, and Silver Stream winning over connoisseurs across the country.

What Are Space Time Seeds?
Space Time strain seeds from White Clouds Genetics bring together Winter Storm and Pearl Cadillac in a flavorful, visually stunning feminized hybrid. This cross captures dreamy terps, relaxing effects, and bag appeal that turns heads. Each 6-pack delivers all-female plants bred for quality and potency, making it a smart choice for both home growers and extract artists.

Structure and Appearance
Space Time develops medium-height plants with dense, glistening buds and a classic hybrid structure. Expect thick colas frosted in trichomes with rich purple hues and pink pistils, depending on the phenotype. Its sturdy branches and tight internodal spacing make it great for indoor tents or light-dep runs.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain offers an exotic aroma of sweet floral musk, grape cream soda, and earthy spice. On the inhale, you’ll notice smooth candy terps, while the exhale leaves a faint cool mint or menthol finish. The flavor lingers on the tongue and in the air—ideal for flavor-forward consumers and jar appeal.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Space Time provides a balanced hybrid experience that starts with gentle euphoria and transitions into a soothing, body-calming high. It’s great for evening use, helping with stress, minor pain, and insomnia. Medicinal users may also find benefits for mood support, anxiety, and restlessness.

Growing Space Time at Home
This feminized hybrid performs well in indoor, greenhouse, or controlled outdoor settings. Flowering finishes in 8-9 weeks, with medium-to-high yields and consistent growth patterns. It responds well to training techniques like topping or LST, and its resin output makes it a top choice for hash makers.

Why Choose Space Time Seeds?
Space Time seeds offer a trippy, flavor-rich ride with stunning visual traits and hybrid effects that satisfy both head and body. The pairing of Winter Storm and Pearl Cadillac results in a cultivar that’s ideal for those seeking cosmic flavor, relaxing highs, and elite resin content. Product description
Sodiac Strain Seeds - Umami Seeds (Regular)

What Are Sodiac Seeds?
Sodiac strain seeds by Umami Seeds are a powerhouse cross of Zoda and Sea ’91, bred for high-impact aroma, dense structure, and superior hash yields. This 10-pack of regular seeds includes both male and female plants, making it perfect for breeding projects, pheno hunts, or standout flower runs.
If you’re seeking strong genetics with bold terps and high resin output, Sodiac strain seeds are the perfect pick.

Plant Structure and Appearance
Sodiac plants grow vigorously with medium-to-tall frames and a sturdy, upright structure. Dense, bulbous colas develop early and finish coated in glistening trichomes. Expect dark green foliage, vibrant orange pistils, and striking bag appeal, especially during late flower.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Sodiac’s terpene profile combines Zoda’s fruity funk with Sea ’91’s classic chem and diesel punch. Expect a pungent blend of sweet citrus, fuel, and earthy gas with a hint of sour candy on the back end. This terp profile is bold, layered, and lingers well after the exhale—ideal for extract artists and heavy smokers.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Sodiac seeds produce a powerful, well-balanced high. The onset brings mental stimulation and creativity, followed by a full-body buzz that relaxes without couch lock. Users report relief from tension, stress, and low mood. It’s an excellent option for both recreational and medicinal use.

Growing Sodiac Seeds
These regular seeds flower in 8-9 weeks and perform best in dialed-in indoor or greenhouse setups. Sodiac responds well to training techniques like topping and SCROG. Due to its dense structure and trichome production, this strain is highly recommended for solventless extractions.

Why Choose Sodiac Seeds?
Sodiac seeds offer a perfect mix of funky fruit and classic gas in a reliable, resin-heavy format. The Zoda x Sea ’91 pairing brings together elite breeding lines, making this strain a great addition to any garden. Grab your 10-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and start your next grow with genetics that hit hard and finish loud.

About the Breeder - Umami Seeds
Umami Seeds is a respected U.S.-based breeder focused on flavor-first cannabis with top-tier extraction potential. Known for drops like Sour Zoda, Gas Nana, and Powduh, Umami Seeds continues to deliver elite solventless-friendly genetics for growers and extractors alike.

Silver Stream Strain Seeds - Lovin In Her Eyes (Feminized)

What Are Silver Stream Seeds?
Silver Stream strain seeds by Lovin In Her Eyes combine the creamy dessert terps of Marsh-Mellow #6 with the fruity, frosted beauty of Winterberry. This feminized hybrid delivers eye-catching buds, rich flavor, and a calming, balanced high. Designed for connoisseurs who appreciate terp complexity and trichome-heavy flowers, Silver Stream seeds are perfect for both flower lovers and extractors.
Each 6-pack contains feminized seeds to simplify your grow while maximizing quality and consistency.

Appearance and Plant Structure
Silver Stream grows medium-tall with strong lateral branching and dense, chunky buds. During flowering, plants produce thick trichome layers with icy white resin that sparkles under light. Colorful purple streaks and frosty finishes give Silver Stream standout visual appeal, especially in cooler temps.

Aroma and Flavor Profile
Expect a smooth blend of berries, sweet cream, and soft earth. Marsh-Mellow #6 contributes vanilla and marshmallow undertones, while Winterberry adds ripe fruit and floral gas. Together, these terps create a luxurious, dessert-like experience that lingers on the palate.

Effects and Medicinal Use
The effects of Silver Stream strain seeds are mellow and mentally uplifting. Users report a relaxed, euphoric buzz that eases anxiety, lifts the mood, and calms the body without total sedation. This makes it a great option for evening use, creative sessions, or winding down with friends.

Growing Silver Stream Seeds
These feminized seeds flower in about 8-9 weeks and thrive in both soil and hydro systems. Plants respond well to topping and light defoliation. Growers can expect solid yields, heavy resin production, and a terp-rich flower that’s ideal for smoking, pressing, or washing.

Why Choose Silver Stream Seeds?
Silver Stream seeds are an elegant, boutique choice for growers who appreciate frost, flavor, and soothing effects. The Marsh-Mellow #6 x Winterberry lineage makes this strain uniquely rich in terps and visuals. Add it to your lineup today from Neptune Seed Bank and experience why Lovin In Her Eyes cultivars are so highly sought after.

Every seed is a work of art meant for collectors and flavor chasers alike.

Sake’ Seeds - Sin City Seeds (Feminized)

What Are Sake’ Seeds?
Sake’ seeds by Sin City Seeds offer a deliciously potent cross of Apples & Bananas and Blue Power IX2. This feminized hybrid bursts with fruit-forward flavor, creamy smoothness, and reliable potency. Whether you’re a fan of dessert terps, big resin content, or smooth indica-leaning effects, Sake’ seeds deliver on all fronts.
Available in 3-, 5-, or 7-seed packs, this cultivar is ideal for indoor grows, flavor chasers, and extractors alike.

Plant Appearance and Structure
Sake’ plants grow dense and medium in height, with strong lateral branching and tight internodes. Buds are round, frosty, and often show off purple and light green hues. Thanks to the Blue Power lineage, expect heavy trichome coverage and strong structure—perfect for topping or SCROG setups.

Aroma and Flavor Profile
Crack open a jar, and Sake’ seeds reveal a mouthwatering mix of apple pie, banana cream, and light berry funk. The Apples & Bananas side delivers a sweet, gassy punch, while Blue Power IX2 adds creamy vanilla and kush undertones. Together, they produce a smooth, dessert-style smoke that lingers on the tongue.

Effects and Medicinal Use
The effects begin with a warm cerebral lift that quickly settles into full-body relaxation. Users describe it as soothing yet clear-headed—great for unwinding without total couch-lock. Medical patients often use Sake’ seeds to ease anxiety, minor aches, and mood swings. Because the high is balanced, it works well for both day and evening use.

Growing Sake’ Seeds
These feminized seeds are beginner-friendly and flower in 8-9 weeks. Sake’ thrives in both soil and hydro setups, producing medium-to-heavy yields with minimal effort. The dense buds, high resin content, and uniform structure make this a solid pick for flower and extract production.

Why Choose Sake’ Seeds?
Sake’ seeds bring together two modern powerhouse strains to create a plant that’s flavorful, relaxing, and easy to grow. If you’re looking for a fruit-forward cultivar with creamy undertones and reliable results, this one belongs in your lineup. Order your pack today from Neptune Seed Bank and explore Sin City’s next-level breeding.

About Sin City Seeds
Founded in 2010 in Las Vegas, Sin City Seeds is known for its terpene-rich, hash-friendly strains. From Blue Power IX2 to SinMint Cookies, their lineup is a favorite among pheno hunters and extract artists. Their award-winning genetics have earned spots in national competitions and elite gardens across the country.

Structure and Appearance

Flavor and Aroma Profile

Growing Royal Feast Strain Regular Seeds
This cultivar flowers in 8-9 weeks and performs well in both indoor and outdoor environments. It handles training like a champ and thrives in organic or hydro systems. Due to its dense structure, proper airflow is important to prevent humidity issues.

Why Choose Royal Feast Seeds?

Rocksalts F1 Strain Feminized Seeds - Bred by Romulan Genetics

What Are Rocksalts F1 Strain Feminized Seeds?
Rocksalts F1 feminized seeds by Romulan Genetics combine the tropical punch of Pineapple Express, the sweet heat of Red Hots, and the earthy power of Romulan. This hybrid delivers exotic terps, rich flavor, and a potent body high. The result is a cultivar with old-school structure and modern flavor that stands out in any grow. Each 6-pack includes feminized seeds for a consistent and straightforward cultivation experience.

Structure and Appearance
Rocksalts F1 grows with thick stems, sturdy branches, and a balanced hybrid structure. Buds stack densely and are caked in sticky trichomes by late flower. You’ll notice hues of green, purple, and amber pistils throughout its chunky colas. Because of its Romulan backbone, it adapts well to both indoor and outdoor environments with minimal fuss.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain is loud from start to finish. On the nose, you get waves of ripe pineapple, cinnamon spice, and earthy kush. As you break apart the buds, a deeper musk and peppery gas emerge. The inhale delivers fruit-forward sweetness, while the exhale finishes with herbal spice and rich fuel. For those who love layered terps, Rocksalts brings both heat and sweetness in every hit.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Rocksalts F1 produces a deeply relaxing high with a smooth, euphoric onset. Users describe a clear-headed buzz at first, which slowly eases into a full-body calm. Because of this, it’s great for winding down, relieving stress, or easing tension after a long day. Medicinally, patients may use Rocksalts for anxiety, muscle pain, migraines, or sleep support.

Growing Rocksalts F1 Feminized Seeds
These plants flower in 8-9 weeks and reward growers with dense, sticky buds and pungent aroma. Rocksalts F1 thrives under both LEDs and sunlight, performing well with topping or light training. With strong resistance to mold and pests, it makes a great choice for growers in varying climates. Expect medium-to-high yields and a rich terpene return for extractors.

Why Choose Rocksalts F1 Seeds?
Rocksalts F1 seeds give you a bold mix of spice, fruit, and gas in an easy-to-grow format. Bred by Romulan Genetics, this strain blends the best of both modern and classic genetics. With feminized seeds and standout terps, it’s a must-have for connoisseurs and cultivators alike. Pick up your 6-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and enjoy this flavorful hybrid.

About the Breeder - Romulan Genetics
Romulan Genetics is known for crafting heavy-hitting, therapeutic hybrids with exceptional terpene profiles and rock-solid structure. Their use of classic Romulan genetics—paired with modern flavor lines—has earned them a loyal following. Other fan favorites include Irie Maiden and Electric Lettuce, both of which reflect the same quality found in Rocksalts F1.

What Are Ricky’s Hash Plant Feminized Seeds?
Ricky’s Hash Plant strain seeds from Brothers Grimm Seeds combine legendary genetics to deliver a potent, hash-rich cultivar ideal for extractors and flower lovers alike. Structure and Appearance

Why Choose Ricky’s Hash Plant Seeds?

Flavor and Aroma Profile of Reptar Zereal Strain Seeds

Why Choose Reptar Zereal Seeds?
Reptar Zereal seeds bring unmatched power, flavor, and resin production in a unique genetic combination. Ramune Strain Feminized Seeds by SHUGA

What Are Ramune Seeds?
Ramune strain seeds by SHUGA blend the sharp funk and frost of Ya Hemi with the candy-sweet, gas-kissed complexity of Randylosa, resulting in a feminized hybrid that explodes with flavor, trichomes, and terpene intensity. This 6-pack of all-female seeds delivers consistent, easy-to-grow plants with loud flavor, big resin, and balanced effects—perfect for flavor-forward growers and hashmakers alike.

Structure and Appearance
Ramune grows with a medium-sized, bushy frame and features dense, colorful buds coated in sticky frost. Expect hues of lime green and violet, layered with vibrant pistils and glistening trichomes. Plants respond well to topping and light defoliation, making them ideal for indoor and greenhouse cultivation.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
As the name suggests, Ramune offers bright, bubbly soda terps—think lemon-lime fizz, sour candy, and herbal funk. Ya Hemi brings creamy gas and resin, while Randylosa adds a fruity, exotic backend. The flavor is sweet, fizzy, and smooth on the exhale, making it a standout in both flower and extract form.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Ramune delivers a sativa-leaning hybrid high that starts with a euphoric mental lift and fades into a relaxing body buzz. Ideal for daytime use, creativity, and social sessions, it can help manage stress, fatigue, and mood swings without heavy sedation.

Growing Ramune at Home
This feminized strain flowers in 8-9 weeks and thrives in a variety of environments. It performs well under topping, training, and moderate feeding, producing medium-to-high yields of resin-loaded flower. Its strong trichome production and complex terp profile also make it great for hash and rosin extraction.

Why Choose Ramune Seeds?
Ramune seeds are perfect for growers seeking unique terps, elite resin, and smooth hybrid effects. With standout genetics from Ya Hemi x Randylosa, this release from SHUGA brings soda-shop flavor, serious bag appeal, and performance-driven traits to your garden. Grab your 6-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and taste the fizzy frost.

Why Choose Rainbow Ramune Feminized Seeds?

What Are Queso Dip Feminized Seeds?
Queso Dip strain seeds from Paper Maker Genetix combine the loud, funky profile of F8 Cheetoz with the creamy, dessert-forward notes of Dole Whip. This strain grows compact and sturdy, with broad leaves and short internodes. Buds are dense, round, and absolutely caked in trichomes. Expect vibrant green and orange coloration with hints of purple near harvest.

Flavor and Aroma Profile

Growing Queso Dip Feminized Seeds
With a flowering time of 8-9 weeks, Queso Dip is beginner-friendly and thrives in multiple grow mediums. It responds well to topping and pruning and performs equally well in indoor tents or outdoor gardens. High resin production and unique terps also make it great for extraction.

Why Choose Queso Dip Seeds?
Queso Dip seeds offer savory-sweet flavor, impressive resin content, and strong effects in an easy-to-grow feminized format. Bred by Paper Maker Genetix, this cultivar brings modern flavor and elite structure to any grow. Order your 6-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and experience the funk.

About the Breeder - Paper Maker Genetix

Purple Cadillac Strain Seeds - “42” (Regular Seeds)

What Are Purple Cadillac Seeds?
Purple Cadillac strain seeds by “42” deliver a stunning combination of vibrant color, intense candy flavor, and thick resin production. By crossing Purple Cadillac with the potent and flavorful London Bridge F3, this hybrid offers sweet grape terps, strong structure, and excellent hash potential. Sold as a 12-pack of regular seeds, it’s ideal for growers chasing loud flavor, frost, and rich purple hues.

Structure and Appearance
Purple Cadillac grows with medium height and strong lateral branching. Expect chunky, dense buds coated in thick white trichomes, often flashing shades of purple, blue, and green by late flower. It performs well with topping or training and produces tight internodes that stack beautifully.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain bursts with sweet grape candy, berry syrup, and creamy undertones, making it a standout in any garden or jar. The London Bridge F3 influence adds a fuel-kissed edge, giving Purple Cadillac a rich, layered terp profile that appeals to connoisseurs and extract artists alike.

Effects and Medicinal Use
Purple Cadillac strain seeds produce flower with a relaxing, mellow high that eases the body while keeping the mind at ease. Great for evening sessions, it helps relieve stress, tension, and anxiety without being overly sedating. Users often report an uplifted mood followed by a smooth body melt.

Growing Purple Cadillac Seeds
These regular seeds finish flowering in around 8-9 weeks, with impressive color and frost setting in during the final stages. Purple Cadillac thrives in both indoor and outdoor environments and responds well to light defoliation and feeding. High resin output also makes it an ideal strain for solventless extraction.

Why Choose Purple Cadillac Seeds?
Purple Cadillac seeds offer a rare blend of eye-catching color, bold fruit flavor, and powerful effects. Bred by “42”, this 12-pack is perfect for pheno hunters, flavor chasers, and hashmakers. Get your pack now at Neptune Seed Bank and grow one of the most vibrant strains on the menu.

About the Breeder - “42”
“42” is quickly becoming a go-to name for exotic crosses with elite washability and terpene depth. Known for standout hits like Zesty Drip, Green Crack BX, and Sour Sage OG, this breeder focuses on resin quality and flavor-first breeding.

description:
Product description
In House Genetics - Platinum S2 x Slurricane 44 (Feminized Seeds)
 Key Info
Strain Name: Platinum S2 x Slurricane 44
Dominant Type: Indica-leaning hybrid
Type of Seed: Feminized
Lineage: Platinum S2 x Slurricane 44
Breeder: In House Genetics
Aromas/Flavors: Earthy grape, cookie dough, gas, berries
Effects: Heavy relaxation, mood elevation, full-body relief
Appearance Summary: Dense, resinous, colorful
Detailed Appearance: Compact buds with dense trichome coverage, hints of violet and silver frost, accented by orange pistils
Aroma Summary: Sweet and gassy upfront, shifting to earthy cookie dough when ground
Medicinal Benefits: Stress, pain, insomnia, appetite loss
Growing Info: Best indoors or greenhouse, 8-9 week flowering, moderate stretch, resin-heavy, beginner-friendly



 Overview
Platinum S2 x Slurricane 44 is a powerhouse feminized strain by In House Genetics, crafted for resin collectors and flavor connoisseurs. This cross pairs the frosty appeal and dessert-forward nose of Platinum S2 with the loud, terp-rich profile of Slurricane 44, delivering a top-tier hybrid with stunning bag appeal and heavy effects.
Whether you’re after hash production or evening relaxation, this cross brings the best of both parent strains. Available now in presale format, each pack includes 12 feminized seeds.



 What It Looks Like
Expect tight, chunky buds coated in frost. The colors range from deep olive green to purples and silvers. Pistils pop with orange hues, making trimming easy and attractive. Thanks to its high resin content, this strain glistens from every angle.



 Aroma & Flavor Profile
On first sniff, you’ll get grape and cookie dough with light diesel undertones. Grinding reveals earthy notes layered with sugar and spice. When smoked or vaped, the flavor mirrors the scent—smooth, sweet, and gassy with a rich exhale that lingers.



⚡ Effects & Experience
Platinum S2 x Slurricane 44 hits hard and settles in fast. It starts with a light mental lift before melting into heavy body effects. Ideal for nighttime use, it offers mood elevation and deep physical comfort. Many report strong couchlock, relaxation, and mild euphoria.



 Medicinal Applications
May help relieve:

Chronic stress or anxiety
Trouble sleeping
Appetite suppression
Body aches or muscle spasms

The calming nature and terpene balance make it effective for winding down without mental fog.



 Growing Tips
This strain performs well indoors or in greenhouses. With a flowering time of 8 to 9 weeks, it produces medium to heavy yields. It reacts well to topping and light defoliation. Resin output is high, making it a great option for rosin presses and hashmakers alike.



✨ Why Choose Platinum S2 x Slurricane 44 Seeds?
This new drop from In House Genetics is bred for both performance and flavor.
✅ Perfect for extracts
✅ Bold grape-dough gas profile
✅ Bag appeal that turns heads

PK x Hindu Feminized Strain Seeds - Bred by Freeborn Selections

What Are PK x Hindu Feminized Strain Seeds?
PK x Hindu feminized strain seeds from Freeborn Selections fuse two powerhouse genetics—PK (Purple Kush) and Hindu—to create a deeply calming, hash-friendly hybrid. This feminized strain brings together the floral sweetness of PK with the bold, incense-forward tones of Hindu, offering a well-balanced smoke and dense trichome coverage. Each 10-pack of feminized seeds ensures you get female plants only, optimized for flower and concentrate production.

Structure and Appearance
This hybrid grows short and sturdy, with broad fan leaves and a compact, bushy structure. Buds are round, tightly packed, and completely coated in trichomes. During flowering, you may notice deep purple streaks and a frosty finish that stands out visually and in potency.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect a deliciously rich mix of grape, hash, sweet earth, and sandalwood spice. The PK brings that classic purple sweetness, while Hindu contributes earthy, musky depth and old-school charm. Together, these terps create a flavorful, calming strain that tastes as good as it smells.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
PK x Hindu feminized strain seeds produce flower with strong body effects and tranquil cerebral calm. This strain is ideal for evening use, especially for users seeking relief from stress, anxiety, or chronic tension. Many medicinal users report benefits for sleep support and muscle relaxation.

Growing PK x Hindu Feminized Seeds
With a flowering time of 8 to 9 weeks, PK x Hindu is easy to grow and performs well in small spaces. It thrives in indoor tents or outdoor gardens and responds well to topping and low-stress training. Thanks to its high resin production and stout frame, it’s also a prime candidate for hash making.

Why Choose PK x Hindu Seeds?
PK x Hindu seeds deliver powerful indica effects, heavy frost, and nostalgic kush flavor—all wrapped in a compact, easy-to-grow plant. Bred by Freeborn Selections, this cross combines West Coast legend with heritage Hindu hashplant vigor. Get your 10-pack today at Neptune Seed Bank and elevate your garden with reliable, resin-rich genetics.

About the Breeder - Freeborn Selections
Freeborn Selections, led by Mean Gene from Mendocino, has built a reputation for top-tier terpene profiles, outdoor resilience, and breeder-quality stability. Popular releases like Lime 1 x Jaro F3, Cherry AK x Skycuddler, and Grape Lime Skunk highlight the breeder’s legacy in crafting elite cannabis genetics.

What Are Pinup Purple Strain Seeds?
Pinup Purple strain seeds by Fatcat Labs blend the exotic berry tones of Purple Flamingo with the candy-coated funk of Rainbow Belts. This flavorful, resin-heavy hybrid delivers eye-catching color, sweet terpenes, and a relaxing effect that makes it perfect for evening use. Structure and Appearance
Pinup Purple grows into a medium-height plant with strong lateral branches and tightly packed buds. As it matures, the flowers reveal rich hues of purple, deep green, and orange beneath a thick coat of frost. Its sturdy structure makes it ideal for indoor grows and controlled environments.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This cultivar brings a luscious mix of sweet grape, floral berry, and subtle gas. Purple Flamingo lends bold fruit and lavender notes, while Rainbow Belts enhances the profile with sugary funk and a citrus twist. The result is a fragrant, flavorful smoke that’s perfect for flavor chasers and extract artists alike.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Pinup Purple feminized seeds produce flower known for its calming and mood-lifting effects. The high starts with a smooth head buzz that quickly melts into relaxing body effects. It’s a go-to option for winding down, easing anxiety, or settling into a restful night.

Growing Pinup Purple Feminized Seeds
With a flowering time of 8-9 weeks, Pinup Purple is easy to grow and suitable for a variety of techniques. It thrives in soil, coco, or hydro systems and responds well to topping and light defoliation. Thanks to its dense buds and high trichome production, it’s also a great choice for solventless extraction.

Why Choose Pinup Purple Feminized Seeds?
Pinup Purple feminized seeds offer a striking visual appeal, berry-forward flavor, and balanced hybrid effects in a reliable, easy-to-grow plant. Bred by Fatcat Labs, this release also includes bonus seeds—either Symbiote Sour x Antivenom or Antivenom #43. Product description
Pink Kush x Double Dose Diesel Strain Feminized Seeds by Katsu Seeds
Pink Kush x Double Dose Diesel strain by Katsu Seeds is a high-impact feminized hybrid that merges the sweet floral gas of Pink Kush with the loud fuel-forward power of Double Dose Diesel. Offered in a 6-pack of feminized seeds, this cultivar delivers bag appeal, heavy resin, and knockout effects—perfect for connoisseurs, extractors, and fans of pink gas with a diesel kick.
 Lineage
Pink Kush x Double Dose DieselType: Feminized SeedsPack Size: 6 SeedsDominant Type: Indica-Leaning Hybrid

 Aroma, Flavor & Terpenes
Expect a unique fusion of sweet cream, pink floral kush, sour citrus, and diesel fuel. On the grind, the nose sharpens with notes of skunk, lemon zest, earthy musk, and chem funk, delivering an aggressive and refined terp profile with lingering flavor on the palate.

⚡ Effects & Experience
This strain hits fast with a euphoric, cerebral high, quickly melting into a deep body stone. Best for evening use or heavy relaxation, Pink Kush x Double Dose Diesel is known for mood elevation, muscle relief, and stress reduction. High doses may lead to couchlock—low doses remain mentally smooth and physically calming.

 Growing Info
Pink Kush x Double Dose Diesel strain grows with medium height, strong lateral branching, and dense, frost-heavy flowers, finishing in 8-9 weeks. Buds often display lavender and forest green hues, with pungent aroma and resin-packed calyxes—ideal for solventless extraction or high-end flower. Performs best indoors with moderate training.

 Pink floral kush meets high-octane diesel

Phosphorescent Strain Feminized Seeds by White Clouds Genetics

What Are Phosphorescent Seeds?
Phosphorescent strain seeds by White Clouds Genetics merge Black Velvet and Gary Satan into a bold, resinous hybrid with visually stunning appeal. This feminized cultivar boasts intense coloration, sweet-fuel terps, and a strong, long-lasting high. Each 6-pack includes all-female seeds bred for growers who want potency, beauty, and bag appeal in one plant.

Structure and Appearance
Phosphorescent grows with tight node spacing and produces bulky, frosty colas that radiate shimmer. Expect deep purples, dark greens, and silver trichomes that create an almost glow-in-the-dark appearance under lights. The structure is strong and ideal for topping, training, and indoor setups.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain delivers a complex blend of creamy dessert, diesel fuel, and earthy sweetness. The Black Velvet influence offers smooth berry and floral tones, while Gary Satan brings gassy funk and piney sharpness. On the exhale, expect lingering grape-gas flavor with a slight herbal finish.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Phosphorescent offers a powerful, relaxing high that eases the body and calms the mind. Perfect for evening use, it can help with insomnia, chronic pain, and stress relief. Its mood-lifting properties also make it useful for anxiety or mental fatigue.

Growing Phosphorescent at Home
This feminized hybrid is easy to grow indoors or in a greenhouse, flowering in about 8-9 weeks. Phosphorescent performs best with light defoliation and regular feeding. Its resin-heavy buds are perfect for solventless extraction, making it a great choice for hash artists and rosin producers.

Why Choose Phosphorescent Seeds?
Phosphorescent seeds bring visual firepower, exotic flavor, and knock-out potency all in one pack. The fusion of Gary Satan and Black Velvet creates a strain that’s perfect for growers seeking premium smoke and vibrant bag appeal. Grab your 6-pack of feminized seeds today from Neptune Seed Bank.

description:
Product description
In House Genetics - Permanent Urkle x Slurricane 44 (Feminized Seeds)
 Key Info

Strain Name: Permanent Urkle x Slurricane 44
Dominant Type: Indica-dominant hybrid
Type of Seed: Feminized
Lineage: Permanent Urkle x Slurricane 44
Breeder: In House Genetics
Aromas/Flavors: Grape candy, skunky diesel, earthy funk
Effects: Heavy sedation, calm euphoria, deep body high
Appearance Summary: Frosty, purple, dense
Detailed Appearance: Thick purple nugs with glistening trichomes, tight structure, and bright orange pistils
Aroma Summary: Sweet grape and gas up front, with earthy undertones and a funky aftergrind
Medicinal Benefits: Insomnia, anxiety, pain, muscle tension
Growing Info: Indoor preferred, medium height, 8-9 week flowering, moderate yields, resin-heavy




Overview
Permanent Urkle x Slurricane 44 is a deeply sedating feminized strain from In House Genetics, built for lovers of purple gas and couch-lock potency. This pairing merges the iconic Urkle lineage with the loud and resinous Slurricane 44, resulting in a terp-heavy, purple-forward hybrid that delivers bold flavor and knockout effects.
With a focus on color, aroma, and nighttime impact, this strain stands out in both bag appeal and smoke quality. Each presale pack includes 12 feminized seeds, ready to level up your indoor garden.



What It Looks Like
Expect dense, chunky buds wrapped in layers of frost. Deep purple hues show up mid to late flower, especially under cool night temps. Pistils contrast with burnt orange tones, while the resin production makes it a trichome-rich beauty.



Aroma & Flavor Profile
The scent opens with classic grape candy and sour gas. Breaking it up brings out old-school funk and earthy skunk tones. When smoked, it leans sweet and gassy on the inhale and musky and grounding on the exhale.



⚡ Effects & Experience
This strain is designed for serious wind-down. It starts with a foggy euphoria and quickly transitions to a full-body stone. Ideal for nighttime use, Permanent Urkle x Slurricane 44 promotes couchlock, relaxation, and a sense of physical ease.



Medicinal Applications
Commonly used for:

Insomnia or poor sleep quality
Chronic pain and soreness
Muscle spasms or physical stress
Anxiety and overstimulation

Its sedating profile makes it a great pick for end-of-day relief or patients seeking strong physical effects.



Growing Tips
This cultivar prefers indoor or greenhouse settings. It flourishes with training techniques and good airflow. Flowering time is around 8 to 9 weeks, and it puts out moderate to high resin yields. Cooler temperatures bring out its stunning color and intensify aroma.



✨ Why Choose Permanent Urkle x Slurricane 44 Seeds?
A must-have for purple lovers and heavy hitters alike.
✅ Powerful nighttime effects
✅ Rich purple coloration
✅ Strong grape-fuel nose
✅ Feminized & easy to grow

Product description
Peanut Butter Pie Breath Bx Strain Regular Seeds - Bred by Staefli Farms Genetics

What Are Peanut Butter Pie Breath Bx Regular Seeds?
Peanut Butter Pie Breath Bx strain from Staefli Farms Genetics are a potent backcross of Peanut Butter Pie Breathwith itself and a twist of GMO Mac, resulting in a sticky, loud, and flavorful hybrid. Designed for gas lovers and extract artists, this 10-pack of regular seeds offers a chance to find uniquely potent phenotypes with strong terpene profiles and knockout effects.

Structure and Appearance
This cultivar grows stout and sturdy, with a medium-height frame and heavy lateral branching. Buds are large, dense, and completely drenched in trichomes. Dark green and purple tones come through late in flower, accented by fiery orange pistils and thick frost coverage.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
The terpene profile of this strain is loud and complex—expect roasted peanut butter, savory gas, sweet pie crust, and earthy funk. The backcross intensifies the creamy nuttiness from Peanut Butter Pie Breath, while GMO Mac adds fuel and depth that lingers on the palate.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Peanut Butter Pie Breath Bx seeds produce flower with deeply relaxing effects that calm the body while delivering a euphoric mental buzz. Best suited for nighttime use, it may help with pain relief, insomnia, and chronic stress. Its heavy-handed nature makes it ideal for those with a higher tolerance or seeking full-body sedation.

Growing Peanut Butter Pie Breath Bx Regular Strain
Flowering in about 9 weeks, this strain thrives indoors or outdoors and adapts well to different grow mediums. It responds positively to topping and training and produces high yields of sticky, extract-ready buds. Due to its dense bud structure, good airflow and humidity control are recommended.

Why Choose Peanut Butter Pie Breath Bx Seeds?
Peanut Butter Pie Breath Bx seeds deliver potent gas-forward terps, dense frosty buds, and knockout effects in a regular seed format. Bred by Staefli Farms Genetics, this cross was built for flavor chasers, heavy hitters, and concentrate producers. Get your 10-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and grow something unforgettable.
