What Are Peach Around Strain Regular Seeds?
Peach Around regular seeds by Romulan Genetics bring together the tropical citrus of Tropicana Cookies and the potent body high of Romulan. This indica-leaning hybrid features bold flavors, heavy resin production, and powerful relaxation. It’s a fruit-forward cultivar with depth and structure—perfect for growers who enjoy candy terps with knockout strength. Each 12-pack of regular seeds includes male and female phenos, ideal for breeders and adventurous growers.

Structure and Appearance
Peach Around grows with a strong indica frame—bushy, squat, and dense. The plants develop wide fan leaves, thick stems, and short internodes. Buds form quickly, stacking into heavy colas covered in trichomes. Expect colors that range from deep green to hints of purple, all framed by bright orange hairs and sticky frost.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain explodes with a candy citrus aroma that carries notes of ripe peach, tangerine, and cream. Tropicana Cookies shines with sweet orange terps and sugar, while Romulan adds earth, pine, and depth. On the inhale, you get fresh fruit and cookie sweetness; on the exhale, a mellow herbal-kush finish. The room fills with creamy, fruity funk that’s impossible to ignore.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Peach Around delivers a balanced high that starts with a heady lift and ends in deep body relaxation. Users report mood enhancement, tension relief, and calm focus. It’s ideal for afternoon and evening use, especially when you want to unwind without full sedation. Medicinally, this strain may help with anxiety, mild aches, and insomnia.

Growing Peach Around Regular Seeds
Peach Around flowers in 60-65 days and performs well in both indoor and outdoor gardens. Regular seeds offer pheno variety and breeding potential, with some plants leaning fruity and others showing more gas and density. The strain responds well to topping and light training, and its structure makes it easy to manage in tight spaces. Expect medium-to-heavy yields with high trichome content.

Why Choose Peach Around Seeds?
Peach Around seeds offer unique peachy terps, strong indica effects, and breeding flexibility in a regular seed format. Bred by Romulan Genetics, this Tropicana Cookies x Romulan hybrid stands out for its sweet flavor, color, and potency. Order your 12-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and explore this fruity, frosty powerhouse.

About the Breeder - Romulan Genetics
Romulan Genetics is respected for preserving Romulan’s legendary power while blending it with modern, terp-rich genetics. Their strains like Fudgie F1, Salty Pickle, and Rocksalts F1 showcase flavor, frost, and full-body strength. Each release offers therapeutic value and complex aromas.

Overpower Strain Seeds - Sin City Seeds (Feminized)

What Are Overpower Seeds?
Overpower strain seeds by Sin City Seeds combine the couch-lock power of King Louis XIII with the sweet, creamy terps of Blue Power IX2. This feminized hybrid lives up to its name, delivering heavy sedative effects, thick trichome coverage, and loud aroma. Whether you’re growing for personal stash or concentrate production, Overpower seeds offer elite results in every pack.
Each 3-7 seed pack includes stable, feminized genetics perfect for indoor or outdoor cultivation.

Plant Structure and Appearance
Overpower plants grow stocky and strong, with dense branching and compact internodes. The buds are tight, resin-soaked, and often take on deep green or purple tones late in flower. Expect high yields of sticky, hash-friendly flower with very little fluff.

Flavor and Aroma
This strain boasts a pungent blend of pine, fuel, and earthy kush with creamy vanilla backing. The King Louis XIII side brings heavy OG funk, while Blue Power IX2 adds smooth, sweet undertones. Together, Overpower seeds produce an aroma that’s loud, long-lasting, and unmistakably gas-forward.

Effects and Medical Use
Expect fast-acting, heavy-hitting effects that start in the head and quickly melt into full-body sedation. Ideal for end-of-day use, Overpower promotes deep relaxation and mental calm. Medical users often turn to this strain for relief from chronic pain, insomnia, and high stress. Its potency is best suited for experienced consumers.

Growing Overpower Seeds
These feminized seeds are beginner-friendly but reward careful growers with premium flower. Plants flower in 8-9 weeks and respond well to topping and pruning. Overpower thrives in both soil and hydro setups, and its high trichome density makes it a favorite for hash makers.

Why Choose Overpower Seeds?
Overpower seeds are perfect for fans of gassy, high-impact indicas. With King Louis XIII for potency and Blue Power IX2 for flavor and structure, this strain brings elite-level performance and unforgettable aroma. Get your pack today from Neptune Seed Bank.

About Sin City Seeds
Sin City Seeds is a Las Vegas-based breeder known for small-batch, terp-heavy strains. Founded in 2010, their drops like SinMint Cookies and Blue Power IX2 have won awards and become staples for extract artists and flavor hunters. With a commitment to genetic stability and aroma-rich phenos, Sin City continues to raise the bar.

Optimus Lime strain by Katsu Seeds is a vibrant, citrus-fueled hybrid that merges the zesty spice of Black Lime OG with the sharp, energizing power of Sour Diesel. Offered in a 10-pack of regular seeds, this cultivar delivers a sativa-leaning high, aggressive terpene profile, and extract-worthy resin—perfect for connoisseurs who love loud lime-forward funk.
 Lineage
Black Lime OG x Sour DieselType: Regular SeedsPack Size: 10 SeedsDominant Type: Sativa-Leaning Hybrid

 Aroma, Flavor & Terpenes
Optimus Lime strain bursts with notes of lime zest, pine cleaner, sour gas, cracked pepper, and earthy kush. On the grind, it sharpens into a bold aroma of lime-diesel haze, blending old-school fuel funk with citrus tang. The flavor follows suit, offering a mouth-coating mix of lime candy and diesel fumes.

⚡ Effects & Experience
Expect a fast-hitting cerebral rush that uplifts the mind, boosts focus, and elevates mood. This cultivar is perfect for daytime use, creative sessions, or physical activity, offering clear-headed energy without overstimulation. A light body buzz balances the experience, keeping you grounded while mentally alert.

 Growing Info
Optimus Lime strain grows with a tall, vigorous structure, long internodes, and elongated, trichome-rich buds, finishing in 9-10 weeks. Flowers are frosty, dense, and pungent, making this strain a great option for solventless hash and flavorful flower. Performs best indoors or in greenhouses with vertical space and training techniques.

description:
Product description
In House Genetics - OGKB V2.1 x Slurricane 44 (Feminized Seeds)
 Key Info

Strain Name: OGKB V2.1 x Slurricane 44
Dominant Type: Indica-leaning hybrid
Type of Seed: Feminized
Lineage: OGKB V2.1 x Slurricane 44
Breeder: In House Genetics
Aromas/Flavors: Nutty kush, grape gas, earthy spice, cookie dough
Effects: Potent, sedative, body-heavy, mentally calming
Appearance Summary: Frosty, chunky, colorful
Detailed Appearance: Dark green buds with lavender hints, stacked calyxes, and thick trichome layers
Aroma Summary: Pungent dough and kush before grind; deeper gas and nutty funk post-grind
Medicinal Benefits: Sleep, anxiety, pain, stress, appetite loss
Growing Info: Great for indoor setups, 8-9 week flowering time, high resin output, strong stretch, moderate difficulty




 Overview
OGKB V2.1 x Slurricane 44 is a powerhouse feminized cross from In House Genetics, designed to deliver deep relaxation and bold flavor. OGKB brings creamy cookie notes and knockout potency, while Slurricane 44 adds heavy resin, grape gas, and bag appeal.
This cultivar is made for extractors, nighttime users, and growers who want chunky, frosty buds. Available now in limited 12-seed feminized presale packs.



 What It Looks Like
Expect frosty, dense flowers with dark green bases and purple streaks. Buds are heavily trichome-coated and thick, with a sturdy structure and bold orange pistils.



 Aroma & Flavor Profile
The nose hits with earthy dough and nutty kush, followed by hints of grape and diesel. Grinding brings out deeper notes of spicy funk and creamy sweetness. The smoke is rich and expansive with a dessert-gas finish.



⚡ Effects & Experience
This one hits hard. It kicks off with a cerebral hush and then flows into a full-body melt. Sedating, calming, and long-lasting, it’s ideal for evenings or anyone seeking heavy relief. Some users may find it helpful before bed or during deep relaxation.



 Medicinal Applications
Commonly used for:

Pain relief and body tension
Insomnia or sleep trouble
Anxiety and overthinking
Appetite stimulation and nausea

Its strong indica effects make it a reliable nighttime strain.



 Growing Tips
This cultivar performs best in controlled indoor environments. It stretches during early flower, so early training is recommended. Flowering finishes in 8-9 weeks, producing resin-rich buds ideal for concentrates or top-shelf flower.



✨ Why Choose OGKB V2.1 x Slurricane 44 Seeds?
Heavy flavor, heavy frost, heavy effect.
✅ Cookie gas with grape diesel finish
✅ Resin-rich and potent
✅ Great for solventless extraction
✅ Feminized and limited-run

Growing Ocifer Feminized Seeds

What Are Not Deathstar x Grape Lime Skunk F2 Strain?
Not Deathstar x Grape Lime Skunk F2 Strain from Freeborn Selections bring together two terp-rich cultivars to create a funky, resin-heavy hybrid that’s ideal for extractors and flavor chasers. This regular seed release features Not Deathstar, a variant of the legendary cut, and the F2 generation of Grape Lime Skunk, known for its explosive citrus-fuel nose. Each 10-pack of regular seeds includes a mix of male and female plants, ideal for breeding, pheno hunting, or full-spectrum flower production.

Structure and Appearance
This cultivar tends to grow medium-tall with broad leaves and aggressive lateral branching. Buds form tight and greasy, with deep green to purple tones and extreme trichome coverage. Both parents pass on their stability, making this cross highly grower-friendly for indoor and outdoor setups.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect a loud terp profile of sour grape, lime zest, diesel, and earthy funk. Grape Lime Skunk dominates with zesty fruit and floral notes, while Not Deathstar contributes dense fuel and sweet decay. Together, they create a truly layered flavor with massive nose appeal and lingering aftertaste.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Not Deathstar x Grape Lime Skunk strain seeds produce flower with a potent, relaxing high that lifts the mind before settling into a cozy body buzz. It’s perfect for evening sessions, creative moments, or decompressing after a long day. Medical users often turn to this strain for stress relief, insomnia, and mild physical discomfort.

This hybrid flowers in around 8-9 weeks and performs well in a variety of growing systems. It thrives under both organic and hydro setups and responds well to topping and canopy management. Its heavy resin production and unique terp profile also make it a go-to for hash makers and rosin artists.

Why Choose Not Deathstar x Grape Lime Skunk Seeds?
Not Deathstar x Grape Lime Skunk seeds offer a blend of legacy funk and modern fruit terps in a vigorous, hash-friendly package. Bred by Freeborn Selections, this F2 generation promises diversity in phenos with reliable structure and standout flavor. Pick up your 10-pack of regular seeds now at Neptune Seed Bank.

strain_name: Lovin In Her Eyes - Mystic Martian
description:
Product description
Mystic Martian Strain Seeds - Lovin In Her Eyes (Regular)

What Are Mystic Martian Seeds?
Mystic Martian strain seeds by Lovin In Her Eyes bring together the exotic fusion of Half Pint and Mars Hotel to create an out-of-this-world experience. This regular seed drop features a 15-pack of male and female plants, giving growers the ability to hunt for the perfect pheno or create their own stellar crosses. Expect a mix of heavy frost, berry-forward terps, and mind-expanding effects.
With vibrant visuals and rich aromas, this strain is a cosmic treat for growers and flavor chasers alike.

Appearance and Plant Structure
Mystic Martian Strain Seeds grows with strong, upright structure and beautiful symmetry. Buds form thick and dense with bold color expressions, especially under cooler temps. Trichomes stack early and often, giving the plants a frosty, interstellar glow. This strain performs well in both soil and hydro, with wide branching that’s great for training.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Break apart the buds and experience deep berry funk layered with sweet fuel and creamy undertones. The Half Pintlineage adds a jammy richness, while Mars Hotel contributes gassy cherry and earthy depth. The result is a smooth, bold smoke that satisfies both the sweet tooth and the chem lover.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Mystic Martian seeds produce a hybrid effect that combines uplifted focus with full-body relaxation. Users often report a calm mental state with a happy, euphoric vibe. Medicinally, this strain may help ease anxiety, low mood, or minor aches while still keeping you productive. It’s a great choice for afternoon or evening use.

Growing Mystic Martian Seeds
These regular seeds offer plenty of potential for selection or breeding. Flowering time averages 8-9 weeks. Plants are vigorous and resilient, with a strong immune response to pests and mold. Whether you’re seeking standout flower or making your own crosses, Mystic Martian gives you everything you need.

Why Choose Mystic Martian Seeds?
Mystic Martian seeds combine elite genetics with rich flavor, frosty presentation, and flexible growing. This drop from Lovin In Her Eyes is perfect for those who love variety and quality in one pack. Get your 15-pack of regular seeds now from Neptune Seed Bank and take your next grow to another galaxy.

About the Breeder - Lovin In Her Eyes
Lovin In Her Eyes is a boutique breeder based in Colorado, known for crafting visually stunning, terp-rich cultivars. Each strain is carefully selected for beauty, balance, and aroma. Fan favorites like Silver Stream, Boardwalk Bubba, and Mystic Martian reflect her thoughtful approach and artistic eye.

Product description
Moth Man F2 Strain Auto Feminized Seeds - Bred by Gnome Automatics

What Are Moth Man F2 Auto Feminized Seeds?
Moth Man F2 Strain seeds from Gnome Automatics continue the legacy of one of the most talked-about autoflowers in recent memory. A cross of Black Strap x Coal Miner’s Daughter, this second-generation release brings enhanced stability, deeper color expression, and even louder terpene output. Each pack of 3 or 5 auto feminized seeds also includes a freebie of The Forge, making this a must-have for serious collectors and connoisseurs.

Structure and Appearance
Moth Man F2 grows with a compact structure and dense lateral branching, ideal for tight grow spaces or indoor setups. Expect deep purples, near-black sugar leaves, and glistening trichomes. Its bag appeal is undeniable, especially in colder temps where colors intensify.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
The terpene profile leans into dark berry funk, diesel, and earthy spice. Black Strap’s rich molasses tones pair beautifully with Coal Miner’s Daughter’s gassy, forest-floor depth. The F2 generation boosts both aroma intensity and flavor clarity—perfect for solventless hash or full-flavor flower.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Moth Man F2 seeds produce flower with a balanced high, starting with focused euphoria before gently transitioning into deep relaxation. Medical users often report relief from anxiety, tension, and insomnia. Recreationally, it’s a great strain to unwind with in the evening or on slow weekends.

Growing Moth Man F2 Auto Feminized Seeds
Moth Man F2 finishes in about 70-80 days from sprout and is highly adaptable to both indoor and outdoor conditions. It thrives in soil or hydro setups and requires minimal training. The strain’s dense bud structure, resin output, and stability make it ideal for beginners and hashmakers alike.

Why Choose Moth Man F2 Seeds?
Moth Man F2 seeds are built for growers who want something visually stunning, terpene-rich, and stable. As one of the flagship lines from Gnome Automatics, it combines unique lineage with top-tier autoflower performance. Each purchase comes with a freebie pack of The Forge, adding even more value to your grow. Grab your 3- or 5-pack nowat Neptune Seed Bank.

About the Breeder - Gnome Automatics
Gnome Automatics is redefining autoflower genetics with stable, flavor-packed strains like Bobby’s Widow, Mango Sunrise, and the original Moth Man. Known for innovative pairings and rich terpenes, Gnome’s work stands out among both hobby growers and professionals.

description:
Product description
Mello Nilla Strain Seeds - Square One Genetics (Feminized)

What Are Mello Nilla Seeds?
Mello Nilla strain seeds by Square One Genetics blend the sweet, creamy flavors of Marshmallow OG with the terp-heavy Banana Butter Cups (BBC). This feminized strain delivers smooth vanilla and marshmallow notes with calming effects that settle both the mind and body. Each 5-pack comes with a freebie of Red Hot Violet, a cross of Red Hot Cookies x GRC x BBC.
Whether you’re after unique flavor or relaxing effects, Mello Nilla delivers. It’s easy to grow, resin-rich, and designed to stand out in any garden.

What Mello Nilla Looks Like
Mello Nilla produces medium-height plants with dense, frosty buds. Flowers develop a light green base with creamy yellow undertones and bright orange hairs. The trichome coverage is heavy, especially near harvest, giving the buds a frosted look. Structurally, it’s bushy and well-suited for both topping and SCROG setups.

Aroma and Flavor Profile
Break open the buds and you’ll instantly notice Mello Nilla’s sweet, dessert-like aroma. Expect heavy vanilla, light marshmallow, and a warm buttery finish from the BBC side. As the flowers cure, more creamy notes come through, along with a touch of earth and gas. These terpenes shine in both flower and hash.

Mello Nilla Effects
This strain is known for its mellow, feel-good vibe. It starts with a gentle mental uplift, followed by full-body calm. Many users say it helps quiet the mind without heavy sedation. Because of this balance, Mello Nilla seeds are great for winding down, relaxing after work, or enjoying a peaceful evening.

Medicinal Benefits of Mello Nilla
Medical users may enjoy Mello Nilla for its stress-reducing and muscle-relaxing qualities. It may also ease anxiety or racing thoughts without feeling overwhelming. Those with mild insomnia or mood swings might find some relief too. Its smooth terpene profile makes it a gentle, functional medicinal option.

Growing Mello Nilla at Home
Mello Nilla seeds are beginner-friendly and respond well to various techniques. Flowering finishes in around 8-9 weeks. The plant thrives in both indoor and outdoor environments and adapts well to low-stress training. Expect strong lateral branching and solid yields. Thanks to its frost and terp profile, it’s a great candidate for extraction.

Mello Nilla Strain Seeds Are a Must-Have
Mello Nilla offers creamy vanilla flavor, relaxing effects, and solid yields—all in one feminized seed pack. The cross of Marshmallow OG x BBC brings sweet terps and high resin production to the table. It’s easy to grow, hash-friendly, and pairs perfectly with an evening smoke session. Even better, every pack comes with free Red Hot Violet seeds. Grab your 5-pack today from Neptune Seed Bank.

About the Breeder - Square One Genetics
Square One Genetics, created by breeder THC Titan, is known for unique, flavor-forward crosses and small-batch quality. They run full pheno hunts in indoor, greenhouse, and outdoor settings to ensure consistency and stability. Their drops are heavily tested and highly sought after by craft growers and solventless extractors alike.

Master Kush S1 Strain - Feminized Seeds by Neptune Pharms

Master Kush S1 Strain: A Classic Kush with Modern Power
The Master Kush S1 strain by Neptune Pharms is a feminized version of one of the most trusted indica hybrids of all time. A cross between Hindu Kush and Skunk #1, this selfed line stays true to its original flavor and strength while offering stability and ease for today’s grower. Each 3- or 6-pack of feminized seeds gives you a reliable crop of sticky, resin-heavy plants.

Genetics: Hindu Kush x Skunk #1
This legendary pairing has been popular since the 1990s for good reason:


Hindu Kush brings earthy spice, dense buds, and deep body effects.


Skunk #1 adds vigor, bag appeal, and a funky gas finish.


By creating an S1 version, Neptune Pharms has locked in the most desirable traits—making the Master Kush S1 strain more stable while staying true to the original.

Aroma and Flavor: Earthy, Spicy, and Gassy
Open a jar of Master Kush S1, and you’ll get a bold mix of old-school funk and earthy spice. The flavor is rich and deep, with notes of sandalwood, hash, and a light citrus kick. Because of its gassy finish, this strain is great for smokers who love bold, classic terps.

Effects: Calming, Heavy, and Long-Lasting
The Master Kush S1 strain delivers a strong body high that settles in quickly. At first, you may feel a sense of calm and mental quiet. Soon after, your body will fully relax, making it easier to let go of stress. As a result, this strain is best used at night or during times of deep rest.

Medicinal Benefits: Relief You Can Count On
Medical users often choose the Master Kush S1 strain for pain, insomnia, and anxiety. It may also help with muscle tension and overactive thoughts. Since it doesn’t have an overwhelming head high, it provides clean relief without confusion or paranoia.

How to Grow Master Kush S1
These feminized seeds grow well indoors or outdoors and flower in 8-9 weeks. Plants stay compact with strong lateral branching, making them great for tents, small rooms, or stealth grows. Buds are chunky, resin-packed, and easy to trim. Thanks to its structure and resistance, the Master Kush S1 strain is ideal for beginners and pros alike.

Why Choose Master Kush S1 Feminized Seeds?
If you love classic strains with rich flavor and strong effects, the Master Kush S1 strain is a solid choice. It’s reliable, easy to grow, and delivers top-shelf results every time. Whether you’re looking for old-school gas or medicinal relief, this one checks every box. Order your 3- or 6-pack today at Neptune Seed Bank.

About the Breeder - Neptune Pharms
Neptune Pharms is the in-house breeding team behind Neptune Seed Bank. They specialize in feminized and auto-flower genetics designed for stability, flavor, and ease of use. Known for producing high-quality seeds at scale, they cater to hobby growers and commercial operations alike.

Product description
Marsh-Mellow Seeds - Lovin In Her Eyes (Regular)

What Are Marsh-Mellow Seeds?
Marsh-Mellow strain seeds by Lovin In Her Eyes are regular cannabis seeds bred from Marshmellow OG Bx1 and Stardawg IX. This balanced hybrid brings together creamy, dessert-like terps with classic chem funk and a relaxing, long-lasting high. Each 15-pack of regular seeds gives you the freedom to hunt for keeper males or females, making it perfect for breeding or personal cultivation.
If you’re looking for a terp-rich strain that blends new-school flavor with old-school gas, Marsh-Mellow seeds are a must.

Structure and Appearance
Plants from Marsh-Mellow seeds grow with strong structure and medium height. Expect thick branching and dense, frosty colas by the end of flower. Buds display rich green tones with occasional purple flecks, all coated in a thick blanket of trichomes.

Aroma and Flavor Profile
Open a jar, and you’ll catch sweet vanilla, toasted marshmallow, and sharp diesel. The Marshmellow OG Bx1 offers a creamy, dessert-forward profile, while Stardawg IX adds funky chem, pine, and fuel. Together, they create a flavorful and balanced smoke that lingers pleasantly.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
The high is mellow yet potent—ideal for easing tension, boosting mood, and promoting mental calm. While the initial lift is light and euphoric, the body effects gradually build into a relaxing, full-body buzz. Medical users may appreciate Marsh-Mellow seeds for managing stress, anxiety, and minor aches.

Growing Marsh-Mellow Seeds
These regular seeds thrive indoors or out. Flowering takes about 8-9 weeks. Plants are resilient and respond well to topping or low-stress training. High trichome production also makes Marsh-Mellow an excellent option for hash makers and extract artists.

Why Choose Marsh-Mellow Seeds?
Marsh-Mellow seeds offer unique flavor, heavy resin, and balanced hybrid effects. With a genetic lineage combining Marshmellow OG Bx1 and Stardawg IX, it’s ideal for pheno hunters, breeders, and smokers who appreciate both dessert and gas. description:
Product description
Mars Hotel Seeds - Lovin In Her Eyes (Regular)

What Are Mars Hotel Strain Seeds?
Mars Hotel strain seeds by Lovin In Her Eyes bring together the vibrant fruitiness of Cherry Punch and the funky, gassy power of Stardawg IX. This regular seed release produces a balanced hybrid that leans slightly indica, offering rich flavor, dense frost, and standout color. If you’re hunting for terps, bag appeal, and powerful effects, Mars Hotel seeds deliver all three in every phenotype.
With 15 regular seeds per pack, this drop is perfect for both breeding projects and head stash pheno hunts.

Plant Structure and Appearance
Mars Hotel grows strong, stocky plants with wide, supportive branches. Buds stack tightly along the colas, often finishing with purple highlights and heavy trichome coverage. Expect healthy vigor, uniform growth, and excellent yields under both indoor and outdoor setups.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain is all about loud, layered terps. Cherry Punch contributes bright, candied cherry notes, while Stardawg IXadds heavy gas, chem, and earth. Together, they create a profile that’s sweet on the front and pungent on the back, with a lingering skunky finish.

Effects and Medicinal Use
Mars Hotel strain seeds produce flowers that strike a perfect balance between head and body. The high begins with a clear, uplifting mental effect, then transitions into a warm, relaxing buzz. Many medical users report relief from anxiety, stress, and mood swings without excessive sedation. This makes it a great choice for afternoon or evening use.

Growing Mars Hotel Seeds
These regular seeds flower in about 8-9 weeks and thrive in a variety of conditions. Mars Hotel is an easy-to-grow hybrid with a solid structure and high resistance to pests and mildew. With proper training, growers can expect generous yields of top-tier flower or wash-ready material.

Why Choose Mars Hotel Seeds?
Mars Hotel seeds offer a unique flavor combo of sweet cherries and chemical funk in a grower-friendly format. This is a standout regular release from Lovin In Her Eyes, known for breeding rare and flavor-rich cultivars. Pick up your 15-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and explore your next keeper pheno.

Lovin In Her Eyes is a Colorado-based boutique cannabis breeder known for elegant, exotic genetics and limited-release regular seeds. Limonada Strain Feminized Seeds by Star Fire Genetix

What Are Limonada Seeds?
Limonada strain seeds from Star Fire Genetix combine the zesty brightness of Lemonchello with the creamy tropical depth of Apples and Bananas, creating a feminized hybrid with exotic terps, rich trichome coverage, and well-balanced effects. This flavorful cross is crafted for connoisseurs seeking fruit-forward funk with a potent hybrid kick.

Structure and Appearance
Limonada grows with medium-tall height, showcasing vibrant green foliage, orange hairs, and frosty trichomes that coat each dense cola. With tight internodes and symmetrical branching, it performs beautifully in indoor setups, light-dep greenhouses, or sunny outdoor plots. Expect excellent results with topping and light training.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Limonada’s terpene profile is a standout—lemon candy, tropical cream, sweet gas, and apple zest come together in a loud, lingering aroma. Lemonchello adds tangy brightness and zest, while Apples and Bananas bring creamy complexity and backend power. The flavor is smooth on the inhale and funky on the finish, perfect for flavor lovers.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
This strain delivers a euphoric, upbeat high that gradually eases into relaxation without sedation. Limonada is great for daytime creativity, socializing, or simply enhancing your mood. Medicinal users may find relief from stress, anxiety, and mild fatigue—without sacrificing mental clarity.

Growing Limonada at Home
Limonada flowers in just 8-9 weeks and offers moderate-to-heavy yields of aromatic, resin-rich buds. It thrives in environments with good air circulation and responds well to topping and defoliation during mid-veg. This cultivar is also well-suited for solventless extraction, thanks to its greasy trichome heads and terpene retention.

Why Choose Limonada Seeds?
Limonada seeds offer the best of both parents—tangy citrus terps and creamy fruit funk, paired with hybrid effects that satisfy both daytime and evening users. Bred by Star Fire Genetix, this strain shines in both flavor and finish. Grab your 11-pack of feminized seeds now from Neptune Seed Bank and grow a burst of fruit-fueled potency.

About the Breeder - Star Fire Genetix
Star Fire Genetix is a boutique breeder focused on crafting resin-loaded, terp-rich hybrids built for both flower lovers and extractors. Known for hits like Appleade, their genetics are packed with unique flavor, exceptional potency, and standout bag appeal. Explore more Star Fire Genetix strains.

Product description
Lime 1 x Jaro F3 Strain - Regular Seeds by Freeborn Selections

What Are Lime 1 x Jaro Seeds?
Lime 1 x Jaro strain by Freeborn Selections offer a citrus-soaked, hash-friendly hybrid that shines in both flower and extract form. This regular seed pack contains a cross of two terpene-heavy cultivars: the bold, fruity Lime 1 and the stabilized, flavor-rich Jaro F3. With 10 regular seeds per pack, breeders and growers alike can find standout phenotypes and explore new expressions of lime-forward funk.

Structure and Appearance of Lime 1 x Jaro F3 Strain
This hybrid grows with strong branching and moderate internodal spacing. Plants typically stay medium-height and produce thick, sticky colas that glisten with trichomes. Expect a balanced structure with wide fan leaves, lime-green buds, and hints of purple during later flower stages.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Prepare for a full citrus explosion—lime candy, lemon zest, and a sour floral backnote. Lime 1 delivers a sweet-and-sour punch, while Jaro F3 brings creamy undertones, fuel, and complexity. The terp profile is bright, bold, and loud, making this cross a standout in any garden.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Lime 1 x Jaro F3 Strain Seeds produce flower that leans toward a creative and energetic high, followed by a relaxing but manageable body effect. Great for daytime or social use, it may also assist with focus, stress relief, and low mood. It’s balanced enough to use in the afternoon without heavy sedation.

Growing Lime 1 x Jaro Regular Seeds
This strain flowers in around 9 weeks and performs well in both indoor and outdoor grows. Thanks to the F3 stability from Jaro, plants exhibit uniform growth patterns and great resistance to stress. High resin content and terpene volume also make it a prime choice for solventless hash production.

Why Choose Lime 1 x Jaro Seeds?
Lime 1 x Jaro F3 Strain offer vivid lime terps, balanced effects, and excellent washability in a stable, breeder-friendly package. Developed by Freeborn Selections, this cross is ideal for extract artists, terp lovers, and seed collectors alike. Pick up your 10-pack of regular seeds today from Neptune Seed Bank.

About the Breeder - Freeborn Selections
Freeborn Selections, led by Mean Gene from Mendocino, is known for producing flavor-forward, resilient hybrids that thrive in diverse conditions. Popular releases like Not Deathstar x Grape Lime Skunk, Cherry West x Skycuddler, and PK x Hindu reflect a commitment to top-tier terpene expression and breeding innovation.

Lime 1 x Hindu Strain - Bred by Freeborn Selections



What Are Lime 1 x Hindu Strain?
Lime 1 x Hindu feminized seeds from Freeborn Selections combine the refreshing zest of Lime 1 with the grounding calm of Hindu. This potent hybrid offers an irresistible citrus-hash terp profile, resin-packed buds, and a deeply relaxing high. Each 10-pack of feminized seeds produces all-female plants, ensuring consistent quality and stress-free cultivation.



Appearance and Structure
Lime 1 x Hindu grows short to medium in height with strong lateral branching. The buds are dense, golf ball-sized, and coated in sticky trichomes. As flowering progresses, some plants display purple streaks under the frost, adding visual appeal to its already attractive structure.



Aroma and Flavor Profile
Expect a bold mix of fresh lime peel, creamy pine, and earthy incense. The Lime 1 parent contributes its signature citrus bite, while Hindu grounds it with a smooth, hashy finish. Together, they create a loud aroma and complex flavor that translate beautifully to both flower and concentrates.



Effects and Medicinal Use
This strain is deeply relaxing, starting with a calm euphoria before easing into a full-body melt. It’s ideal for evening use, particularly for those managing anxiety, insomnia, or chronic tension. While powerful, the effects remain clear-headed enough for socializing or creative work in small doses.



How to Grow Lime 1 x Hindu Feminized Seeds
Flowering time averages 8-9 weeks. The plants respond well to topping, light pruning, and LST, thriving in both indoor and outdoor setups. Its dense buds and rich terpene profile also make it a prime choice for solventless hash extraction.



Why Choose Lime 1 x Hindu Seeds?
Lime 1 x Hindu seeds deliver citrus-heavy terps, smooth indica effects, and heavy resin—all in a manageable feminized format. Bred by Freeborn Selections, this hybrid combines unique flavors with functional potency. Grab your 10-pack today at Neptune Seed Bank before this drop disappears.

About the Breeder - Freeborn Selections
Freeborn Selections, headed by Mean Gene from Mendocino, is renowned for unique terpene profiles and genetic stability. Known for elite crosses like Jaro F3, Cherry AK x Skycuddler, and Not Deathstar x Grape Lime Skunk, Freeborn continues to lead the way in quality cannabis genetics.

Product description
Lemon Pupil Strain Feminized Seeds by Mass Medical Strains

What Are Lemon Pupil Seeds?
Lemon Pupil strain seeds from Mass Medical Strains fuse the tangy, citrus-fuel of Kernel Putang with the signature purple funk and spiritual uplift of Star Pupil, creating a feminized hybrid that is flavorful, vibrant, and energetically balanced. This 7-pack of all-female seeds delivers unique expressions of sour lemon zest, floral spice, and sweet gas with the reliability and stability MMS is known for.

Structure and Appearance
Lemon Pupil produces medium-sized plants with a unique and colorful presentation. Expect purple streaks, lime green buds, and heavy resin production, along with classic Star Pupil structure—bushy, sturdy, and symmetrical. It thrives in a variety of environments and is ideal for growers who value unique visual appeal and pungent terpene profiles.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain offers an expressive terpene blend of sharp lemon, earthy pine, floral incense, and pupil funk. Kernel Putang brings tangy citrus and skunk, while Star Pupil enhances it with sweet perfume, spice, and grape musk. The result is bright and complex, both sour and soothing on the exhale.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Lemon Pupil offers a mindful, energetic high with a strong sense of euphoria, focus, and spiritual clarity. It’s great for daytime use, meditation, or creative pursuits. Medicinal users may find it useful for stress relief, anxiety, mood enhancement, and fatigue, without heavy sedation.

Growing Lemon Pupil at Home
This feminized strain flowers in 8-9 weeks and grows well indoors, outdoors, or in greenhouses. Lemon Pupil is easy to grow, resilient, and mold-resistant, with excellent yield potential. Its vigor and beauty make it a great pick for both novice growers and advanced cultivators looking to work with rare and expressive genetics.

Why Choose Lemon Pupil Seeds?
Lemon Pupil seeds offer a vibrant fusion of citrus, purple funk, and uplifting energy in a feminized package. Bred by Mass Medical Strains, this unique cross of Kernel Putang x Star Pupil is perfect for growers who want something flavorful, rare, and emotionally uplifting. Lemon Mamba Strain Seeds - Bred by Fatcat Labs

What Are Lemon Mamba Strain Seeds?
Lemon Mamba feminized seeds by Fatcat Labs fuse the vibrant, candy-rich terps of Rainbow Belts with the slushy citrus punch of Wocky Slush. This mouth-watering hybrid brings bold flavor, strong resin production, and balanced effects in a compact plant. Each 7-pack of feminized seeds offers all-female phenos and includes a bonus freebie—either Antivenom #37 or Symbiote Sour x Antivenom.

Structure and Appearance
Lemon Mamba plants grow medium in height with strong branching and dense internodes. Buds stack tightly and are drenched in frost, often flashing green and purple under layers of trichomes. This strain is easy to manage in tents or greenhouses and performs well with light defoliation and topping.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect a terpene profile bursting with lemon candy, tropical gas, and creamy sweetness. Wocky Slush delivers sharp citrus and icy fruit notes, while Rainbow Belts adds a funky candy backend that sticks to the palate. The result is a rich, balanced flavor ideal for both flower and solventless extraction.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Lemon Mamba feminized seeds produce flower with uplifting cerebral effects followed by a smooth, calming body high. It’s perfect for daytime creativity or early evening relaxation. Medicinal users report relief from stress, low mood, and minor physical discomfort.

Growing Lemon Mamba Strain Seeds
Flowering in just 8-9 weeks, Lemon Mamba grows easily and thrives in both soil and hydro setups. It responds well to training techniques like LST or topping and delivers medium-to-high yields. Resin production is top-notch, making it a strong candidate for rosin or dry sift.

Why Choose Lemon Mamba Feminized Seeds?
Lemon Mamba feminized seeds offer a bold citrus-candy terp profile, easy-growing traits, and reliable feminized performance. Bred by Fatcat Labs, this drop includes a free bonus pack of either Antivenom #37 or Symbiote Sour x Antivenom. Grab your 7-pack of feminized seeds today at Neptune Seed Bank and add some slush to your stash.

About the Breeder - Fatcat Labs
Fatcat Labs continues to gain momentum in the craft cannabis scene by releasing terp-forward, solventless-friendly cultivars. Known for hits like Yankie Rose, Antivenom, and Symbiote Sour, their drops are perfect for both flower connoisseurs and hash lovers.

L.A. Zkittlez F2 Strain Seeds - “42” (Regular Seeds)

What Are L.A. Zkittlez F2 Seeds?
L.A. Zkittlez F2 Strain seeds by breeder “42” offer a stabilized and refined version of the beloved L.A. Zkittlez, which itself is a cross of L.A. Kush and Zkittlez. This 10-pack of regular indica-dominant seeds brings together the fuel-forward funk of L.A. Kush with the tropical candy sweetness of Zkittlez, creating a strain that’s deeply relaxing, terpene-rich, and built for both flower and hash.

Structure and Appearance
This strain grows short and stocky, showcasing classic indica structure with tight internodes and thick, frosty buds. L.A. Zkittlez F2 produces vibrant green nugs with streaks of purple, often dusted in heavy trichomes. The plant responds well to topping and thrives in both small spaces and full canopy setups.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect a sweet and gassy terp profile, blending ripe tropical candy with earthy kush and diesel. On the inhale, it’s fruity and smooth. On the exhale, it hits with a satisfying skunk and sour fuel finish. The scent fills the room and lingers long after you’ve broken down the bud.

Effects and Medicinal Use
L.A. Zkittlez F2 strain seeds produce flower that leans heavily toward deep relaxation and physical calm, making it ideal for nighttime use. Users report relief from anxiety, chronic stress, insomnia, and body aches. The soothing high settles in fast and sticks around, offering a stoney yet functional experience.

Growing L.A. Zkittlez F2 Seeds
These regular seeds finish in about 8-9 weeks and perform well indoors and outdoors. L.A. Zkittlez F2 is easy to manage, mold-resistant, and highly productive with minimal training. Its excellent resin production and terpene profile also make it a favorite among solventless extractors.

Why Choose L.A. Zkittlez F2 Seeds?
L.A. Zkittlez F2 strain seeds give you a refined version of a proven hybrid—with boosted stability, flavor, and bag appeal. Created by breeder “42,” this strain is perfect for indica lovers, pheno hunters, and extract artists looking for candy gas and heavy frost. Kush ‘N Keyz R1 Strain Feminized Seeds - Bred by Floraganix Genetics

What Are Kush ‘N Keyz R1 Strain Feminized Seeds?
Kush ‘N Keyz R1 strain seeds by Floraganix Genetics combine the intense depth of Scarface with the rich potency of Platinum Chimera Breath #16, resulting in a feminized hybrid that stands out for flavor, strength, and yield. This 12-pack also includes a freebie pack of Garlic Dip (Platinum Garlic #3 x Chimera #2) x Truffle Treats, while supplies last. Growers will appreciate its elite pedigree and reliable structure, while smokers enjoy bold effects and unique terpene expressions.

Structure and Appearance
Kush ‘N Keyz R1 grows with a strong, stocky build, forming chunky colas loaded with frost. Its internodal spacing is tight, and the buds develop with a thick layer of trichomes that gleam under the light. As it matures, expect hues of deep green with hints of purple and orange pistils, giving it true bag appeal.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain delivers complex aromas of earthy kush, creamy gas, and funky sweetness. The Scarface lineage brings bold diesel and chem notes, while Platinum Chimera Breath layers in vanilla, spice, and baked goods. Together, they produce a loud, room-filling scent and a rich, flavorful smoke that keeps users coming back.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Kush ‘N Keyz R1 strain seeds produce flower with potent, full-body effects that begin with a euphoric cerebral buzz before melting into soothing relaxation. This strain is great for evening use or whenever deep calm is needed. Medicinal users often turn to it for relief from chronic pain, insomnia, stress, and appetite loss.

Growing Kush ‘N Keyz R1 Feminized Seeds
Flowering in about 8-9 weeks, Kush ‘N Keyz R1 performs well indoors and outdoors. It responds well to topping and SCROG techniques and can handle moderate feedings throughout its life cycle. With dense buds and high resin output, this strain is also a solid choice for hash makers and extract artists.

Why Choose Kush ‘N Keyz R1 Seeds?
Kush ‘N Keyz R1 seeds offer elite genetics, complex flavors, and reliable yields—all in a feminized format. Bred by Floraganix Genetics, this hybrid is perfect for those who value craft cannabis with depth and personality. Product description
In House Genetics - (Juicy J x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44 (Feminized Seeds)
 Key Info

Strain Name: (Juicy J x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44
Dominant Type: Indica-leaning hybrid
Type of Seed: Feminized
Lineage: (Juicy J x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44
Breeder: In House Genetics
Aromas/Flavors: Tropical candy, citrus gas, sweet funk, creamy grape
Effects: Euphoric, relaxing, creative, calming
Appearance Summary: Frosty, vibrant, resin-rich
Detailed Appearance: Neon green and violet buds drenched in trichomes with orange pistils and sugary calyxes
Aroma Summary: Sweet candy and fruit funk on the nose; deeper gas and kush tones emerge when broken down
Medicinal Benefits: Anxiety, stress, appetite loss, mood swings
Growing Info: 8-9 week flowering, moderate stretch, indoor preferred, high resin production




 Overview
(Juicy J x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44 is a flavor-forward, visually stunning hybrid from In House Genetics, bringing together three terp-rich cultivars. Juicy J lends tropical candy and bright fruit notes, Blue Zushi adds exotic citrus funk and color, while Slurricane 44 locks in the resin and calming power.
Perfect for extractors and connoisseur growers, this strain is now available in limited 12-pack feminized seed presale.



 What It Looks Like
Expect showy buds packed with resin, sparkling with trichomes, and showcasing hues of green, purple, and sometimes pink. The structure is tight and conical, with excellent bag appeal and minimal trim waste.



 Aroma & Flavor Profile
This strain hits the nose with bright candy, mango, and orange cream. After grinding, you’ll detect grape gas, herbal kush, and sweet-skunky undertones. The smoke is flavorful and smooth, with a creamy tropical finish.



⚡ Effects & Experience
Expect an uplifting mental buzz followed by relaxing physical waves. Great for mood elevation, chill creative sessions, and stress relief. Balanced enough for early evening use, but heavier doses may lean stoney.



 Medicinal Applications
Common uses include:

Relief from anxiety or social stress
Appetite stimulation
Easing mood swings or irritability
Mild pain and tension relief

This hybrid’s balanced effects are great for medical users needing daytime-to-evening relief.



 Growing Tips
This cultivar prefers controlled indoor environments or greenhouse setups. It responds well to topping and SCROG. Flowering time is 8-9 weeks, with heavy trichome output and moderate stretch.



✨ Why Choose (Juicy J x Blue Zushi) x Slurricane 44 Seeds?
Flavor, frost, and color collide.

What Are Jifflez Regular Seeds?
Jifflez strain seeds by Staefli Farms Genetics combine the fruity explosion of Zkittez with the smooth, cakey flavor of Jiffy Cake to create a dessert-inspired hybrid with huge appeal. These regular seeds come in a 10-pack, offering male and female plants for breeders, extractors, and flavor-focused growers.

Structure and Appearance
Jifflez grows with tight internodes, strong lateral branching, and excellent resin production. Its buds form in dense clusters that sparkle with trichomes and feature a mix of lime green, violet, and deep orange tones. Expect a compact structure with high yield potential when properly trained.

Flavor and Aroma Profile of Jifflez Strain
The terpene profile of Jifflez delivers a sweet and tangy mix of candy fruit, lemon-lime zest, vanilla frosting, and fresh dough. Zkittez brings sugary tropical fruit and rainbow candy terps, while Jiffy Cake balances the profile with creamy smoothness and a rich bakery finish. The result is loud and long-lasting on both nose and palate.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Jifflez seeds produce flower with uplifting mental clarity and gentle body relaxation. It’s great for creative work, light social settings, or daytime use without overwhelming sedation. Many medical users appreciate its mood-boosting qualities and stress-relieving effects.

Growing Jifflez Strain
This cultivar finishes in 8-9 weeks and is well-suited for indoor or outdoor growing. It thrives under various mediums and responds well to topping, LST, and SCROG techniques. Thanks to its strong structure and terpene-rich profile, Jifflez also performs well in extraction-focused gardens.

Why Choose Jifflez Seeds?
Jifflez seeds deliver delicious flavor, colorful buds, and smooth hybrid effects in a grower-friendly regular seed format. Bred by Staefli Farms Genetics, this cultivar stands out for its dessert-forward appeal and easy handling. What Are Jet Fuel OG x Sherbacio Strain Seeds?
Jet Fuel OG x Sherbacio strain seeds by Way2Heady Selections fuse two elite cuts into one powerfully aromatic and potent hybrid. The gassy intensity of Jet Fuel OG meets the creamy, dessert-forward profile of Sherbacio, resulting in a rich, flavorful strain with heavy resin production and strong hybrid effects. Flavor and Aroma Profile
Jet Fuel OG x Sherbacio offers a bold and complex terpene profile featuring sharp jet fuel, earthy pine, creamy gelato, and sweet citrus. The Jet Fuel OG parent brings pungent gas and diesel funk, while Sherbacio smooths the edges with dessert-like richness and light floral notes.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits

It’s an ideal strain for late afternoon or evening use, offering relief from stress, tension, and insomnia. Many users also report improved mood and focus before the heavier effects take hold.

It’s resilient and relatively low-maintenance, making it suitable for intermediate and experienced growers. Why Choose Jet Fuel OG x Sherbacio Seeds?

In House Genetics - Jelly Breath S2 x Slurricane 44 (Feminized Seeds)
Key Info


Strain Name: Jelly Breath S2 x Slurricane 44


Dominant Type: Indica-leaning hybrid


Type of Seed: Feminized


Lineage: Jelly Breath S2 x Slurricane 44


Breeder: In House Genetics


Aromas/Flavors: Grape candy, gas, berries, dough


Effects: Sedative, euphoric, body-melting


Appearance Summary: Frosty, chunky, colorful


Detailed Appearance: Dense buds coated in heavy trichomes, with deep purples, lime greens, and bright orange pistils


Aroma Summary: Sweet berry and grape on the nose, gassy and creamy after the grind


Medicinal Benefits: Insomnia, chronic stress, appetite loss, physical pain


Growing Info: Ideal for indoor grows, medium height, heavy resin, 8-9 week flowering time, beginner to intermediate skill level





Overview
Jelly Breath S2 x Slurricane 44 is a powerhouse feminized hybrid from In House Genetics. It was engineered for flavor chasers and heavy hitters alike. This strain combines the frosty, doughy sweetness of Jelly Breath S2 with the resin-rich, grape-fueled knockout of Slurricane 44.
The result is unforgettable bag appeal and deeply relaxing effects. Expect terpene-heavy flowers with rich coloration. Consequently, it’s a go-to for hashmakers, connoisseurs, and indoor cultivators. They’ll love its performance and shelf presence. Now available for presale in 12 feminized seeds per pack.



What It Looks Like
These buds are frosted out and rock solid. They feature vibrant tones of violet, forest green, and occasional pink hues. The flower structure is tight and resin-drenched—perfect for solventless extractions.
Bright orange pistils thread through the dense calyxes, making this strain a total eye-catcher with excellent trim quality.



Aroma & Flavor Profile
Before the grind, the nose is grape-heavy and candy-like, with hints of fermented berries and dough. Once broken down, expect deeper notes of sweet gas and sugary cream.

⚡ Effects & Experience

Product description
Infatuation Strain Seeds - Sin City Seeds (Feminized)

What Are Infatuation Strain Seeds?
Infatuation seeds from Sin City Seeds are a feminized hybrid combining the sweet funk of Jealousy Bx with the creamy, berry-forward Blue Power IX2. This indica-dominant strain features vibrant colors, heavy resin, and crowd-pleasing effects. Whether you’re growing for flavor, bag appeal, or extract potential, Infatuation seeds offer a premium experience from seed to harvest.
The strain grows strong, flowers fast, and hits hard—all while offering a delicious, dessert-like terpene profile.

Infatuation strain seeds Appearance and Structure
Infatuation produces medium-height plants with strong lateral branches and excellent internode spacing. Buds are dense and heavily frosted, often displaying purple, green, and pink hues by the end of flower. These seeds grow well in both soil and hydro setups and are ideal for trellis or topping.

Aroma and Flavor of Infatuation Seeds
Break apart a cured nug, and you’ll be greeted with a blend of sweet berries, vanilla, and subtle earthy spice. The Blue Power IX2 contributes creamy notes, while the Jealousy Bx side adds complex fuel and candy tones. As a result, Infatuation seeds produce flowers that are both flavorful and loud in aroma.

Infatuation Effects and Benefits
Users often report a euphoric head buzz paired with full-body relaxation. Although the effects lean toward indica, they don’t overwhelm, making this strain ideal for unwinding after work or socializing. For medical users, Infatuation seeds may offer relief from anxiety, minor aches, or mood swings. Because it provides both mental ease and physical calm, it’s a balanced option for any time of day.

Growing Info for Infatuation Seeds
Infatuation seeds are easy to grow and perform well indoors or outdoors. The flowering cycle is typically 55-65 days. Plants exhibit strong vigor in veg and form thick, sticky colas as they flower. With consistent feeding and airflow, growers can expect above-average yields and a solid return in both flower and resin.

Why Choose Infatuation Seeds?
With bold flavor, vibrant color, and balanced effects, Infatuation seeds are a solid choice for cultivators seeking both beauty and strength. The Jealousy Bx x Blue Power IX2 lineage brings depth to every puff and consistency to every harvest. Grab your 3-, 5-, or 7-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and enjoy the best of Sin City genetics.

About Sin City Seeds
Sin City Seeds was founded in 2010 by breeders out of Las Vegas who are committed to creating naturally bred, high-quality strains. Their library now includes over 200 original varieties, including SinMint Cookies, which was named a High Times Top 10 Strain of the Year. The cornerstone of many of their crosses, Blue Power, is known for its creamy, terp-rich profile and beautiful bag appeal.

Blue Power IX2


Beach Truffle


Nuclear Power

Humboldt Pound Cake Strain Feminized Seeds by Humboldt Seed Co

What Are Humboldt Pound Cake Seeds?
Humboldt Pound Cake strain seeds by Humboldt Seed Co merge the massive potency of Notorious THC with the creamy dessert terps of Wedding Cake. This feminized hybrid delivers dense, frosty buds, sweet gassy aroma, and long-lasting hybrid effects. Available in 3- or 5-pack feminized seed options, this strain brings high-end flavor and structure straight to your grow room.

Structure and Appearance
Humboldt Pound Cake grows with a strong, medium-tall frame, forming large, resin-coated colas. Expect tight internodal spacing and thick lateral branches that can hold heavy flower weight. Buds are chunky, bright green with purple accents, coated in a generous layer of trichomes that shimmer under lights.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Prepare for a sweet, creamy inhale layered with gassy undertones and a subtle berry finish. Notorious THC lends deep gas and power, while Wedding Cake contributes its iconic dessert richness and vanilla frosting notes. The smoke is smooth, flavorful, and lingering—ideal for flavor seekers and extractors.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Humboldt Pound Cake produces a balanced hybrid high starting with uplifting mental clarity and sliding into a relaxing, full-body buzz. It’s perfect for evening use, aiding with stress, anxiety, mild pain, and insomnia. A versatile strain that suits social events or solo chill sessions alike.

Growing Humboldt Pound Cake at Home
This feminized strain flowers in 8-9 weeks and thrives in indoor, outdoor, or greenhouse environments. It performs exceptionally well under topping and SCROG setups, producing high yields of terpene-rich, resin-heavy flowers. Mold resistance and vigor make it beginner-friendly but satisfying for experienced growers.

Why Choose Humboldt Pound Cake Seeds?
Humboldt Pound Cake seeds offer the perfect combination of power, dessert terps, and resin production. Bred by Humboldt Seed Co, this cross between Notorious THC and Wedding Cake is made for growers looking for potent, flavorful flowers with incredible bag appeal. Holy Grail S1 feminized seeds from Katsu Seeds revive one of the most iconic strains of the early 2010s. Originally bred by DNA Genetics, the Holy Grail clone-only cut was created by crossing Kosher Kush with OG #18. Katsu has now made it available in seed form for the first time. The terpene profile of Holy Grail S1 is both complex and loud. Expect diesel, pine, citrus, and sweet hash in every jar. On the inhale, the smoke is thick and earthy. On the exhale, however, the flavor shifts to a lingering hashy sweetness.

Available in 3- and 5-pack feminized seed options, it’s a must-have for gardens craving loud terps and quick turnaround.

Structure and Appearance
Hella Jelly grows with a medium-sized, bushy structure, producing dense, colorful buds packed with trichomes. Flowers often showcase hues of lime green, pink, and purple with a glossy frost finish. It’s a strong plant with excellent lateral branching, making it ideal for topping, SCROG, or low-stress training.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain explodes with sweet candy, ripe berries, and tropical fruit aromas, layered over a hint of tart citrus. Very Cherry and Hella Jelly genetics contribute juicy candy-shop flavors, while Notorious T.H.C deepens the terpene profile with gassy-sour undertones. The flavor lingers long after the exhale—perfect for flavor hunters and rosin makers.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Hella Jelly offers an uplifting, energetic head high that transitions into a light, functional body buzz. It’s great for enhancing creativity, socializing, or staying active. Medicinal users may find it helpful for mood support, mild stress relief, and fatigue management without sedation.

Growing Hella Jelly at Home
This feminized strain flowers fast, finishing in just 7-8 weeks. It thrives in indoor, greenhouse, and outdoor grows, demonstrating excellent mold resistance and strong vigor. Hella Jelly is ideal for growers seeking high-quality, high-yielding plants in a shorter-than-average cycle.

Why Choose Hella Jelly Seeds?
Hella Jelly seeds offer a perfect blend of speed, flavor, and energetic effects. Whether you’re growing for top-shelf flower, solventless extracts, or fast production, this hybrid delivers. Bred by Humboldt Seed Co, it’s crafted for those who value candy terps, vibrant buds, and easy growing. Order your 3- or 5-pack of feminized seeds now from Neptune Seed Bank.

Head Mount Strain by Surfr Seeds - Feminized Indica-Dominant Hybrid
The Head Mount Strain by Surfr Seeds blends the tropical zest of Point Break with the funky richness of Redneck Wedding to deliver a flavorful, balanced smoking experience. This feminized Indica-dominant hybrid offers deeply relaxing body effects paired with mental clarity and creative stimulation. Its tall, dense buds shimmer with trichomes and radiate bold citrus and peppery notes. With a quick flowering time of just 8-9 weeks and versatile indoor/outdoor performance, Head Mount is a grower’s dream.

What Head Mount Looks Like
Head Mount grows tall, dense, and absolutely glistens with trichomes. Its olive-green buds occasionally flash golden-orange accents, giving it an eye-catching, oceanic sparkle. The structure remains narrow but stacked, showing off both its sativa heritage and indica density. Whether cured or fresh off the stem, the buds exude a rich, resinous shine that reflects quality craftsmanship.

What Head Mount Smells Like
This strain bursts with the aroma of sweet citrus and tropical fruit, led by sharp limonene and supported by earthy myrcene and floral linalool. Notes of tangerine zest and grapefruit lift the nose, followed by sweet wood and peppery spice. As you break apart the bud, the sour orange rind becomes more prominent and energizing. The scent profile feels bright yet grounded, perfect for day-to-evening use.

Head Mount Effects
Head Mount delivers a euphoric headspace while gently relaxing the body. You may notice an initial uplift in mood and focus, perfect for artistic or thought-driven tasks. As time passes, a calming body buzz rolls in, releasing tension and grounding the mind. Despite its indica lean, Head Mount remains versatile—ideal for both daytime focus and nighttime relaxation.

Medicinal Benefits of Head Mount
Medical cannabis users report Head Mount as helpful for managing stress and anxiety. Its body-calming properties may relieve muscle tension and minor aches. Meanwhile, its mood-boosting and focus-enhancing effects could assist those dealing with depression or ADHD. With balanced effects and a smooth terpene profile, Head Mount offers both comfort and clarity, making it a great choice for evening wellness routines.

How to Grow Head Mount at Home
Head Mount thrives both indoors and outdoors, reaching a modest height of 2.5 to 5 feet. Its flowering cycle wraps up in just 8 to 9 weeks, making it perfect for growers looking for quick, reliable returns. With dense buds and frosty coverage, it performs well under various growing conditions. Its washability and solid structure also make it a great option for hash makers and extract artists.

Why Head Mount Strain Seeds Are the Best
Head Mount seeds from Surfr Seeds offer the best of both worlds—zesty citrus flavor and tranquil, long-lasting effects. The genetic pairing of Point Break and Redneck Wedding brings together trophy-tier flavor and powerful resin production. Its ease of growth and fast turnaround make it a favorite among both hobby growers and experienced cultivators. Whether you’re growing for flavor, potency, or both, Head Mount delivers. Order your feminized Head Mount strain seeds now at Neptune Seed Bank.

Final Thoughts
Thanks for checking out the Head Mount strain! If you’re after a vibrant, citrus-forward hybrid with both mind and body benefits, this one belongs in your garden. Cultivation:
Harlem River Haze is a feminized strain, ensuring a straightforward growing experience. It thrives in both indoor and outdoor environments, rewarding growers with generous yields of high-quality buds. Its resilience and vigor make it a favorite among cultivators seeking a reliable and rewarding harvest.

Green Crack BX Strain Seeds - “42” (Regular Seeds)

What Are Green Crack BX Seeds?
Green Crack BX strain seeds by “42” offer a reimagined version of the legendary sativa-dominant strain Green Crack, now backcrossed with the gas-heavy Animal Face for extra resin, potency, and depth. This 12-pack of regular seeds delivers uplifting, energetic effects with a flavor profile that balances sweet citrus and earthy funk. If you’re after vigor, flavor, and frosty results, Green Crack BX is a top pick.

Structure and Appearance
Green Crack BX grows with classic sativa traits—tall structure, strong branching, and explosive vertical growth during flower. However, thanks to Animal Face, it also develops tight, chunky buds coated in thick trichomes. Expect lime green flowers, fiery orange hairs, and dense coverage perfect for both flower and extract use.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This cross blends the sweet, zesty citrus of Green Crack with the fuel-forward funk of Animal Face. The result is an uplifting terpene mix of lemon-lime, sour pine, and earthy gas with a slightly creamy backend. The flavor is bright and lingers long on the palate and in the jar.

Effects and Medicinal Use
Green Crack BX seeds produce flower with energetic, mood-lifting effects perfect for daytime use. Users report increased focus, motivation, and creativity—ideal for busy schedules or social sessions. Medicinally, it may help with fatigue, depression, and stress while keeping your mind clear and active.

Growing Green Crack BX Seeds
These regular seeds flower in about 8-9 weeks and thrive in indoor and outdoor setups. Green Crack BX is easy to train and stretches during flower, so plan for some extra height. Its resin-rich buds and terp-heavy output make it ideal for both flower markets and extract artists.

Why Choose Green Crack BX Seeds?
Green Crack BX strain seeds offer an energized, citrus-forward hybrid with boosted resin production and modern gas terps. Bred by “42”, this cross brings new life to a classic sativa-dominant strain. Grab your 12-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and enjoy vintage vigor with modern potency.

About the Breeder - “42”
“42” is a rising name in the cannabis breeding world, known for releasing elite, hash-ready genetics like Zesty Drip, Sour Sage OG, and Dole Whip. With an eye for flavor and a focus on quality, “42” continues to drop heat for connoisseurs and cultivators.

Product description
Granddaddy Purple x Chocolate Trip Strain Regular Seeds by Katsu Seeds
Granddaddy Purple x Chocolate Trip strain  by Katsu Seeds is a deep, flavor-packed indica hybrid that pairs the grape syrup and purple glow of Granddaddy Purple with the earthy cocoa and hashy richness of Chocolate Trip. Offered in a 10-pack of regular seeds, this cultivar brings old-school soul with modern frost and structure—perfect for fans of sedating effects, vintage terps, and resin-heavy flowers.
 Lineage
Granddaddy Purple x Chocolate TripType: Regular SeedsPack Size: 10 SeedsDominant Type: Indica-Leaning Hybrid

 Aroma, Flavor & Terpenes
Expect a luscious profile of ripe grape, dark cocoa, incense, and earthy hash, with layers of floral spice and woody sweetness. On the grind, the Chocolate Trip influence adds depth to the classic GDP aroma, resulting in a unique blend of dessert fruit and hashy funk.

⚡ Effects & Experience
This cross delivers a relaxing, body-melting high with a mellow, euphoric head effect—ideal for evening use, deep stress relief, or a restful night. It’s perfect for users seeking potent physical effects, mood elevation, and flavorful smoke that leans classic yet refined.

 Growing Info
Granddaddy Purple x Chocolate Trip strain grows with a medium height and bushy, indica-dominant frame, finishing in 8-9 weeks. Buds are dense, frosty, and often exhibit deep purples and silvers, especially under cooler temperatures. A great option for indoor or greenhouse cultivation with excellent potential for solventless hash production.

Grand Gasoline Strain Seeds - “42” (Feminized)

What Are Grand Gasoline Seeds?
Grand Gasoline strain seeds by “42” deliver a flavorful fusion of Grape Gasoline and Grand Daddy Purple, creating a powerful indica-leaning hybrid with bold terpene expression and deep purple hues. These feminized seeds are perfect for growers who love fruity gas, heavy resin, and stress-melting effects. With elite lineage and stable performance, Grand Gasoline is a must-have for flavor and frost seekers.

Structure and Appearance
Grand Gasoline grows with a compact, bushy frame and thick, sturdy branches. Expect chunky, trichome-covered buds with stunning purple tones and fiery orange pistils. The bag appeal is exceptional, making it a standout in any garden or grow room.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain offers an intense mix of grape candy, earthy gas, and sweet fuel. Grape Gasoline delivers the loud fruity punch, while Grand Daddy Purple adds old-school depth and calming musk. Together, they form a rich and memorable flavor perfect for both smoking and dabbing.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Grand Gasoline strain seeds produce flower with calming, full-body effects. The high starts with a warm head buzz that melts into relaxing physical sedation. It’s ideal for evening use, stress relief, and sleep support. Medicinal users may find it helpful for anxiety, insomnia, and chronic pain.

Growing Grand Gasoline Seeds
These feminized seeds finish flowering in 8-9 weeks and thrive in indoor, greenhouse, or outdoor environments. Grand Gasoline responds well to topping and produces thick resin, making it a great pick for hash makers and extractors.

Why Choose Grand Gasoline Seeds?
Grand Gasoline seeds bring bold flavor, heavy resin, and deep purple color together in one easy-to-grow hybrid. The pairing of Grape Gasoline and Grand Daddy Purple delivers unbeatable taste and a smooth, relaxing high. Pick up your pack today from Neptune Seed Bank and fuel your next harvest with top-tier genetics from “42.”

About the Breeder - “42”
“42” is a boutique cannabis breeder known for flavor-driven crosses and vibrant terpene profiles. With strain drops like Zesty Drip and Sour Sage OG, the “42” lineup has quickly gained attention for quality, consistency, and creative lineage selections.

Product description
Goblin Mode Strain Feminized Seeds by White Clouds Genetics

What Are Goblin Mode Seeds?
Goblin Mode strain seeds from White Clouds Genetics unleash a chaotic hybrid built for terp heads and heavy-hitters. Created by crossing Pablos Revenge with Zombie Storm, this feminized strain combines loud funk, dense frost, and full-body potency. Each 6-pack offers all-female seeds, making it easy to grow sinister flower with maximum aroma and impact.

Structure and Appearance
Goblin Mode grows short and stocky, with a rugged appearance and thick resin-dripping colas. The buds show off deep greens, blackish purples, and frosty white trichomes that give it an eerie shine under grow lights. Its strong lateral branching and tight internodes make it ideal for indoor cultivation.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect an intense gas-and-garlic nose with undertones of fermented fruit and earthy funk. Pablos Revenge brings sharp diesel notes, while Zombie Storm layers in skunky decay and chemical spice. On the palate, it tastes like spiced fuel with hints of sweet rot, appealing to fans of exotic and aggressive terp profiles.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Goblin Mode hits hard and fast, delivering a foggy, euphoric head high followed by deep physical sedation. Great for nighttime use, it may help ease chronic stress, anxiety, tension, and insomnia. While beginners should proceed with caution, seasoned users will love its heavy, therapeutic punch.

Growing Goblin Mode at Home
This feminized strain flowers in 8 to 9 weeks and performs best in controlled indoor or greenhouse environments. It responds well to low-stress training, and its thick structure holds up during late flower. With above-average trichome coverage, Goblin Mode is also a strong choice for solventless hash and live rosin.

Why Choose Goblin Mode Seeds?
Goblin Mode seeds deliver unapologetic terps, crazy frost, and knockout effects bred into one aggressive, easy-to-grow plant. This Pablos Revenge x Zombie Storm cross is loud, bold, and built for fans of gas-heavy cultivars. Grab your 6-pack of feminized seeds today at Neptune Seed Bank and turn your garden into a terp-infested goblin lair.

About the Breeder - White Clouds Genetics
White Clouds Genetics creates unique feminized strains known for their wild flavor profiles, visual appeal, and extraction potential. With hits like Ghost Car, Winter Storm, and Canned Heat, the breeder continues to push boundaries with each new drop. Explore more from White Clouds Genetics now.

Offered in a 10-pack of regular seeds, this cultivar delivers insane terpene intensity, heavy resin production, and mind-altering potency—engineered for extractors, flavor chasers, and true gas lovers.
 Lineage

Product description
Ghost Car Strain Feminized Seeds by White Clouds Genetics

What Are Ghost Car Seeds?
Ghost Car strain seeds from White Clouds Genetics bring together GASper’s haunting funk with the refined elegance of Pearl Cadillac. This feminized hybrid delivers vibrant color, gassy-candy terps, and balanced effects that cater to both casual consumers and hash lovers. Every 6-pack includes all-female seeds, making Ghost Car a dependable choice for your next high-end grow.

Structure and Appearance
Ghost Car grows with a medium build, boasting dense, resin-drenched buds that range in color from dark green to deep violet. Its internodal spacing is tight, and the buds stack nicely into chunky, show-ready colas. Frost covers every inch of the flower, adding a ghostly glow under grow lights.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain bursts with a sweet gas aroma, followed by hints of fruit candy, floral haze, and rubbery skunk. GASper contributes raw fuel and dankness, while Pearl Cadillac brings in smooth, sweet undertones. On the exhale, expect a creamy fuel finish with slight grape notes—perfect for connoisseurs.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Ghost Car offers hybrid effects that start with a mental lift and mood boost, followed by physical calm. Great for creative sessions, chill evenings, or easing into sleep, it also provides relief for anxiety, stress, and minor aches. Medicinal users may appreciate its mild sedation without overwhelming couch-lock.

Growing Ghost Car at Home
This feminized strain flowers in 8 to 9 weeks and thrives in indoor or greenhouse setups. Ghost Car is ideal for growers looking for low-maintenance plants with high resin production. It responds well to topping and training, and performs best in environments with solid airflow.

Why Choose Ghost Car Seeds?
Ghost Car seeds deliver gorgeous buds, flavorful smoke, and reliable results in every garden. The fusion of GASper and Pearl Cadillac produces a top-shelf cultivar with exotic terpene depth and modern bag appeal. Don’t miss your chance to grow this ghosted-out gem—grab your 6-pack today from Neptune Seed Bank.

About the Breeder - White Clouds Genetics
White Clouds Genetics specializes in aesthetic-forward, resin-rich feminized strains built for both extractors and flower lovers. Known for creations like Dragon Blues, Phosphorescent, and Winter Storm, the breeder consistently pushes flavorful, visually striking hybrids into the spotlight. Discover more White Clouds Genetics releases today.

Genius Juice Strain Feminized Seeds - Bred by Brothers Grimm Seeds

What Are Genius Juice Feminized Seeds?
Genius Juice strain seeds by Brothers Grimm Seeds deliver an inspired cross of Gluey and Genius, blending intense euphoria with smooth citrus flavor. This feminized hybrid offers the best of both worlds—fast flowering, potent effects, and exceptional flavor. Each 10-pack of feminized seeds ensures consistency, vigor, and top-shelf flower for connoisseurs and cultivators alike.

Structure and Appearance
Genius Juice plants grow medium-tall with strong branching and an open canopy ideal for indoor lighting. The buds form into chunky, frost-covered colas, often showing a lime-green glow beneath layers of glistening trichomes. This structure supports high yields without sacrificing quality or terpene production.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect a burst of citrus, pine, and earthy sweetness with every inhale. The Genius lineage brings lemony, herbal notes, while Gluey deepens the aroma with creamy fuel and subtle spice. The result is a well-rounded profile that satisfies both casual users and flavor chasers.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Genius Juice seeds produce flower that delivers an uplifting, mentally stimulating high, balanced by mild body relaxation. It’s perfect for daytime use, social settings, or creative tasks. Medicinal users have reported benefits for depression, anxiety, fatigue, and mild pain—all without heavy sedation.

Growing Genius Juice Feminized Seeds
This strain flowers in just 8-9 weeks, making it a fast finisher for growers looking for a quick turnaround. It adapts well to training techniques like topping or SCROG and thrives in soil or hydroponic setups. Thanks to its feminized nature, every plant produces smokable flower, maximizing your garden’s efficiency.

Why Choose Genius Juice Seeds?
Genius Juice strain seeds combine vibrant flavor, functional effects, and stable genetics in one feminized package. Bred by the trusted team at Brothers Grimm Seeds, this hybrid reflects years of elite breeding experience. Grab your 10-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and experience Genius-level clarity.

About the Breeder - Brothers Grimm Seeds
Brothers Grimm Seeds is the renowned breeder behind legendary strains like Cinderella 99, Apollo 13, and Rosetta Stone. Their genetics are famous for stability, speed, and flavor, making them a top choice among home growers and professionals alike.

Gelato Split Strain Seeds - Relentless Genetics (Regular)

What Are Gelato Split Seeds?
Gelato Split strain seeds by Relentless Genetics are a flavorful hybrid created by crossing the dessert-like Gelato 41 with the tropical Banana OG Bx1. This blend results in an incredibly smooth, fruit-forward strain with heavy resin and relaxing, balanced effects. Each pack includes 11 regular seeds, perfect for pheno hunters or breeders chasing rich terp profiles and thick, frosty buds.
If you enjoy creamy banana and sweet gelato terps, Gelato Split seeds will be a treat in every grow.

Structure and Appearance
Gelato Split grows with strong lateral branching and a medium-tall frame, ideal for SCROG or multi-top techniques. Buds are chunky, dense, and coated in trichomes, often expressing shades of purple and lime green with fiery orange hairs. Expect heavy visual appeal and excellent bag appeal from every pheno.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain bursts with creamy gelato, overripe banana, and subtle fuel. The Gelato 41 brings dessert-like sweetness and depth, while Banana OG Bx1 layers in fruity funk and tropical richness. The result is a terpene-rich smoke that’s both smooth and loud—perfect for flavor-forward consumers and extract artists alike.

Effects and Medicinal Use
Gelato Split strain seeds produce flower with balanced effects that begin with a happy, uplifting headspace followed by full-body relaxation. It’s a great choice for stress relief, creative sessions, or social settings. Medicinal users report benefits for anxiety, tension, and minor pain without heavy couchlock.

Growing Gelato Split Seeds
With a flowering time of 60-65 days, this strain offers fast, reliable results. It performs well indoors and outdoors with proper support. These regular seeds offer excellent vigor, making them great for both clone selection and solventless extractions.

Why Choose Gelato Split Seeds?
Gelato Split seeds combine exotic dessert terps, high resin content, and strong structure into a grower-friendly hybrid. This 11-pack of regular seeds is a fantastic pick for anyone seeking standout flavor and chill effects. Order now at Neptune Seed Bank and enjoy a truly premium grow experience.

About the Breeder - Relentless Genetics
Relentless Genetics is a trusted name in craft cannabis breeding. Known for terp-rich and visually stunning hybrids like Cherry Cookies, Trop Cherry, and Strawberry n Cherry, Relentless continues to lead the pack with genetics made for flavor, frost, and function.
