description:
Product description
Gelato Put-In Pop Strain Feminized Seeds - Bred by Detroit Seed Company

What Are Gelato Put-In Pop Strain Feminized Seeds?
Gelato Put-In Pop feminized seeds by Detroit Seed Company bring together two powerhouse strains: Gelato 41 and Red Pop. This indica hybrid is rich in sweet, dessert-like terpenes and produces dense, resin-loaded flowers. With its deep flavor, calming effects, and eye-catching appearance, this strain offers the perfect combination for both flavor chasers and relaxation seekers. Each 6-pack contains all-female seeds for predictable results and an easy growing experience.

Structure and Appearance
This strain grows stocky and strong, with broad leaves and thick stems. Buds form in tight clusters, heavy with trichomes and accented by dark purple hues and orange pistils. Gelato Put-In Pop shows classic indica traits—short internodes, low stretch, and a sturdy build. It’s a great choice for growers working with limited vertical space.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Gelato Put-In Pop is dripping with flavor. It combines the creamy vanilla-gas of Gelato 41 with Red Pop’s fruity soda-pop sweetness. The result is a smooth, dessert-like aroma with notes of berries, dough, and candy. On the exhale, it’s sweet, thick, and slightly earthy—perfect for those who prefer bold, sugary terps.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
This indica strain delivers a heavy, relaxing body high that melts away stress and tension. The experience starts with a euphoric mental lift, then transitions into full-body calm. It’s perfect for evening use, helping with sleep, pain, and anxiety. Medicinal users often choose it for relief from insomnia, chronic pain, and overthinking.

Growing Gelato Put-In Pop Feminized Seeds
Gelato Put-In Pop flowers in around 8-9 weeks. It performs well indoors, especially in soil or coco setups with low humidity during late flower. The plant responds well to topping and pruning, producing dense colas and heavy resin output. With feminized genetics and resilient structure, it’s a solid option for growers of all levels.

Why Choose Gelato Put-In Pop Seeds?
Gelato Put-In Pop seeds offer top-tier genetics, sweet terps, and relaxing indica effects in a grower-friendly format. Bred by Detroit Seed Company, this feminized 6-pack delivers stunning flavor, potent highs, and standout bag appeal. Don’t wait—order now from Neptune Seed Bank and add this frosty dessert to your rotation.

About the Breeder - Detroit Seed Company
Detroit Seed Company is known for flavorful, exotic crosses that focus on loud terpenes and visual appeal. Their standout work with Red Pop hybrids has earned them a dedicated following. Other hits like Carmen Miranda and Candy Fumez show their love for candy-forward, potent flowers. Expect nothing less than top-tier flavor and performance.

Gas Melons strain by Katsu Seeds is a flavor-packed hybrid that fuses the sweet, juicy essence of Watermelon with the sharp, fuel-soaked punch of Sour Diesel. Offered in a 10-pack of regular seeds, this cultivar delivers tropical funk, functional effects, and resin-heavy buds perfect for flower, rosin, or traditional hash.
 Lineage
Watermelon x Sour DieselType: Regular SeedsPack Size: 10 SeedsDominant Type: Hybrid (Sativa-Leaning)

 Aroma, Flavor & Terpenes
Gas Melons strain boasts a vibrant terpene profile of candied watermelon, sour citrus, pine cleaner, and diesel exhaust, rounded out with notes of skunk and herbal spice. On the grind, the nose transforms into a sweet-meets-skunky blast of fruity funk and gas, perfect for connoisseurs and extractors chasing unique profiles.

Gas Melons grows with medium-to-tall structure, vigorous branching, and dense, aromatic buds, finishing in 9-10 weeks. Flowers are frosty, sticky, and colorful, with excellent terp retention and trichome coverage. Ideal for indoor, outdoor, or greenhouse setups and highly recommended for solventless extraction.

Product description
Garlic Budder Strain Feminized Seeds by Humboldt Seed Co

What Are Garlic Budder Seeds?
Garlic Budder strain seeds by Humboldt Seed Co fuse the funky garlic terpene dominance of GMO with the sweet, doughy richness of Fortune Cookie. This feminized hybrid delivers pungent aroma, dense trichome coverage, and knockout potency, making it a standout for flavor chasers and extractors alike. Each 3- or 5-pack includes all-female seeds, ensuring uniformity and ease of cultivation.

Structure and Appearance
Garlic Budder grows into medium to large plants with strong branching and heavy colas. Buds are dense, chunky, and wrapped in a thick coat of trichomes. Expect deep greens and occasional purple flashes late in flower, especially in cooler environments.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain is loud—pure funky garlic, savory herbs, and creamy sweet backing notes. The GMO lineage provides sharp garlic and gas on the nose, while Fortune Cookie adds doughy vanilla and sugar cookie sweetness to balance the profile. On the exhale, it’s rich, savory, and unforgettable.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Garlic Budder delivers powerful, relaxing effects. Expect an initial euphoric mental lift followed by deep body sedation. It’s ideal for nighttime use, perfect for managing chronic pain, anxiety, stress, and insomnia. Its potency and depth also make it a favorite among medicinal users seeking longer-lasting relief.

Growing Garlic Budder at Home
Garlic Budder thrives indoors, outdoors, or in greenhouse setups. It flowers in just 8-9 weeks, making it a quick finisher for a gassy-heavy cultivar. This strain responds well to topping and LST, and its heavy resin production makes it an excellent candidate for solventless extraction or hash making.

Why Choose Garlic Budder Seeds?
Garlic Budder seeds bring together savory funk, sweet richness, and powerhouse effects. Bred by Humboldt Seed Co, this hybrid is perfect for growers who crave loud flavor profiles, heavy resin, and relaxing highs. Order your 3- or 5-pack of feminized seeds today from Neptune Seed Bank and fill your garden with savory greatness.

About the Breeder - Humboldt Seed Co
Humboldt Seed Co is known for creating stable, terpene-intense cannabis varieties like Very Cherry, Blueberry Muffin, and Hella Jelly. They prioritize flavor, potency, and ease of cultivation, making them a go-to breeder for growers worldwide. Browse more Humboldt Seed Co seeds.

Fudgie F1 Strain Feminized Seeds - Bred by Romulan Genetics

What Are Fudgie F1 Strain Feminized Seeds?
Fudgie F1 feminized seeds by Romulan Genetics bring together two heavy hitters: the legendary Romulan and the modern dessert powerhouse, Pure Michigan. This indica-dominant hybrid is loaded with rich flavor, dense structure, and soothing effects. The result is a plant that checks every box—frosty, funky, and full of knockout potential. With 6 feminized seeds per pack, growers can expect consistent performance and vigorous growth.

Structure and Appearance
Fudgie F1 grows low and wide, developing strong lateral branches and thick central colas. Buds form chunky and dense, often expressing shades of forest green, deep purple, and silver-white resin. Thanks to its Romulan lineage, the plant holds its shape well and doesn’t require excessive staking. It’s an ideal choice for both indoor and outdoor setups.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain delivers a mouth-coating mix of sweet chocolate, earthy kush, and gassy undertones. Pure Michigan brings dessert-style terps like creamy vanilla and dank funk, while Romulan adds herbal spice and pine. On the inhale, it tastes sweet and rich; on the exhale, you’ll notice a nutty, kushy finish. The scent lingers in jars, rooms, and rolling trays—loud and unforgettable.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Fudgie F1 delivers a deeply relaxing experience that eases the body and softens the mind. The high sets in quickly with a heady buzz, then melts into a tranquil, full-body calm. Because of its indica profile, many turn to this strain for pain relief, stress management, and evening use. Medicinal users may also find it useful for improving appetite or reducing inflammation.

Growing Fudgie F1 Feminized Seeds
This strain flowers in 8-9 weeks and offers a smooth, manageable growing experience. Fudgie F1 thrives in soil, coco, or hydro, and it responds well to topping and light defoliation. Due to its dense buds, it’s important to maintain airflow during late flower. With the right conditions, growers can expect medium to high yields and premium-quality flower.

Why Choose Fudgie F1 Seeds?
Fudgie F1 seeds deliver the perfect mix of old-school punch and dessert modernity. Bred by Romulan Genetics, this Romulan x Pure Michigan cross offers elite terpenes, powerful effects, and gorgeous bag appeal. Secure your 6-pack today at Neptune Seed Bank and experience the full-body bliss of Fudgie.

About the Breeder - Romulan Genetics
Romulan Genetics has built a loyal following by producing hardy, high-potency strains like Irie Maiden, Electric Lettuce, and Salty Pickle. Their mission is to keep Romulan heritage alive through thoughtful hybridization and consistent breeding practices. Each release packs heavy flavor, effects, and visual fire.

Structure and Appearance

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain brings a burst of cherry candy, citrus zest, and creamy fuel. Cherry Tart delivers a sweet, tangy punch, while Lemon Runtz adds bright lemon and candy funk. Together, they create a rich terpene profile that’s perfect for both smoking and solventless extraction.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Fruity Booty seeds produce flower known for its deeply relaxing and mood-lifting effects. Most users report a calm mental state paired with full-body comfort. It’s ideal for winding down after a long day or for easing mild pain and anxiety. Medical users may find it helpful for stress, muscle soreness, and sleep support.

Growing Fruity Booty Seeds
With a flowering time of 8-9 weeks, Fruity Booty is fast, stable, and easy to manage. It performs well in indoor environments, light dep setups, and greenhouses. High resin content and a terp-rich profile make this strain a favorite for hash makers and extract artists.

Why Choose Fruity Booty Seeds?
Fruity Booty seeds are perfect for growers chasing fruit-forward flavor, indica effects, and solventless quality. Bred by “42”, this cultivar combines old-school structure with loud, modern terps. Flambanger Strain Seeds - Bloom Seed Co. (Regular)

What Are Flambanger Seeds?
Flambanger strain seeds by Bloom Seed Co. combine the decadent, dessert-forward Flambe Mints with the powerful, fuel-heavy Sherbanger to create a gassy, creamy hybrid with bold effects and insane trichome production. This 12-pack of regular seeds is perfect for anyone who loves terp-rich flower, solventless hash, or loud, flavorful buds that stand out in any lineup.
If you’re after a balanced hybrid with top-tier aroma, structure, and potency, Flambanger seeds are a sure bet.

Structure and Appearance
Flambanger plants grow with strong, upright structure and produce thick, sticky colas with deep green and purple hues, accented by vibrant orange pistils. The buds are dense and absolutely caked in trichomes, making them great for both flower and extracts. Expect medium-tall height and excellent response to topping or low-stress training.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
The terpene profile is sweet and gassy, blending creamy mint dessert notes with sour sherb, burnt sugar, and fuel. Flambe Mints brings that sugary, cool inhale, while Sherbanger adds pungent funk and lingering gas on the exhale. Together, they deliver a well-rounded flavor that’s complex, rich, and perfect for terp hunters.

Effects and Medicinal Use
Flambanger strain seeds produce flower that offers a hybrid high—mentally uplifting at first, followed by a relaxing body effect. Ideal for evening use, it eases the mind while keeping the body calm. Medicinal users report help with anxiety, pain, and sleep without the heavy crash some strains bring.

Growing Flambanger Seeds
These regular seeds flower in about 60-65 days and thrive in both indoor and outdoor grows. Flambanger is easy to train, responds well to feeding, and delivers dense, terp-packed buds. Its high resin content makes it a top choice for those producing rosin or bubble hash.

Why Choose Flambanger Seeds?
Flambanger seeds give you the best of both worlds—dessert-style sweetness from Flambe Mints and gassy funk from Sherbanger. Bred by Bloom Seed Co., this 12-pack is ideal for growers chasing big terps, serious resin, and balanced effects. Get yours now at Neptune Seed Bank and experience flavorful fire in your next grow.

About the Breeder - Bloom Seed Co.
Bloom Seed Co. is a premier breeder delivering terp-rich hybrids like Red Runtz, Lemon Vuitton, and Double Tap. Known for elite flavor, hash yields, and consistent phenos, Bloom Seed Co. is a favorite among growers and extract artists.

What Are Fa Nana Strain Feminized Seeds?
Fa Nana strain seeds from Paper Maker Genetix combine the tropical dessert funk of Banana OG with the creamy, exotic terpene profile of Dole Whip. This feminized cross delivers dense flavor, soothing effects, and frost-heavy buds—all wrapped up in a 6-pack of all-female seeds. Structure and Appearance
Fa Nana grows bushy and stout with minimal stretch, making it ideal for smaller tents or discreet outdoor plots. Its buds are fat, resinous, and bright green with golden hues, thanks to its Banana OG lineage. Thick trichome coverage and minimal leaf-to-calyx ratio make trimming easy and efficient.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
The flavor is where Fa Nana shines. Expect a rich profile of ripe banana, vanilla cream, light fuel, and sweet dough. Banana OG provides the tropical funk, while Dole Whip adds smooth dessert vibes. This combo offers one of the most unique terpene profiles in the fruity/dessert category.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Fa Nana seeds produce flower that offers relaxing body effects with a euphoric mental uplift. The high begins with a mellow, cerebral shift before settling into full-body calm. Medicinal users may find relief from anxiety, restlessness, and muscle tension, without being locked to the couch.

Growing Fa Nana Feminized Seeds
This cultivar flowers in 8-9 weeks and thrives in both indoor and outdoor gardens. Its low-stretch, stout structure makes it ideal for Sea of Green setups or compact grow spaces. High resin output and terpene density also make it a strong contender for solventless extraction and rosin pressing.

Why Choose Fa Nana Seeds?
Fa Nana strain seeds offer bold banana flavor, smooth effects, and exceptional resin production. Created by Paper Maker Genetix, this drop stands out for its dessert-forward profile and ease of growth. The effects also move in stages. First, Durban delivers a clear, uplifting energy that suits daytime use. Later, NL5 slows things down with deep muscle relaxation and calm sedation. Therefore, this strain works well for growers who want balance in both mind and body.

Flowering typically takes 9-10 weeks, and yields are high. In addition, trichomes appear early, giving flowers a frosty look by mid-flower. For extractors, resin production makes this hybrid even more appealing.

What Are Dragon Blues Seeds?
Dragon Blues strain seeds by White Clouds Genetics combine the mythical funk of Goblin Mode with the classy terp profile of Pearl Cadillac, creating a feminized strain full of flavor and frost. This hybrid stands out for its grape-gas aroma, vibrant coloration, and powerful effects. Each 6-pack includes feminized seeds, making it a smooth experience for growers seeking standout flower with zero guesswork.

Structure and Appearance
Dragon Blues produces dense, chunky flowers coated in trichomes and often painted in shades of deep blue, violet, and forest green. Its sturdy structure and medium height make it easy to manage indoors, with strong lateral branching and great response to topping. Expect buds that sparkle under light and cure beautifully in jars.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain offers a rich blend of berry candy, gassy funk, and sweet musk. The inhale is smooth and fruity, while the exhale delivers a strong kick of fuel and grape peel. Thanks to the Pearl Cadillac lineage, Dragon Blues maintains refined, balanced terps with high jar appeal and bag presence.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Dragon Blues delivers a calming body buzz with a mellow, uplifting headspace. It’s a great choice for evening use, helping relieve stress, muscle tension, and mood imbalances. Many medical users reach for it to manage insomnia, anxiety, or to simply relax after a long day.

Growing Dragon Blues at Home
This feminized strain is ideal for growers of all skill levels. Flowering completes in 8-9 weeks, with strong resistance to mold and mildew. It performs well in soil or hydro setups, and its resin output makes it excellent for solventless extractions like rosin or bubble hash.

Why Choose Dragon Blues Seeds?
Dragon Blues seeds offer a unique twist on modern gas-forward strains, pairing loud terps with bold color and hybrid balance. Bred by White Clouds Genetics, this cross between Goblin Mode and Pearl Cadillac offers exceptional resin, flavor, and structure in every pack.  Overview
Double Kush Breath x Slurricane 44 by In House Genetics is a sedating, resin-rich hybrid made for kush lovers and terp chasers alike. It pairs the earthy, nutty power of Double Kush Breath with the grape-heavy frost of Slurricane 44, resulting in a cultivar with knockout potency and deep flavor.
Offered in limited 12-seed feminized packs during this exclusive presale.



 What It Looks Like
This strain develops rock-solid nugs that are caked in resin. Expect green buds with occasional purple flecks, dense calyxes, and long fiery pistils. Visual appeal is high, and trimming is straightforward thanks to the tight structure.



 Aroma & Flavor Profile
The terpene profile opens with rich kush and musky earth, layered with sweet nutty dough. After grinding, gas rises to the top, creating a powerful aroma that’s both savory and sweet. The smoke is heavy and full-bodied with a gassy aftertaste.



⚡ Effects & Experience
Expect a relaxing wave that starts in the head and crashes into the body. This is a perfect end-of-day strain—deeply calming, stoney, and physically relieving. Ideal for movie nights, couch sessions, or winding down in quiet environments.



 Medicinal Applications
Helpful for:

Sleep disorders or insomnia
Chronic pain and inflammation
Appetite stimulation
Mental tension or overstimulation

Its heavy body effects are especially suited for night use.



 Growing Tips
Double Kush Breath x Slurricane 44 prefers stable indoor environments. Use topping and training to shape the canopy. Flowering completes in 8-9 weeks, with high trichome output making it a favorite for extractors.

strain_name: Katsu Seeds - Original Diesel x Northern Lights #5
description:
Product description
Buy Original Diesel x Northern Lights #5 Cannabis Seeds - Neptune Seed Bank
Original Diesel x Northern Lights #5 feminized seeds from Katsu Seeds unite two East Coast legends into one powerhouse hybrid. By crossing the high-octane Original Diesel cut with the heavy-hitting Northern Lights #5 clone, this strain produces fuel-soaked buds, sticky resin, and a balanced high that blends speed with sedation.
Key Information


Strain Name: Original Diesel x Northern Lights #5


Lineage: Original Diesel x Northern Lights #5


Seed Type: Feminized Seeds


Seeds Per Pack: 6


Breeder: Katsu Seeds


Flavor, Aroma & Effects
The terpene profile is loud and unforgettable. From the Diesel side, expect sharp gas, burning rubber, and metallic funk. From the NL5 side, however, you’ll notice peppered plum, spice, and earthy depth. Together, the flavors are bold and heavy, cutting through filters and lingering on the palate.
The high is intense and long-lasting. Diesel delivers a fast rush behind the eyes, while Northern Lights grounds the experience with body sedation. As a result, the effects strike hard and settle deep. It’s a strain best suited for evenings when you want to relax, zone out, and stay planted.


Aromas: Fuel, rubber, pepper, earthy plum


Flavors: Gas, spice, bitter funk, metallic notes


Effects: Fast head rush, heavy body stone, immersive, long-lasting


Growing Original Diesel x Northern Lights #5
Growers will appreciate the shorter plant structure and tight internodes from the Northern Lights side. At the same time, the Diesel heritage brings elongated colas and swollen buds. Flowering finishes in about 8-9 weeks, with resin production showing as early as week 6.
Expect dense, greasy flowers with minimal fluff. Yields are solid, and the resin rails make this strain especially appealing for concentrate makers. In addition, the terpene profile is versatile, producing phenotypes that range from citrus-fuel dominant to earthy spice-forward.


Difficulty: Easy to moderate; forgiving genetics


Structure: Short to medium height, tight spacing, swollen buds


Flowering Time: 8-9 weeks


Resin Production: Very high; early trichome coverage


Best Suited For: Indoor or greenhouse grows


Why Choose Original Diesel x Northern Lights #5?


Brings together two legendary East Coast strains


Loud gas terps combined with earthy spice and fruit


Feminized seeds for reliable, female-only plants


Balanced effects that start fast and finish heavy

Crazy Bitch Strain by Surfr Seeds - Sativa-Dominant Hybrid
Crazy Bitch by Surfr Seeds is a lively hybrid created by crossing Inzane in the Membrane with Trophy Wife. As a result, this sativa-leaning strain delivers a boost of energy, creativity, and happiness. It also carries a bold flavor profile packed with sour lemon, pine, and spice. What Crazy Bitch Looks Like

What Crazy Bitch Smells Like
When you open a jar of Crazy Bitch, a sharp lemon smell hits you right away. Then, you’ll notice a mix of earthy herbs, pine, and a hint of spice—thanks to terpenes from both parents. Together, these notes create a bright, fresh scent that sticks with you. If you enjoy bold citrus with a twist, this one delivers.

What It Feels Like

Over time, a light body buzz sets in to help you unwind without slowing you down. This makes it a great pick for daytime use or any moment you need a mental reset.

Medicinal Benefits of Crazy Bitch

Plus, it may reduce light aches and tension without making you sleepy. Since it’s balanced and smooth, many find it useful during daily routines.

How to Grow Crazy Bitch at Home
Growing Crazy Bitch is simple enough for beginners but still rewarding for advanced growers. The plants grow to a medium or tall height and thrive both indoors and outdoors. With just 8 to 9 weeks of flowering, you’ll enjoy quick results and solid yields. To get the best outcome, consider light pruning and good air flow.

Why Crazy Bitch Strain Seeds Are a Great Choice
Crazy Bitch seeds bring together flavor, strength, and easy growing. The mix of Inzane in the Membrane and Trophy Wife creates a unique combo of energy and calm. Structure and Appearance
Coconut Cloud grows bushy and well-structured, making it perfect for topping and training. The buds are light green with hints of lavender and are heavily frosted. Growing Coconut Cloud Seeds
These feminized seeds are easy to manage and respond well to training. The flowering period is about 8-9 weeks. Coconut Cloud does best in controlled environments but can also thrive outdoors with adequate airflow. High trichome output makes it a strong choice for solventless hash.

Why Choose Coconut Cloud Strain Seeds?

Citrus Smash Strain Feminized Seeds - Bred by Paper Maker Genetix

What Are Citrus Smash Feminized Seeds?
Citrus Smash strain seeds from Paper Maker Genetix are a flavorful, feel-good hybrid made by crossing Tangie S1 with the tropical creaminess of Dole Whip. This feminized cross brings the best of sweet citrus and exotic dessert terps into one vibrant package. Each 6-pack of feminized seeds produces all-female plants ideal for growers who want reliable structure and standout aroma.

Structure and Appearance
Citrus Smash grows medium-tall with great branching and sturdy colas. Its buds are chunky and heavily frosted, often glowing with orange pistils and lime-green hues. The structure is ideal for SCROG setups or outdoor canopies where airflow and light penetration matter.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
The terp profile bursts with fresh tangerine, pineapple, vanilla cream, and sweet gas. Tangie S1 brings citrus-forward energy, while Dole Whip adds creamy backend notes that mellow the sharpness. As a result, Citrus Smash smells like a fruit smoothie with a slightly gassy twist.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Citrus Smash seeds produce flower that leans toward a euphoric, social, and energetic high. The uplifting effects hit quickly and make this cultivar perfect for daytime use, creative work, or outdoor activities. Medical users report improved mood, increased focus, and relief from anxiety without couch lock.

Growing Citrus Smash Feminized Seeds
Expect flowering in about 8-9 weeks, with robust yields and easy-to-train structure. This cultivar does well in both soil and hydro, and it reacts well to topping and low-stress training. Because of its resin production and terpene density, it’s also a great option for hash and rosin extraction.

Why Choose Citrus Smash Seeds?
Citrus Smash seeds offer intense flavor, strong effects, and hassle-free growing. Whether you’re a citrus terp fanatic or just looking for a fast-finishing, productive hybrid, this cross delivers. Pick up your 6-pack of feminized seeds now at Neptune Seed Bank and smash your next harvest.

About the Breeder - Paper Maker Genetix
Paper Maker Genetix is an up-and-coming craft breeder known for flavorful, high-yielding crosses with modern appeal. Focused on combining dessert terps and exotic fruit lines, their work delivers on flavor, structure, and bag appeal. Watch out for future drops from Paper Maker on Neptune Seed Bank.

Cinderella Purple Strain Feminized Seeds - Bred by Brothers Grimm Seeds

What Are Cinderella Purple Feminized Seeds?
Cinderella Purple strain feminized seeds by Brothers Grimm Seeds combine the best traits of two iconic strains—Purple Urkle and Cinderella 99. The result is a colorful, flavor-heavy hybrid that finishes fast and hits hard. Expect a sativa-leaning experience with body-lightening effects and strong euphoric elevation. Each pack includes 10 feminized seeds, ensuring consistent and reliable female plants for every grow.

Structure and Appearance
Cinderella Purple grows with moderate height and excellent branching, ideal for both topping and training. Buds develop dense and resinous, showing off deep purple hues from the Urkle parent and a glistening coat of trichomes from C99. Bright orange pistils contrast against the dark foliage, making for bag appeal that’s second to none. Its structure adapts well to indoor setups, especially SCROG or LST techniques.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain is a flavor-forward hybrid, offering a mouthwatering mix of grape, berry, and citrus. Purple Urkle lends its signature sweet grape and earthy funk, while Cinderella 99 contributes tropical fruit, pineapple, and tangy sharpness. The aroma is loud and lingers, blending sweet candy notes with a subtle herbal finish. It’s a crowd-pleaser for connoisseurs who crave complex terpene profiles.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Cinderella Purple delivers a euphoric, mentally engaging high that pairs well with social settings, artistic work, or mood lifting. It brings clear-headed energy at first, followed by a gentle, relaxing comedown that doesn’t sedate. Medicinal users turn to this strain for relief from depression, anxiety, and creative block. Its balanced nature also makes it helpful for light pain and fatigue.

Growing Cinderella Purple Feminized Seeds
With a fast flowering time of 8-9 weeks, Cinderella Purple offers speed and color in one reliable package. It performs exceptionally well in controlled indoor environments but can also thrive outdoors in temperate climates. Plants respond well to topping and training, with strong lateral branching and good resistance to mold and mildew. Expect medium to high yields of premium, frosty purple flower.

Why Choose Cinderella Purple Seeds?
Cinderella Purple seeds bring together bold flavor, rich color, and sativa-forward effects in a grower-friendly feminized format. Bred by Brothers Grimm Seeds, this hybrid combines legendary genetics into a dependable performer that delivers top-shelf results. Grab your 10-pack today from Neptune Seed Bank and add vibrant power to your garden.

About the Breeder - Brothers Grimm Seeds
Brothers Grimm Seeds is celebrated for stable, high-performance hybrids like Cinderella 99, Apollo 13, and Rosetta Stone. Known for precision breeding and top-tier terpene development, they’ve built a global reputation for quality and innovation. Explore more of their strains like Genius Juice and Durban Thai x C99 at Neptune Seed Bank.

description:
Product description
Cherry West x Skycuddler Double Kush F3 - Regular Seeds by Freeborn Selections

What Are Cherry West x Skycuddler Seeds?
Cherry West x Skycuddler Double Kush F3 seeds by Freeborn Selections fuse the bold cherry and diesel funk of Cherry West with the creamy, structured hash plant lineage of Skycuddler Double Kush F3. This regular seed drop offers a unique opportunity for pheno hunting or breeding, thanks to its depth of flavor and strong growth traits. Each 10-pack of regular seeds includes both male and female plants for full exploration.

Structure and Appearance
This hybrid grows with a strong central stalk and lateral branches, creating a well-balanced canopy. The buds are medium-sized, sticky, and dense with thick calyxes and deep green coloration. Purple hues may emerge late in flower, especially under cooler temps.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect a strong bouquet of ripe cherry, diesel fuel, vanilla cream, and earthy kush. Cherry West contributes bright fruit and gassy funk, while Skycuddler layers in smooth hash and floral notes. The result is a terpene-rich profile that’s perfect for extract artists and flavor connoisseurs.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Cherry West x Skycuddler seeds typically produce hybrid effects with a creative lift and deep relaxation. The high starts off with a cheerful mood shift, then eases into a mellow, full-body buzz. Many users report benefits for stress, anxiety, and tension, without overwhelming sedation.

Growing Cherry West x Skycuddler Double Kush F3
This cultivar finishes in about 8-9 weeks and performs well indoors or out. The F3 lineage brings increased stability, while Cherry West adds vigor and stretch. It responds well to training and defoliation and is known to produce above-average resin content.

Why Choose Cherry West x Skycuddler Seeds?
Cherry West x Skycuddler seeds deliver powerful terps, calming effects, and easy-to-grow structure in a regular seed format. Bred by Freeborn Selections, this hybrid is perfect for growers looking to explore a unique fusion of cherry funk and kush hashiness. Order your 10-pack today at Neptune Seed Bank while supplies last.

About the Breeder - Freeborn Selections
Freeborn Selections, founded by Mean Gene from Mendocino, is a respected name in craft cannabis breeding. Known for cultivars like Lime 1 x Jaro F3, Not Deathstar x Grape Lime Skunk, and Cherry AK x Skycuddler, the brand consistently delivers strains with powerful aroma, structure, and stability.

Product description
CapJunky x Sherbacio Strain Seeds - Bred by Way2Heady Selections

What Are CapJunky x Sherbacio Strain Seeds?
CapJunky x Sherbacio strain seeds from Way2Heady Selections bring together two powerhouse strains known for flavor, frost, and resin. This feminized hybrid combines the loud, funky funk of CapJunky with the dessert-forward sweetness of Sherbacio, creating a cultivar rich in aroma, color, and potency. Each 6-pack of feminized seeds produces all-female plants, perfect for reliable indoor or outdoor cultivation.

Structure and Appearance
Plants grow medium-tall with strong stems and tight internodes. Expect dense, resin-coated nugs with hues ranging from deep forest green to lavender. Trichome coverage is heavy, making this cultivar ideal for both flower and extraction.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This cross delivers a bold terpene profile of gassy funk, sour candy, creamy gelato, and earthy pine. CapJunky brings sharp, skunky gas and sweet funk, while Sherbacio softens the profile with smooth, dessert-like notes. The aroma is intense, complex, and long-lasting.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
CapJunky x Sherbacio seeds produce flower with a balanced hybrid high—cerebral and uplifting at first, then relaxing and mellow. It’s great for easing tension, sparking creativity, or winding down after a long day. Medicinal users may find relief from anxiety, minor pain, or low mood.

Growing CapJunky x Sherbacio Feminized Seeds
Flowering in 8-9 weeks, this strain performs best in well-lit, well-ventilated grow rooms. It handles training well and rewards patient growers with large, frosty colas. Resin production is top-tier, making this a great pick for solventless extraction.

Why Choose CapJunky x Sherbacio Seeds?
CapJunky x Sherbacio seeds deliver elite genetics, explosive terps, and potent hybrid effects. Bred by Way2Heady Selections, this cultivar is perfect for those chasing both flavor and potency. Pick up your 6-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank while supplies last.

About the Breeder - Way2Heady Selections
Way2Heady Selections creates modern feminized cannabis genetics designed for flower quality, flavor, and extraction. Known for strains like White Runtz x Sherbacio and Permanent Marker hybrids, their drops consistently meet the demands of connoisseurs and commercial growers.

Canned Heat Strain Feminized Seeds by White Clouds Genetics

What Are Canned Heat Seeds?
Canned Heat strain seeds by White Clouds Genetics combine the potent trichome production of Tricho Jordan with the rich, gassy smoothness of Pearl Cadillac. This feminized hybrid delivers top-tier resin output, vibrant visual appeal, and complex flavor, making it a must-have for extractors and connoisseurs alike. Each 6-pack includes all-female seeds, ensuring an easy, consistent grow every time.

Structure and Appearance
Canned Heat grows with a strong, compact frame and develops dense, frosty buds that shine under grow lights. Expect colors ranging from forest green to deep violet, often accented with bright orange pistils. The plant forms thick colas with tight internodal spacing and a resin-heavy finish, perfect for hash making.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain delivers a rich and layered terp profile, combining creamy fuel, floral earth, and subtle berry undertones. Tricho Jordan brings the loud, sticky gas while Pearl Cadillac contributes smooth, sweet depth. The result is a jar-popping aroma with lingering flavor on both inhale and exhale.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Canned Heat offers balanced hybrid effects, providing a creative headspace followed by relaxing body effects. Ideal for both daytime focus and evening wind-downs, it may help with stress, anxiety, muscle soreness, and mental fatigue. Medical users love its calming properties paired with mood enhancement.

Growing Canned Heat at Home
This strain flowers in 8-9 weeks and adapts well to indoor, greenhouse, or light-dep environments. It performs beautifully in soil or hydroponics, with low-maintenance care and heavy trichome coverage ideal for solventless extraction. Growers should expect moderate height, strong branching, and easy harvests.

Why Choose Canned Heat Seeds?
Canned Heat seeds deliver elite hash performance, flavor complexity, and striking bag appeal in a dependable feminized format. Bred by White Clouds Genetics, this cross of Tricho Jordan x Pearl Cadillac is ideal for those chasing terp-rich frost and heady yet functional effects. description:
Product description
Bubble’s Blueberry F4 Strain Feminized Seeds by Brothers Grimm Seeds

What Are Bubble’s Blueberry F4 Seeds?
Bubble’s Blueberry F4 strain seeds are a feminized, fourth-generation stabilized line created by Brothers Grimm Seeds using DJ Short’s original Blueberry F3 stock. This cultivar was refined over multiple generations to lock in the classic blueberry flavor, sweet floral aromas, and consistent structure. Each pack includes 9 feminized seeds, offering growers an all-female, fruit-forward garden with exceptional flavor and nostalgia.

Structure and Appearance
Bubble’s Blueberry F4 develops into medium-height plants with strong lateral branching and dense, rounded buds. The flowers often display lavender and violet tones, especially under cooler temps, and are coated in a thick frost layer. This stabilized version shows excellent uniformity, making pheno hunting easy and rewarding.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
As expected from its Blueberry lineage, this strain is bursting with sweet berry terps, backed by notes of grape candy, floral perfume, and earthy kush. The aroma intensifies during the cure and stays rich throughout the entire smoke session. It’s one of the best representations of old-school fruit-forward cannabis in feminized form.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Bubble’s Blueberry F4 delivers a calming, joyful high that’s great for day or night use, depending on dose. Expect a relaxing body buzz paired with uplifting mood effects, perfect for stress relief, anxiety management, or simply unwinding. Medicinal users appreciate its gentle onset and manageable mental effects.

Growing Bubble’s Blueberry F4 at Home
These feminized seeds perform well in indoor tents, greenhouses, and outdoor setups. Flowering completes in 8-9 weeks, and the plants respond well to topping and light pruning. Known for moderate-to-high yields and bag appeal, this strain is a great choice for personal and small-scale commercial gardens.

Why Choose Bubble’s Blueberry F4 Seeds?
If you’re hunting for true-blue blueberry terps in feminized form, Bubble’s Blueberry F4 seeds by Brothers Grimm are the ticket. With stabilized traits, nostalgic flavor, and consistent growth, this line brings old-school charm with new-school reliability. Grab your 9-pack today from Neptune Seed Bank and grow something timeless.

About the Breeder - Brothers Grimm Seeds
Brothers Grimm Seeds has long been celebrated for their precision breeding and legendary cultivars like Cinderella 99 and Rosetta Stone. With decades of experience and access to rare clone-only genetics, they create stable, high-performing strains that deliver both flavor and power. Explore the full Brothers Grimm lineup now.

Breadstix Strain Regular Seeds - Bred by Staefli Farms Genetics

What Are Breadstix Strain Regular Seeds?
Breadstix seeds by Staefli Farms Genetics bring together two powerhouse flavor profiles—Garlic Bread and Jiffy Cake—to create a savory-sweet hybrid that delivers in both flavor and function. These regular seeds come in a 10-pack, offering male and female phenotypes for breeders, pheno hunters, and growers looking for variety and expression.

Structure and Appearance
Breadstix plants grow stocky and uniform, with tight internodal spacing and hearty lateral branches. Buds are chunky and heavily frosted, often showing light greens with golden tones. Its sturdy structure and compact growth make it perfect for indoor tents or dialed-in outdoor grows.

Flavor and Aroma Profile of Breadstix Strain
The terpene profile is where Breadstix shines. You’ll find a savory mix of garlic, dough, buttered toast, and sweet vanilla cake. Garlic Bread brings pungent depth, while Jiffy Cake layers in sugary smoothness and bakery-shop sweetness. Together, they create an unmistakable, crave-worthy aroma.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Breadstix strain seeds produce flower that offers calming, body-focused effects with mild euphoria. It’s great for evening relaxation, appetite stimulation, or simply winding down. Medical users may appreciate its ability to ease physical discomfort, insomnia, or chronic stress without overwhelming sedation.

Growing Breadstix Seeds
Breadstix finishes in 8-9 weeks and adapts easily to various environments. It thrives in organic soil, coco, or hydro setups and responds well to topping and shaping. Due to its high resin production and savory terpene blend, it’s a solid pick for solventless extraction and rosin.

Why Choose Breadstix Strain Seeds?
Breadstix seeds offer unique flavor, reliable growth, and heavy resin—all in a regular seed format. Bred by Staefli Farms Genetics, this cross stands out for its balance of savory and sweet with strong structure and terp appeal. Order your 10-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and take your grow menu in a delicious new direction.

About the Breeder - Staefli Farms Genetics
Staefli Farms Genetics is known for crafting bold terpene-forward hybrids that deliver on flavor, yield, and vigor. With crosses like Apricot Mimosa F2 and Breadstix, their work brings together modern potency with distinctive profiles perfect for hash makers and connoisseurs.

 Key Info

Strain Name: Blue Skunk x Slurricane 44
Dominant Type: Indica-dominant hybrid
Type of Seed: Feminized
Lineage: Blue Skunk x Slurricane 44
Breeder: In House Genetics
Aromas/Flavors: Funky skunk, berry, sour fuel, earthy sweetness
Effects: Relaxing, sedative, mentally hazy, mood-enhancing
Appearance Summary: Colorful, sticky, trichome-rich
Detailed Appearance: Chunky nugs with dark green and violet hues, amber pistils, and a sugary trichome glaze
Aroma Summary: A mix of sour funk and sweet berry before grind; post-grind brings gas and musky haze
Medicinal Benefits: Stress relief, anxiety, mild pain, insomnia
Growing Info: Indoor or greenhouse, mid-height, 8-9 week flowering time, high resin output, moderately easy to grow




 Overview
Blue Skunk x Slurricane 44 is a pungent, power-packed feminized strain from In House Genetics. It fuses the funky, old-school bite of Blue Skunk with the modern resin production and terp profile of Slurricane 44. The result is a full-bodied indica-dominant hybrid that delivers flavor, funk, and frost in every nug.
Tailored for connoisseurs and extract artists alike, this strain excels in bag appeal, terpene intensity, and sedative effect. Each pack contains 12 feminized seeds, now available in limited presale.



 What It Looks Like
The flowers are bold and beautiful—featuring dark greens and purples with thick trichome coverage. Nugs are compact, sticky, and easy to trim. The contrast between bright pistils and frosty surfaces makes for serious eye candy.



 Aroma & Flavor Profile
Skunk and berry dominate the initial nose, with undertones of earth and funk. Breaking it down unleashes sour gas and spicy musk. The smoke is thick and flavorful, blending old-school funk with sweet and spicy exhale.



⚡ Effects & Experience
Expect a cerebral haze followed by a mellow, stony body high. This strain is ideal for end-of-day sessions, solo nights, or sleep support. While mentally foggy, it also boosts mood and promotes calm.



 Medicinal Applications
Reported benefits include:

Relief from stress and tension
Insomnia support
Reduced physical discomfort
Anxiety reduction

Its mellow-but-powerful effect makes it a favorite for nighttime use.



 Growing Tips
Blue Skunk x Slurricane 44 grows well indoors and in greenhouses. It prefers stable temps and solid airflow. Flowering finishes in 8 to 9 weeks, with heavy resin production and medium stretch. Great for hashmakers.

Blue Power IX2 Strain Seeds - Sin City Seeds (Feminized)

What Are Blue Power IX2 Strain Seeds?
Blue Power IX2 strain seeds by Sin City Seeds are the result of stacking two powerhouse parents: Blue Power F2 and Blue Power IX1. This feminized hybrid builds on the original Blue Power line, known for its rich blueberry flavor, creamy smoke, and powerful indica-leaning effects. Available in 3-, 5-, or 7-packs, these seeds bring next-gen performance and terpene depth to your garden.
If you’re looking for a flavorful, resin-coated strain that’s easy to grow and perfect for rosin, this one’s for you.

Structure and Appearance
Blue Power IX2 plants grow sturdy and bushy, making them ideal for SCROG setups or low-stress training. The buds are dense and covered in thick trichomes, showing shades of forest green with purple tints by harvest. Their strong lateral branching supports heavy yields of top-shelf flower.

Aroma and Flavor Profile
Open a jar of cured flower and you’ll get a blast of sweet blueberry, cream, and earthy kush. The Blue Power lineage shines here with sugary, dessert-like terps, layered over subtle fuel and vanilla. Whether smoked or dabbed, the flavor is smooth, bold, and long-lasting.

Effects of Blue Power IX2 Seeds
These seeds offer relaxing, euphoric effects that make it a go-to for stress relief and mood elevation. While it leans indica, the high starts with a gentle mental lift before settling into a deep, calming body stone. It’s ideal for evening use or anytime you need to unwind.

Medical Benefits
Many medical users say the flower that helps with anxiety, sleep issues, and chronic pain. Thanks to the balanced body-and-mind effects, it’s also useful for managing stress or boosting low mood without heavy couch lock.

Growing Blue Power IX2 Seeds
These feminized seeds are beginner-friendly and finish in 8-9 weeks. The plants grow compact with tight internodes, making them easy to manage indoors. Resin production is high, which makes this strain especially popular among solventless hash makers.

Why Choose Blue Power IX2 Seeds?
Blue Power IX2 seeds build on one of Sin City Seeds’ most beloved lines. They bring stronger structure, better bag appeal, and even louder blueberry terps. Whether you’re growing for personal stash, flavor, or solventless extraction, this pack delivers everything you need.

What Are Blue Power IX2 Seeds?
Blue Power IX2 strain seeds by Sin City Seeds bring together two legendary parents—Blue Power F2 and Blue Power IX1—to create a regular (non-feminized) seed line with elite potential. This refined backcross captures everything growers love about the Blue Power line: rich blueberry terps, vibrant color, and incredible resin production.
With 15 regular seeds per pack, these genetics offer both stability and versatility. They’re a great choice for breeders, hash makers, and growers who want the best of the Blue Power family.

Appearance and Structure
Blue Power IX2 grows sturdy, bushy plants with tight node spacing and strong branching. Buds are dense, resin-heavy, and coated in icy trichomes. Near the end of flowering, expect hues of purple and dark green to develop, especially under colder temperatures.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Crack open a jar of Blue Power IX2, and you’ll find a blend of sweet blueberry, vanilla cream, and soft earthy kush. The aroma is loud and lingers in the air, making it a favorite among extractors. The flavor matches the scent and stays smooth all the way through the session.

Effects and Uses
While the high leans toward indica, it doesn’t overpower. Users often report a euphoric lift followed by calm body relaxation. It’s a great choice for unwinding in the evening or managing stress during the day. Medical users turn to Blue Power for relief from pain, anxiety, and insomnia.

Growing Blue Power
These regular seeds thrive indoors or outdoors and flower in about 8-9 weeks. Because they aren’t feminized, growers can expect both male and female plants—ideal for pheno hunts and custom breeding projects. High trichome output also makes this a favorite for solventless extraction and hash.

Why Choose Blue Power IX2 Seeds?
If you’re hunting for unique berry flavor, incredible frost, and stable breeding stock, Blue Power IX2 seeds deliver all of the above. This 15-pack of regular seeds is perfect for those looking to create their own hybrids or run large, dialed-in crops. Grab yours now from Neptune Seed Bank.

Offered in a 6-pack of feminized seeds, this cultivar brings intense flavor, powerful effects, and heavy resin production, making it ideal for extractors and growers who love old-school gas with modern edge.
 Lineage
Biker Kush x Double Dose DieselType: Feminized SeedsPack Size: 6 SeedsDominant Type: Indica-Leaning Hybrid

⛽ Aroma, Flavor & Terpenes
Expect a dank fusion of lemony diesel, skunky funk, rubber tire, earthy pine, and sour OG gas. On the grind, it hits with sharp notes of fuel, forest floor, citrus rind, and chem cleaner, creating a nose-wrinkling aroma that lingers in the room—and on the palate.

⚡ Effects & Experience
This hybrid hits hard and fast with a punchy cerebral rush followed by a long-lasting body stone. Great for late-day use, stress relief, and full-body relaxation, Biker Kush x Double Dose Diesel is known to deliver calming, sedative effects without heavy brain fog, especially in moderate doses.

 Growing Info
Biker Kush x Double Dose Diesel strain grows with a medium height and sturdy, OG-style frame, finishing in 8-9 weeks. Buds are dense, frosty, and gassy, ideal for solventless extraction or premium jar appeal. It thrives in indoor environments and responds well to topping, LST, and airflow control.

Product description
Beach Truffle Strain Seeds - Sin City Seeds (Feminized)

What Are Beach Truffle Seeds?
Beach Truffle seeds by Sin City Seeds deliver a terpene-rich hybrid that mixes the earthy funk of White Truffle with the creamy berry tones of Blue Power IX2. This feminized strain is perfect for connoisseurs who crave flavor, frost, and balanced effects. Available in 3-, 5-, and 7-seed packs, it’s a versatile choice for growers at all levels.
Because of its strong genetics, Beach Truffle offers great stability, dense buds, and standout color.

Appearance and Growth Traits
Beach Truffle grows medium-height plants with strong branching and tight internodes. The buds are chunky, rounded, and heavily frosted. Thanks to the Blue Power lineage, you’ll see a mix of purples and deep greens late in flower. These seeds are feminized, so you can expect consistent female plants every time.

Aroma and Flavor Profile
Open a jar of Beach Truffle, and you’re hit with a rush of garlic, cream, and sweet berries. The White Truffle brings that classic savory funk, while Blue Power IX2 layers in smooth candy and vanilla tones. When smoked or vaped, the flavor is rich and full-bodied, making this strain perfect for flavor chasers.

Effects of Beach Truffle
The high from Beach Truffle seeds is both relaxing and clear-headed. It begins with a calm, focused mental state and gradually melts into a full-body chill. This makes it ideal for afternoon or evening sessions. Many users report stress relief and mood elevation without feeling sedated.

Medicinal Benefits
Medical cannabis users say Beach Truffle Strain  may help ease anxiety, muscle tension, and mild depression. Its mood-boosting effects combined with gentle physical relaxation make it useful for day-to-evening use. Moreover, the terpene profile is rich in myrcene and caryophyllene, which may provide additional relief for inflammation.

How to Grow Beach Truffle Seeds
Beach Truffle strain seeds are easy to manage in both indoor and outdoor environments. Flowering finishes in 8 to 9 weeks. The plant responds well to topping, trellising, and light defoliation. Yields are solid, and the trichome coverage is ideal for hash and rosin.

Why Choose Beach Truffle Seeds?
Beach Truffle seeds deliver top-tier flavor, strong visual appeal, and smooth hybrid effects. The White Truffle x Blue Power IX2 pairing results in a unique cultivar that checks all the boxes: terps, frost, and ease of growth. Pick up a pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and experience the best of Sin City breeding.

About the Breeder - Sin City Seeds
Founded in Las Vegas in 2010, Sin City Seeds has become a trusted name among hashmakers and home growers alike. Known for strains like SinMint Cookies and Blue Power IX2, their work is recognized for stability, terpene profiles, and extraction-friendly traits. In fact, SinMint Cookies was named a High Times Top 10 Strain of the Year.

Banana Sours Strain Seeds - Umami Seeds (Regular)

What Are Banana Sours Seeds?
Banana Sours strain seeds by Umami Seeds bring together the tart, minty edge of Mint Sours with the creamy fruit profile of Banana OG, resulting in a strain that’s bold, flavorful, and rich in trichomes. These regular seeds come in a 10-pack, offering both male and female plants ideal for breeding, pheno hunting, or growing exceptional flower.
For those who love fruit-forward gas with dessert-style funk, Banana Sours seeds are a must.

Structure and Appearance
Banana Sours plants grow sturdy and medium in height with strong lateral branching. The buds form into dense, frosty clusters that show bright green tones and occasional purple flashes during late flower. High trichome coverage and great bag appeal make this strain popular among connoisseurs and hashmakers alike.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain delivers a sweet and tangy blend of banana cream, sour mint, and gas. Banana OG brings tropical smoothness, while Mint Sours adds sharp, cool notes that create a unique and complex terp profile. The aroma is strong and lingers long after the jar is opened.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Banana Sours strain seeds produce flower with balanced hybrid effects—calming the body while keeping the mind focused. Many users enjoy the uplifting mood and chill energy, making it great for creative tasks or unwinding at the end of the day. Medicinally, it may help ease stress, anxiety, and light aches.

Growing Banana Sours Seeds
These regular seeds flower in about 8-9 weeks and perform well in both indoor and outdoor setups. Banana Sours responds well to topping, LST, and light defoliation. With strong structure and heavy resin production, it’s also a great pick for solventless extractions and hash production.

Why Choose Banana Sours Seeds?
Banana Sours seeds offer a flavor-packed experience with excellent resin, unique terps, and steady performance. The Mint Sours x Banana OG cross combines classic fruit gas with something refreshingly different. Pick up your 10-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and grow your next favorite pheno.

About the Breeder - Umami Seeds
Umami Seeds is a U.S.-based breeder known for creating hash-forward, terp-heavy genetics. With popular strains like Powduh, Sour Zoda, and Gas Nana, Umami Seeds focuses on cultivars that deliver for both flavor and resin lovers.

Banana Pancakes Strain Feminized Seeds by Star Fire Genetix

What Are Banana Pancakes Seeds?
Banana Pancakes strain seeds from Star Fire Genetix deliver a flavor-packed feminized hybrid that combines the sweet, buttery terpene profile of Pancakes with the tropical funk of Apples and Bananas. Designed for flavor seekers, extractors, and connoisseurs, this strain offers dessert terps, rich resin production, and a smooth, relaxing effect perfect for winding down.

Structure and Appearance
Banana Pancakes grows with a medium stature and solid branching, producing thick, trichome-coated buds with deep greens and purple hints. Buds are dense and sticky, and the plant responds well to topping, light training, and defoliation. It performs great in indoor setups, greenhouses, and sunny outdoor plots.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
The terpene profile is straight from a bakery—sweet banana bread, maple syrup, buttered pancakes, and a fruity funk finish. Apples and Bananas brings bright, tropical notes, while Pancakes adds rich, creamy doughiness. Together, they create a dessert strain that’s loud, lingering, and deeply satisfying.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Expect a relaxing indica-leaning high that begins with gentle euphoria and transitions into full-body calm. Banana Pancakes is great for evening sessions, Netflix binges, or calming a racing mind. Medicinal users may appreciate its ability to relieve anxiety, tension, appetite loss, and sleeplessness.

Growing Banana Pancakes at Home
Banana Pancakes flowers in 8-9 weeks and yields moderate-to-heavy harvests of resin-rich, aromatic buds. It thrives with good airflow and light management. Its dense flower structure and greasy trichome coverage make it ideal for solventless extraction and small-batch connoisseur flower.

Why Choose Banana Pancakes Seeds?
Banana Pancakes seeds offer indulgent dessert terps, consistent growth, and relaxing effects in a reliable feminized format. Bred by Star Fire Genetix, this cross of Pancakes x Apples and Bananas is a must-have for any flavor-focused grower. Grab your 11-pack of feminized seeds now from Neptune Seed Bank and enjoy terpene-rich bliss.

About the Breeder - Star Fire Genetix
Star Fire Genetix crafts high-impact, terpene-loaded hybrids built for both flower and extract lovers. Known for strains like Appleade and Limonada, their work consistently delivers flavor, potency, and bag appeal. Explore more Star Fire Genetix strains.

Atlantis (Fem) (7-Pack) By Sin City Seeds
Where excellence in cannabis genetics meets the ultimate grower’s choice.

Product Overview
Atlantis is a top-tier feminized cannabis strain developed by Sin City Seeds. This strain exemplifies the perfect union of flavor, potency, and grower satisfaction. A cross between the exotic Forbidden Fruit and the resilient Blue Power IX2, Atlantis delivers a terpene-rich and visually stunning experience for growers and connoisseurs alike.

Parent Strain Lineage & Descriptions

Forbidden Fruit: A hybrid of Cherry Pie x Tangie, Forbidden Fruit is celebrated for its sweet tropical fruit notes combined with pine and citrus undertones. It offers a balanced body-mind high with a rich, fruity aroma.
Blue Power IX2: A stabilized phenotype of Blue Power (Sour Double x Master Kush x The White x Blue Moonshine). Known for its dense buds, soothing effects, and signature blueberry and kush flavor, it enhances both yield and resin production.


Key Features

Genetics: Forbidden Fruit x Blue Power IX2
Seed Type: Feminized
Pack Size: 7 premium seeds
Yield: Medium to High (ideal for commercial and personal cultivation)
Flowering Time: Approx. 8-10 weeks
Terpene Profile: Berry-rich with citrus and kush notes
Growth Characteristics: Resilient structure, ideal for indoor and outdoor grows


Why Choose Atlantis?

Optimal Terpenes: Provides a rich blend of fruity, citrusy, and kush flavors.
Feminized Genetics: Increases the likelihood of female plants, reducing cultivation challenges.
Stunning Bag Appeal: Produces dense, resin-rich flowers with visually vibrant hues.
Trusted Breeder: Sin City Seeds is a globally recognized name in cannabis genetics, backed by 20+ years of breeding expertise.

Structure and Appearance
Apple Cloud plants grow strong and moderately tall, with supportive branching and dense, round buds. Expect a colorful finish, with lime green and purple hues, highlighted by deep orange pistils and a thick resin coat. These plants do well in SCROG setups or multi-top techniques.

Why Choose Apple Cloud Seeds?

Animal Cookies x Hindu Strain Feminized Seeds - Bred by Freeborn Selections

What Are Animal Cookies x Hindu Strain Feminized Seeds?
Animal Cookies x Hindu feminized seeds from Freeborn Selections combine two legendary genetics to create a potent, flavorful, and resin-rich hybrid. By crossing the sweet and sedating Animal Cookies with the old-school power of Hindu, this strain delivers bag appeal, aroma, and effects in one package. Each 10-pack of feminized seeds contains all-female plants, making it a convenient choice for growers seeking top-shelf flower with minimal guesswork.

Structure and Appearance
This cultivar grows stocky and strong, with wide leaves and thick branches. It develops dense, golf ball-style buds coated in trichomes and often displays purple hues late in flower. Its tight internodal spacing and low-maintenance structure make it perfect for both indoor and outdoor grows.

Flavor and Aroma Profile

This hybrid leans toward the indica side, offering stress relief, mood elevation, and physical comfort. It’s a great strain for evening use, especially for those dealing with anxiety, restlessness, or muscle tension.

Growing Animal Cookies x Hindu Feminized Seeds
This strain flowers in about 8-9 weeks and thrives in soil, coco, or hydroponic setups. It responds well to topping and low-stress training and performs best in environments with strong airflow. Due to its heavy resin output and terpene complexity, it’s also a solid pick for hash makers and extractors.

Why Choose Animal Cookies x Hindu Feminized Seeds?
Animal Cookies x Hindu feminized seeds offer a powerful mix of flavor, frost, and effects in a grower-friendly format. Bred by Freeborn Selections, this hybrid brings together two elite lines for a top-shelf result. Grab your 10-pack now at Neptune Seed Bank and grow a classic with a modern twist.

What Are Amalfi Coast Seeds?

Structure and Appearance

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain brings a sweet, creamy cookie base with layers of fuel, citrus rind, and sour sherbet. Biscotti adds a smooth dessert backbone, while Sherbanger intensifies it with gassy funk and sour zest. The result is loud, complex, and highly sought after by extractors and connoisseurs.

Effects and Medicinal Use
Amalfi Coast strain seeds produce flower that offers a balanced, calming high. Expect a euphoric lift followed by full-body relaxation—ideal for unwinding in the evening or managing stress. Medicinal users may benefit from relief of anxiety, minor pain, or insomnia symptoms without heavy sedation.

Growing Amalfi Coast Seeds
These regular seeds finish in around 60-65 days and adapt well to indoor or outdoor setups. Amalfi Coast responds well to LST, topping, and SCROG methods. With its resin production and loud terps, it’s also a solid pick for hash artists and solventless processors.

AJ’s Sour Diesel x Sensi Star strain by Katsu Seeds is a potent indica-leaning hybrid that brings together the sharp, fuel-heavy power of AJ’s Sour Diesel cut with the hashy, lemon-spiced knockout punch of Sensi Star. Offered in a 10-pack of regular seeds, this cultivar is bred for gassy terp lovers, hashmakers, and those seeking long-lasting physical relief with bold flavor.
 Lineage

⛽ Aroma, Flavor & Terpenes
This strain delivers a bold aroma with notes of diesel fuel, citrus rind, earthy musk, and spicy lemon hash. On the grind, AJ’s Sour D leads with its skunky chemical tang, while Sensi Star adds depth, richness, and a cool, herbal finish, creating a complex and pungent terp profile that’s unmistakably gassy.

⚡ Effects & Experience
Expect a fast-acting, euphoric lift followed by a deep, full-body stone. AJ’s Sour Diesel x Sensi Star is best used in the evening, offering relief from stress, chronic pain, and insomnia, while preserving mental clarity at lower doses. It’s a favorite among medical users and relaxation-focused cultivators.

Performs exceptionally well indoors and is ideal for solventless extraction or hydrocarbon processing due to its high trichome density and terp retention.

Product description
Air Wolf Strain Regular Seeds - Colab with Katsu Seeds

What Are Air Wolf Strain Regular Seeds?
Air Wolf regular seeds by Katsu Seeds combine two potent cultivars—Dogwalker OG and Romulan—into a hybrid with strong aroma, resin production, and full-spectrum effects. Dogwalker OG contributes its unmistakable skunk and diesel notes, while Romulan adds pine, depth, and hard-hitting body relief. This 12-pack of regular seeds gives growers a range of unique phenotypes and breeding potential, all backed by Romulan and Katsu’s legendary genetics.

Structure and Appearance
Air Wolf plants grow with a sturdy, branching structure and solid apical dominance. Their thick stalks support fat colas that finish dense, frosty, and loud. Buds tend to be lime green with patches of purple and heavy trichome coverage. These plants handle topping and training well, making them ideal for growers looking to maximize canopy space.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
This strain brings together the best of both parents: sharp gas and pine, layered with earthy skunk and subtle fruit. Dogwalker OG contributes heavy diesel and animal funk, while Romulan infuses herbal spice and forest-floor depth. On the inhale, you’ll catch a mix of citrus-kush and fuel; on the exhale, a long-lasting woodsy funk lingers. This one fills the room and the jar—fast.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
Air Wolf delivers a balanced hybrid high that starts with a cerebral buzz before sinking into a relaxing body effect. Users often experience clear-headed focus at first, followed by a heavy-eyed calm. As a result, it’s a great evening strain, especially for those seeking physical relief without mental cloudiness. Medicinal users may turn to Air Wolf for chronic pain, anxiety, inflammation, or sleep support.

Growing Air Wolf Regular Seeds
Air Wolf flowers in approximately 9-10 weeks and performs well in both indoor and outdoor grows. Regular seeds allow for full genetic exploration, making them ideal for pheno hunters and breeders. Plants thrive under moderate feeding and benefit from defoliation in late veg and early bloom. With the right environment, expect above-average yields and high terpene output.

Why Choose Air Wolf Seeds?
Air Wolf seeds bring elite genetics, complex gas-forward flavor, and full-body strength in one aggressive hybrid. Bred by Katsu Seeds—a name synonymous with OG excellence—this strain offers consistency, bag appeal, and therapeutic potency. Grab your 12-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank and unlock the next wave of OG fire.

description:
Product description
In House Genetics - (Animal Cookies x GG4) x Slurricane 44 (Feminized Seeds)
 Key Info

Strain Name: (Animal Cookies x GG4) x Slurricane 44
Dominant Type: Indica-dominant hybrid
Type of Seed: Feminized
Lineage: (Animal Cookies x GG4) x Slurricane 44
Breeder: In House Genetics
Aromas/Flavors: Funky gas, cookie dough, skunk, earth
Effects: Potent relaxation, heavy body buzz, mental calm
Appearance Summary: Resin-packed, dense, colorful
Detailed Appearance: Rock-solid buds coated in greasy trichomes, dark green with violet flecks and bright pistils
Aroma Summary: Loud gas and sweet dough pre-grind; deeper earthy funk post-grind
Medicinal Benefits: Chronic stress, appetite loss, body aches, insomnia
Growing Info: Best indoors, moderate stretch, 8-9 week flower, high yield potential, hash-friendly




 Overview
(Animal Cookies x GG4) x Slurricane 44 is a new heavy-hitting feminized cross from In House Genetics. This cultivar brings together the sticky potency of GG4, the dessert funk of Animal Cookies, and the terp-loaded resin production of Slurricane 44. The result is a knockout hybrid that’s perfect for nighttime use, extract work, or connoisseur collections.
With loud aroma, deep flavor, and stunning bag appeal, this cross is built for those who want it all. Each pack comes with 12 feminized seeds, now available for presale at Neptune Seed Bank.



 What It Looks Like
Expect dense, greasy buds that sparkle under light. The calyxes swell tight, often showing off deep forest green tones with hints of purple late in flower. High trichome coverage makes it visually impressive and ideal for extractors.



 Aroma & Flavor Profile
The nose starts with sharp gas and sweet dough. As it breaks up, you’ll get hints of skunk and earth, all wrapped in a savory cookie finish. When smoked, the flavor blends diesel, nutty dough, and rich hash.



⚡ Effects & Experience
Expect a heavy onset that melts the body and relaxes the mind. While initial effects bring a slight uplift, they quickly settle into strong physical sedation. Great for sleep, pain relief, or zoning out after a long day.



 Medicinal Applications
May assist with:

Insomnia and restlessness
Chronic physical pain
Appetite stimulation
Evening stress or anxiety

Its GG4 x Cookie lineage makes it a go-to for full-body wellness and nighttime use.



 Growing Tips
This strain prefers indoor cultivation with strong airflow. It performs well with topping and light defoliation. Expect a flowering window of 8-9 weeks, with medium to high yields and dense, sticky flowers.



✨ Why Choose (Animal Cookies x GG4) x Slurricane 44 Seeds?
This is one of the most resin-rich drops in the Slurricane 44 collab line.
✅ Loud terps with rich flavor
✅ GG4 potency meets Cookie funk
✅ Top-tier for extractors

Product description


Surfr Seeds - Point Break x Face Off OG #1 (Feminized Seeds)

A Powerful Cross Between Point Break and Face Off OG #1
Surfr Seeds brings you a top-tier hybrid: Point Break x Face Off OG #1. This feminized strain blends the vibrant energy of Point Break with the heavy-hitting calm of Face Off OG. Each pack includes 10 feminized seeds, giving growers strong genetics with guaranteed female plants. As a result, you can expect rich flavors, sticky buds, and a smooth growing process.

Genetics: Point Break x Face Off OG #1
This strain comes from two trusted parents.


Point Break (Tropicana Cookies x Trophy Wife) offers citrus flavors, colorful buds, and a relaxing yet focused high.


Face Off OG #1 brings classic OG strength, piney notes, and a full-body stone that melts away stress.


When combined, they form a balanced hybrid that offers flavor, aroma, and potency in every puff.

Flavors and Aromas: Zesty Citrus with Earthy Undertones
Thanks to its heritage, this strain has a delicious flavor profile. On the inhale, you’ll notice sweet orange, lemon zest, and tropical fruit. On the exhale, hints of pine and earthy herbs linger on the tongue. Overall, this strain is bold, fresh, and unforgettable.

Effects: Creative Start, Calming Finish
At first, this strain delivers a gentle rush to the head. You may feel uplifted, creative, and ready to focus. However, as time goes on, the relaxing side of Face Off OG settles in. Eventually, it may leave your body calm and your mind at ease. For this reason, it’s great for winding down after a long day.

Medical Benefits: Stress Relief and Better Sleep
Not only is this strain enjoyable, but it also helps with relief. Many users say it helps with stress, anxiety, and mild pain. Because of its calming effects, it may also help those who struggle with sleep. If you’re looking for relief without a heavy mental fog, this strain offers a great option.

Growing Info: Rewarding for Experienced Growers
This strain thrives in indoor and outdoor grows. It flowers in about 8-9 weeks and offers high yields when grown with care. Since it produces a lot of resin, it’s perfect for those who like to press or wash. Keep humidity in check during late flowering, and you’ll be rewarded with dense, frosty buds.

Why You’ll Love These Feminized Seeds
Point Break x Face Off OG #1 feminized seeds are great for growers who want a rich, flavorful plant with both head and body effects. The flavors are bold, the high is balanced, and the results are always top shelf. Whether you’re growing for fun or for function, this hybrid delivers. Grab your 10-pack now at Neptune Seed Bank.

Product description
In House Genetics - Juicy J x Slurricane 44 (Feminized Seeds)
 Key Info

Strain Name: Juicy J x Slurricane 44
Dominant Type: Indica-dominant hybrid
Type of Seed: Feminized
Lineage: Juicy J x Slurricane 44
Breeder: In House Genetics
Aromas/Flavors: Fruity candy, grape gas, creamy kush, tropical punch
Effects: Relaxing, happy, calming, slightly stoney
Appearance Summary: Vibrant, frosty, resin-heavy
Detailed Appearance: Bold lime and violet tones, sparkling trichomes, and copper pistils stacked on dense flowers
Aroma Summary: A sweet burst of fruit and candy upfront; deeper kushy grape gas post-grind
Medicinal Benefits: Stress, depression, mood swings, insomnia
Growing Info: Medium-tall structure, responds well to topping, 8-9 weeks flowering, indoor preferred, high resin production




 Overview
Juicy J x Slurricane 44 is a sweet and stoney hybrid crafted by In House Genetics for those chasing flavor, color, and high-end resin. Juicy J brings candy shop terps to the mix, while Slurricane 44 backs it up with deep gas, frost, and strong indica effects.
This feminized strain is ideal for flavor-forward growers and hashmakers. Each presale pack contains 12 feminized seeds, available while supplies last.



 What It Looks Like
Expect vibrant flowers with deep greens, pops of purple, and heavy trichome coverage. Buds are medium-large and tight, with a thick coat of resin and high bag appeal.



 Aroma & Flavor Profile
This strain hits the nose with a juicy blast of tropical fruit, grape, and sweet candy. Once broken up, expect more kushy undertones and a rich, fuel-laced finish. On inhale, it’s smooth and fruity. On exhale, the gas shines through.



⚡ Effects & Experience
Great for unwinding, this strain brings mild euphoria, elevated mood, and a gentle body melt. While not overpowering, higher doses can lean sedative. It’s perfect for creative relaxation, light socializing, or solo chill sessions.



 Medicinal Applications
May help with:

Depression or low mood
Stress or anxiety
Evening wind-down or sleep prep
Mild body aches and tension

Its terpene-rich profile supports both mental uplift and physical relaxation.



 Growing Tips
Juicy J x Slurricane 44 prefers indoor setups with strong light and airflow. Train early for maximum canopy control. Flowering wraps up in 8-9 weeks, with medium-high yields and premium-grade resin—great for solventless work.

description:
Product description
Cherry AK x Skycuddler Double Kush F3 - Regular Seeds by Freeborn Selections

What Are Cherry AK x Skycuddler Seeds?
Cherry AK x Skycuddler Double Kush F3 seeds from Freeborn Selections fuse bold flavor with structured stability, offering a unique hybrid with deep cherry notes and creamy kush undertones. This regular seed pack includes both male and female plants, ideal for breeding projects or growers seeking full-expression phenotypes. Each 10-pack offers access to a classic Freeborn cross that shines in both flavor and effect.

Structure and Appearance
This strain grows with moderate stretch and strong branching. Buds are medium-dense and dusted in trichomes, with a mix of forest green and deep violet hues. The F3 Skycuddler genetics lend uniformity and great structure, while Cherry AK adds visual pop and vibrant energy to the garden.

Flavor and Aroma Profile
Expect a bold nose of sour cherry, earthy spice, sweet hash, and gas. Cherry AK brings forward bright, fruity top notes with sharpness on the finish, while Skycuddler adds a velvety kush base. This combo results in a well-balanced, loud terpene profile that works beautifully in both flower and extract.

Effects and Medicinal Benefits
These seeds produce phenos with balanced hybrid effects—mentally uplifting at first, then gently calming the body. It’s an excellent choice for daytime creativity or evening social settings. Medical users often report relief from stress, light pain, and fatigue without heavy sedation.

Growing
This cultivar flowers in 8 to 9 weeks and adapts well to multiple growing styles. It thrives in organic soil or hydro systems and handles topping, training, and light pruning with ease. Thanks to its stable F3 lineage, phenos show consistency in growth and resin output.

Why Choose Cherry AK x Skycuddler Seeds?
The seeds offer a standout mix of fruit, hash, and gas in a grower-friendly format. Bred by Freeborn Selections, this regular seed drop is perfect for collectors, breeders, or anyone looking for a flavorful, effect-balanced cultivar. Grab your 10-pack now from Neptune Seed Bank before this drop fades.

About the Breeder - Freeborn Selections
Freeborn Selections, led by Mean Gene from Mendocino, is celebrated for its complex terpene profiles and consistent performance indoors and out. With releases like Lime 1 x Jaro F3, PK x Hindu, and Not Deathstar x Grape Lime Skunk, their work has become a cornerstone of modern cannabis breeding.
